The adidas Ultra 4D Miami Hurricanes is a shoe built for support and a stable step, time and again, with a rubber sole providing the perfect amount of traction.

fields.name: Core Black Eqt Support Ultra X Mastermind
Nmd Human Race Trail Solar Pack Orange X Pharrell

data.description: Developed to channel the style and spirit of East Africa using the NMD Human Race as a canvas and the mind of Pharrell Williams as its brush the NMD Human Race Trail Solar Pack Orange x Pharrell released in August 2018 is a colourful celebration coming from close to the equator. The shoe’s Primeknit upper is a fusion of grey, black and teal hues, that is accented by orange rope laces and a moulded purple lace-cage. On the vamp of each shoe, inscribed in an alphanumeric text, are the Swahili words ‘MIELE’ (forever) and ‘MBELE’ (forward) a notably progressive and positive message one in which Pharrell Williams has become known for through all his Adidas designs. This shoe is perfect as a fashion statement while is also suitably functional, with it's under sole tread mimicking that of hiking shoes to make sure you are never caught out on any terrain.

fields.name: Adidas Forum Low Chocolate To My Strawberry Womens

data.description: Arguably one of the best basketball silhouettes of all time, the adidas Forum Low continues to deliver on style and comfort year after year. If you’re eager to get your hands on a pair, the Chocolate to My Strawberry Women's iteration is a stylish pick. The unique design puts a romantic spin on the innovative sneaker, featuring various brown accents that subtly pair with a strawberry jewel. For instance, the chocolatey hue appears in various shades and materials on the quarter’s Three Stripes, the heel mudguard, and the elongated heel counter. If you look closer, you’ll find a soft beige suede mudguard at the toe and pale pink on the sock lining, tongue trim, ankle strap, and underfoot. Various logos give the sneakers the brand’s seal of approval, as it features the famous Trefoil logo near the collar and on the midsole.

fields.name: Collegiate Navy Nmd R1 (W)
Bred Nmd Xr1
Pharrell X Nmd Tr Holi

data.description: Paying homage to the Hindu Festival of Colour known as Holi, this March 2018 release, as part of the three colourway "Holi Festival" pack, Pharrell Williams and Adidas once again excellently team up to create the Pharrell x NMD TR Holi, and it's a goodun. This pack follows on from the clean and refined ‘Blank Canvas' Collection. Unlike that release, this Pharrell HU NMD sports an eye-popping upper. Just like the explosions of colour seen across the Indian subcontinent during the Holi festival, this pair features a tie-dye printed Primeknit. This colourway is a fusion of oranges, greens and purples which feature in an acid-wash effect. It's totally unique and makes this silhouette especially appealing for the summer months. All the conventional Hu details are present from the integrated laces to the synthetic sidewall caging. This shoe is definitely a unique piece and not one for the fans of the understated, it is genuinely channelling the paint parties of the Indian Festival, and so when you wear it you feel like you are wearing something more than just a shoe.

fields.name: Primeknit Nmd Cs1 X United Arrows & Sons

data.description: adidas has collaborated with many fashion brands in the past, from Yeezy to Stella McCartney. Yet, few have been more exciting and unique than its partnership with United Arrows & Sons, a contemporary Japanese fashion label. Released in 2017, the minimalistic black Primeknit upper offers a stealthy yet simple design, ensuring the sneakers attract attention as you walk down the street. Offering a sock-style fit, you can trust the sleek shoes will feel comfortable throughout the day. Helping the Primeknit NMD CS1 x United Arrows & Sons sneakers stand out further is the white Japanese text from calligrapher MIKITYPE on the medial quarter, front EVA plug, and heel pull, which harmonise with a chunky white Boost midsole unit and gum outsole. It is a unique adidas design that will stand apart in any small or extensive sneaker collection.

fields.name: Adidas Samba X Wales Bonner Leo Dark Brown
Chinese New Year Ultraboost 1.0
Bright Cyan Nmd R1
Adidas Samba X Pharrell Humanrace Night Grey

data.description: Made in partnership with music legend Pharrell Williams, the adidas Samba x Pharrell Humanrace Night Grey combines retro aesthetics with premium materials. Its leather upper is decorated with understated branding and a grey suede toe cap. The gum rubber sole allows for effective grip, the elongated tongue adds a unique feature and padding in the collar offers cushioning. Buy and sell the adidas Samba x Pharrell Humanrace Night Grey with Laced.

fields.name: Grey Metallic Nmd R2

data.description: Showcasing modern sneaker technology, the adidas Grey Metallic NMD R2 is created with comfort and precision in mind. Composed of mesh, leather and suede for a comfortable fit, monochromatic shades dominate the design. Three Stripes branding remains in situ, while React foam is found in the clean white sole. An effortless essential for year-round wear, the adidas Grey Metallic NMD R2 is a certified must-have.

fields.name: Adidas Nmd Hu X Pharrell Animal Print

data.description: Meet the collaborative adidas NMD Hu X Pharrell Animal Print, a Flintstones-inspired design that will add fierce flair to any outfit. With its orange Primeknit animal-print upper, this prehistoric-themed shoe is complete with understated adidas branding on its grey heel tab to let the sneaker’s exotic design shine. Its contrasting aqua green rope-style laces are fed through a grey latticed feature which attaches the system to its orange Boost cushioned midsole. A grippy black midsole grounds the adidas NMD Hu X Pharrell Animal Print, a wild edition of this sporty classic that’s suited to any occasion.

fields.name: Adidas 8Th Street Samba X Ronnie Fieg X Clarks Shadow Green

data.description: Meet the adidas 8th Street Samba x Ronnie Fieg x Clarks Shadow Green collaboration, giving a fresh look to the iconic 8th Street Samba sneaker, in a stylish black and dark green combination. It is crafted from a mix of suede upper, leather on the heel tab and Three Stripes, while sitting on a Clarks’ yellowish rubber sole that delivers traction and durability. Elevate your shoe collection with the adidas 8th Street Samba x Ronnie Fieg x Clarks Shadow Green, combining timeless style with a modern touch.

fields.name: Adidas Nmd Human Race X Human Made
Vintage White Nmd R1

data.description: The reverse colourway of the NMD R1 ‘OG’, this design retains the originals bright red and blue EVA plugs which have become so iconic amongst trainers fans but replace its black upper with a washed out white Primeknit to match its boost under sole. The NMD R1 ‘Vintage White’ was released internationally on May 28 2016, and have quickly become a staple of the NMD product portfolio, who wouldn't want a classic in all white?

fields.name: Adidas Gazelle Bold Black White Womens

data.description: The adidas Gazelle Bold Black White colourway elevates one of the most popular sneaker silhouettes of all time. Stacked three layers higher than usual, it’s a fresh twist on the classic 1968 sneaker and a must-add to a collection. The soft black suede upper helps retain the silhouette’s sporty aesthetic, which pairs with white serrated Three Stripes on the sidewalls and metallic gold Gazelle branding for a heritage feel. Sneaker fans will instantly recognise the iconic T-toe overlay, which adds an extra layer of texture to the timeless shoe.

fields.name: Leather Cage Ultraboost 3.0

data.description: Take your everyday style to the next level with the adidas Leather Cage UltraBoost 3.0. Released in March 2017, the sneakers have a premium design that will upgrade any everyday outfit. The black Primeknit upper is soft and flexible for a comfortable fit, and its added texture creates a more refined style. The luxe black cage provides strength and support while holding the matte black wax laces firmly in place. The matte black hue appears again on the perforated heel counter with debossed UltraBoost branding. Breaking up the black of the Leather Cage UltraBoost 3.0 is the white Boost midsole, which offers soft, responsive cushioning to provide more power as you run or walk. Finishing off the minimalistic aesthetic is the black Continental outsole for superior traction and improved running performance.

fields.name: Cream Glitch Eqt Support 93/17
Adidas Samba X Fucking Awesome Black White

data.description: Reimagined by American skateboarder Jason Dill, the adidas Samba x Fucking Awesome x Black White offers a monochromatic twist on a classic. This collaborative shoe sports a leather upper and Three Stripes branding, fusing timelessness with timeless details. The ‘FA’ logo embossed on the tongue and custom sockliner emblem adds exclusivity to the design. Completed by a sleek black rubber outsole, the adidas Samba x Fucking Awesome Black White is a must-have for your collection.

fields.name: Nmd R1 Primeknit Tri Color

data.description: One half of the Adidas NMD R1 Primeknit 'Tri-Color' pack, this clean take on 2016's most popular trainer sees the iconic three stripes logo take centre stage for the December 2016 NMD R1 Primeknit Tri-Color. Featuring a grey-tinted woven Primeknit upper and with the Three Stripes getting the tri-coloured treatment this goes some way to offering some variation, which with black accents and a white Boost midsole balance out the shoe nicely. It's a celebration of 2016's MVP, and we think its pretty slick.

fields.name: Adidas Velosamba X End Social Cycling Legend Ink

data.description: Sporting a beige-toned colourway, the adidas Velosamba x END Social Cycling Legend Ink is made in collaboration with streetwear store END. Its premium suede upper is detailed with a leather heel cut out, gold lettering and coffee-inspired stripe detailing. Underfoot, midsole cushioning offers comfort and the textured outsole provides effective grip. Fastened with a classic lacing system, the adidas Velosamba x END Social Cycling Legend Ink is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Adidas Ultra Boost 1.0 Solar Yellow 2019

data.description: After four years of absence from the trainer scene, the legendary Adidas Ultra Boost 1.0 Sollar Yellow is back. One of the there original Ultra Boost colourways that debuted in 2015, and is still regarded as one of the hottest on the market. Dipped from heel to toe in a hi-vis yellow hue, the upper is crafted from a stretchy Primeknit that gently hugs the contours of your feet for added comfort with every step. This is all accompanied by black accents that are peppered throughout the toe box, while a complementary cage flanks the lateral and medial sides for extra support and stability.

fields.name: Adidas Forum High 84 Unc

data.description: A spring-ready take on the OG Forum silhouette, the adidas Forum High 84 UNC boasts a retro vibe with premium fabrics, instantly recognisable branding and interchangeable laces. The leather upper is contrasted with UNC blue suede stripes on the sidewalls, with the same hue featuring on the tongue and collar. A sturdy strap is added to the lace-up fastening so you can quickly loosen the fit if you need, while breathable perforations on the toe box enhance ventilation. Easy to style whatever the season, add the adidas Forum High 84 UNC to your off-duty collection and you’ll never want to take them off.

fields.name: Nmd R1 Primeknit Datamosh 2.0 Maroon X Sneakerstuff
Adidas Samba Decon Black White Gum

data.description: The adidas Samba Decon BLACK White Gum preserves the classic Samba silhouette, showcasing a sleeker look. Leather dominates the upper, complemented by a suede T-Toe and sharp Three Stripes. An updated collar and tongue bring reduced padding, ensuring a lighter feel. In a classic colorway, the adidas Samba Decon Black White Gum blends tradition with a modern edge, making it a must-have in your collection.

fields.name: Pharrell X Adidas Nmd Hu Triple Black

data.description: Triple blacks never go out of style, the newly dropped Pharrell x adidas NMD Hu Triple Black is just another example of exactly that. Flaunting a futuristic all-black construction for the once table topping NMD silhouette this model keeps it somewhat traditional by deploying a classic knitted upper with grey accent son the branding and a patented Boost midsole also arriving in a similar grey hue underfoot. Pharrell Williams’ signature wrapping laces also make a triumph return on this model secured with similarly familiar TPU panels on either side. Sleek and streamlined, this kick is finally finished with the words “Breathe” and “Thoughts” printed on the upper portion of either foot to send one of Pharrell’s patented positive affirmations to every wearer.

fields.name: Trace Green Gazelle
Triple Black Nmd R1

data.description: Fans of a minimalistic and classic sneaker design will love this pair of adidas Triple Black NMD R1 sneakers in deep triple black. The fabric upper comes in a breathable mesh fabric that’s built for tailored comfort and works perfectly with the adidas Boost cushioning for the ultimate fit. Adorning the fabric upper are also the black adidas branding stripes, as well as black laces, a black eyestay cage, and a smooth black heel tab. The tongue of the Triple Black NMD R1 is also made from breathable mesh fabric, meaning a more ventilated and comfortable fit. The black rubber midsole includes the adidas brand panel to the front of the sneaker, while the back includes the grill mudguard. The mid and outer sole, both in bold black, combine with cushioned comfort for a shoe you’ll want to wear anywhere.

fields.name: Adidas Gazelle Dark Green Gs

data.description: Staying close to OG Gazelle designs, the two-toned adidas Gazelle Dark Green GS will instantly elevate any everyday outfit. Its suede base is accented with leather stripes, gold lettering and an adidas-branded heel tab. The OrthoLite sockliner offers comfort with every wear, while its textured outsole provides effective grip. Fastened with a classic lacing system, the adidas Gazelle Dark Green GS is packed with retro appeal.

fields.name: Marvel X Adidas Forum 84 Hi 'Star Lord'
Clear Blue Nmd R1
Adidas Velosamba X End Social Cycling Crystal White

data.description: Created in collaboration with streetwear store END, the adidas Velosamba x END Social Cycling Crystal White features a midsole cut-out designed to fit a pedal. Made from premium suede and leather, its upper is decorated with classic branding. Cushioning underfoot offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and the classic lacing system allows for a secure fit. Buy and sell the adidas Velosamba x END Social Cycling Crystal White with Laced.

fields.name: Nmd Human Race X Pharrell Green

data.description: Hot on the heels of the Yellow iterations sell-out success Pharrell Williams yet again takes the opportunity to team up with Adidas to give one of the most popular silhouettes around another new lick of paint. Released in September 2016 the NMD Human Race x Pharrell Green is crafted with soft and lightweight mesh material and a bold shade of green covers the entire upper. The words ‘HUMAN' and ‘RACE' are emblazoned across the shoe in white, which is complemented by a white midsole underfoot. Black offers a stark contrast on that unique lace cage and features again to the re-engineered EVA midsole plugs. This shoe is just another great option from this growing Adidas range which only further highlights Pharrell Williams design prowess.

fields.name: Adidas Adimatic X Neighborhood Charcoal Black Grey

data.description: Created in collaboration with Japanese streetwear brand NEIGHBORHOOD, the adidas Adimatic x NEIGHBORHOOD Charcoal is made using sustainable materials. Sporting a muted colourway, its brushed suede base features sidewall stripes, perforations and co-branded touches. Its midsole takes on a jagged midsole design and also houses classic cushioning, while its textured outsole provides grip. Fastened with thick laces, the adidas Adimatic x NEIGHBORHOOD Charcoal will never fail to impress.

fields.name: Offspring X Adidas Zx 10000 La

data.description: Colourful pastel hues meet soft fabric in the Offspring x adidas ZX 10000 LA collaboration from Offspring and adidas. The upper comes with a soft grey mesh fabric which is overlaid by a rose pink caging in perforated suede. This is paired with the three adidas stripes in pink and white elastic on the side. The same shade of light pink returns for the suede toe cap, as well as the rubber guard at the back of the shoe. Bold black then allows the colours to pop, with a segment at the lower half of the shoe, complete with small pink polka dots. A supportive sole comes in creamy white rubber for both the mid and outer sole, which is grooved for maximum traction. On top, you have soft grey laces and a grey fabric tongue to finish.

fields.name: Stan Smith X Starcow X Alife
Adidas Lg2 Spzl X Liam Gallagher Bottle Green

data.description: Introducing the adidas LG2 SPZL x Liam Gallagher Bottle Green, a blend of tradition and innovation. Crafted from chalk white nylon and adorned with tonal suede overlays, this silhouette is a testament to exclusive design. A protective rubber toe guard ensures durability, while the Three Stripes and back tab contrast the green leather accents. The ‘Endorsed by Liam Gallagher’ emblem on the tongue adds a touch of authenticity. Enjoy comfort in every step with the lightweight EVA midsole, complemented by the herringbone-traction gum rubber outsole. Walk the line between heritage and style with the adidas LG2 SPZL x Liam Gallagher Bottle Green.

fields.name: Olive Primeknit Nmd R1 X White Mountaineering
Primeknit Olive Cargo Nmd Xr1
Olive Cargo Eqt Support Adv

data.description: Originally designed for athletes, the classic EQT receives a versatile update with the adidas Olive Cargo EQT ADV. Crafted with comfortable Primeknit, the sock-like upper features a lightweight design, Three Stripes branding and earth-toned hues. A moulded EVA outsole delivers non-stop support, while textured tread rounds off the design. An effortless style for every occasion, update your rotation with the adidas Olive Cargo EQT ADV.

fields.name: Adidas Originals Gazelle Indoor Green White

data.description: Updating the indoor football training shoe, the adidas Originals Gazelle Indoor Green White boasts vintage-style aesthetics. Sporting a forest green colourway, its suede upper is decorated with classic adidas branding, gold detailing and a leather heel tab. The cushioned midsole offers comfort, the gum rubber outsole provides grip and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Find your size with Laced.

fields.name: Adidas Ultraboost 4.0 Dna Triple Black

data.description: You will feel like you are walking on a cloud when wearing a pair of adidas UltraBoost 4.0 DNA Triple Black sneakers. Since UltraBoost’s debut in 2015, the silhouette has become a top choice for running shoes among sneakerheads. The Triple Black colourway features all the elements you would expect from the much-loved sneaker, including a soft adidas Primeknit upper for a sock-like fit, a lace closure, and a midfoot cage and heel counter for extra support. Eco-conscious sneaker fans can buy with confidence, as the adidas UltraBoost 4.0 DNA Triple Black design is constructed from Primeblue, which is a high-performance recycled fabric crafted from Parley Ocean Plastic. Of course, a pair of UltraBoost wouldn’t be complete without its renowned Boost midsole that’s super comfortable and will add energy and power to every step you take. Completing the all-black iteration is an all-black adidas tongue tab, serving as a symbol of comfort and style.

fields.name: Adidas Samba Adv Black Gum

data.description: Originally made in the 1950s for indoor football training, the adidas Samba ADV Black Gum is also synonymous with ‘90s skateboarding style. Sporting a versatile colourway, its leather base is decorated with suede overlays, gold lettering and Three Stripe detailing. Internal padding delivers comfort, the gum rubber outsole provides grip and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Add the adidas Samba ADV Black Gum to your collection now.

fields.name: Ultraboost 1.0 X Kolor Solar Orange
Bright Cyan Nmd R1 (J)
Collegiate Burgundy Ultraboost 3.0
Adidas Gazelle Maroon Gum
Ultraboost X Sneakerstuff 1.0 Tee Time
Shock Purple Ultraboost 2.0 (W)
Noah X Adidas Vintage Runner Brown
Adidas Forum Low Triple White

data.description: The adidas Forum Low Triple White colourway is the personification of box fresh. The no-thrills sneaker has abandoned all colours for a super white design that allows the original features to shine. The hardwearing, premium leather construction provides a super comfortable fit, and the Velcro strap improves support and stability. adidas takes comfort to the next level by incorporating an EVA midsole, creating a soft, lightweight, and shock-absorbent design you'll never grow tired of wearing. You will feel as if you are walking on air all day long. Giving the adidas Forum Low Triple White sneakers the stamp of approval is the brand's famous Three Stripe emblem on the quarter and the classic logo on the midsole and ankle strap. It is a perfect sneaker pick for the spring and summer seasons.

fields.name: Nmd R2 Primeknit X Wings+Horns
Adidas Campus 00S Ambient Sky

data.description: Dressed in a pastel-toned colourway, the adidas Campus 00s Ambient Sky utilises recycled materials. Its premium suede base features sidewall stripes, perforations and other touches of branding. The padded collar and tongue add to the retro-inspired sneaker’s oversized look, while its rubber sole unit offers both cushioning and grip. Complete with thick laces, refresh your collection with the adidas Campus 00s Ambient Sky.

fields.name: Pharrell X Bbc X Adidas Nmd Hu Plaid Blue

data.description: Born from a collaboration between Pharrell and the Billionaire Boys Club, the Pharrell x BBC x adidas NMD Hu Plaid Blue will suit every style inclination. Part of the limited-edition “Digijack” pack, the sneaker features plaid print overlays and co-branded logos throughout. Black and blue hues adorn the sidewalls, toe cap and heel, while the full-length Boost cushioning in the sole makes it a comfortable addition to any collection.

fields.name: Primeknit Tri Colour Nmd R1

data.description: The French flag-inspired Primeknit Tri Colour NMD R1 will add colour, energy, and effortless style to your look. The synonymous colours of blue, white, and red form the famous Three Stripes logo on the medial and lateral quarters to create a head-turning aesthetic. Released in 2016, the sneakers offer much more than a modern style, as they are super comfortable due to the full Primeknit upper construction with a White Noise knit pattern, providing a sock-like fit. The classic white Boost midsole is a fresh contrast against the black EVA inserts and upper. Boosting the stylish Primeknit Tri Colour NMD R1 sneaker's support are the moulded heel patch, moulded tread, lace-up fastening, and sock-like cuff.

fields.name: Adidas Ultraboost X Lego Color Pack Red
Prada X Adidas Forum Low Black

data.description: Landing as part of the Prada x adidas Forum pack, the Prada x adidas Forum Low Black takes the classic forum and adds a premium spin to deliver a timeless style. The leather upper is detailed with both Prada and three-stripe branding, and the laces host a removable Prada pouch for extra style points. Underfoot, just the right amount of cushioning is added to support your foot from heel to forefoot, while the textured tread delivers on grip. Easy to wear thanks to the clean black colourway, add the Prada x adidas Forum Low Black to your collection and reserve them for special occasions.

fields.name: Adidas Samba X Star Wars Boba Fett Sarlacc Pit
Adidas Handball Spezial Pulse Blue Gum

data.description: Created for handball players back in 1979, the adidas Handball Spezial Pulse Blue Gum stays close to its sporty ‘70s roots. Layered with leather stripes and suede panelling, its nylon base is also accented with adidas branding. Its OrthoLite sockliner offers comfort with every wear, while its gum sole unit offers both concealed cushioning and effective grip. Rounded off with classic laces and a textured tongue, add the adidas Handball Spezial Pulse Blue Gum to your collection now.

fields.name: Palace X Gazelle Indoor
Winter Wool Primeknit Nmd Cs1
Adidas Gazelle Bold Grey White Womens

data.description: A modern spin on a classic silhouette, the adidas Gazelle Bold Grey White Womens is crafted from premium calf suede in an elegant shade of cloudy grey. The Three Stripes are proudly sitting on the sides alongside the golden Gazelle lettering. What sets this pair apart is the chunky rubber sole, ensuring comfort and traction while giving you extra height and a retro silhouette. Elevate your style with the adidas Gazelle Bold Grey White Womens.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Paris White

data.description: This minimalistic Air Jordan 1 Mid Paris White sneaker subtly conveys the colours of Paris in red, white and blue, with a premium upper in Air Jordan 1 Mid silhouette. The upper comes in clean white leather, spreading from the toe to heel, mixing smooth panels across the perforated toe box and main mid sides with tumbled leather around the toe, front side panels, heel panel, and eyelet strip. This is overlaid with a deep navy blue Nike Swoosh along the side in suede, while the rear ankle strap comes in delicate grey leather with a red embroidered Air Jordan Wings logo on the side. The rest of the Air Jordan 1 Mid Paris White sneaker is complete with soft white fabric around the collar, clean white laces, a white rubber midsole, and a soft grey rubber outer sole, built for maximum traction and grip.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Chicago X Off-White

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 gets the Off-White treatment for this September 2017 release, one of the most anticipated releases of the year takes a deconstructed look at a classic Air Jordan 1. Dressed in the original Chicago themed colourway this shoe is draped in nostalgia, but as always with designed Virgil Abloh's unique twists. The Air Jordan 1 Retro High x Off-White purposely looks half-finished in some of its detailing, visible blue stitching, "Air" text printed on the midsole and an Off-White Zip tie all culminate to let everyone know this is an Off-White collaboration. The modern twist on an already established heavyweight is the primary draw for this product and the many other remixed silhouettes in the Nike x Off-White range. Taking a product as overwhelmingly popular as the Air Jordan 1, and breathing new life into it in a way only Virgil could is what makes this trainer a must have. If you love high tops and you like Off-White, well this is a match made in heaven for you, I can promise you, you aren't going to find a better high top around right now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Banned 2020

data.description: The brand new release of the Jordan 1 Mid Banned is going to make Air Jordan 1 have one of its most successful years to date - perhaps the greatest colourway for the silhouette is only just about to drop. The shoe comes dressed in the now infamous 'Banned' colourway. The black and red combo of the Jordan 1 Banned was made famous when the NBA banned Michael Jordan's 1's in 1984. The upcoming Mid reflects the banned AJ1 perfectly and will be a must-cop for fans of the silhouette. Premium leather uppers feature across the Air Jordan 1 Mid Banned's panelling, with the heel and the toe box featuring the Chicago Bulls red just like its OG counterpart. The legendary swoosh features down the lateral and medial sides of the sneaker, also in that same striking red. Perfectly contrasting underlays of black make this sneaker pop, with the wings logo on the ankle finishing off the almost identical look of the shoe. Underfoot, a white midsole features with a red outsole to complement the sneakers 'Bred' colourway. Nike Air technology features to guarantee comfort whether you are looking to hit the court or the streets in them. The Air Jordan 1 Banned is the closest release we have seen to the original colourway in quite some time. Be sure to add these to your winter rotation as they will most definitely sell out.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro University Blue

data.description: Whenever a Jordan silhouette features the legendary UNC blue colourway, you know that sneaker will become a classic. This time around, we see the iconic blue hue grace the Air Jordan 4 Retro University Blue. The uppers are entirely wrapped in the legendary powder blue colour, ensuring that you know this is a UNC Air Jordan. The bright uppers are contrasted by another of Jordan Brand's most legendary design aspects, with grey cement featuring throughout the design too. The iconic Jumpman logo features on the Jordan 4 Retro University Blue sneaker's heel and tongue, completing the shoe's look. Underfoot, a mix of white, grey cement and black makes up the sole unit. This sole houses Nike Air technology which we can see due to the visible air bubble. Comfort is unmatched with the Jordan 4 due to this. The Air Jordan 4 Retro University Blue will be a shoe that is instantly catapulted into the sneaker of the year discussion, be sure to add a pair to your rotation.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Lucky Green Gs

data.description: Showcasing a vibrant colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Low Lucky Green GS puts a modern spin on the ‘80s basketball silhouette. Featuring a perforated toe box for ventilation, its leather upper is accented with classic touches of branding. The Air midsole underfoot offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Complete with padding in its collar, elevate your everyday looks with the Air Jordan 1 Low Lucky Green GS.

fields.name: Jordan 4 Retro Golf White Cement

data.description: The classic retro styling from the Air Jordan 4 line never disappoints, and this minimalistic styling in clean white and light grey is a versatile design that’s ready to be shown off anywhere. The premium upper of the Jordan 4 Retro Golf White Cement comes with smooth panels of white leather extending from the toe to the heel, with a white mesh insert along the side and at the bottom of the eyestay panel. The rear side panels are overlaid with a grey speckled rubber strap leading to the extra-large eyestay accessory in black, alongside clean white laces and a white tongue. The speckled light grey repeats for the heel tab, the rubber mudguards, and the semi-translucent outer sole. To the heel of the Jordan 4 Retro Golf White Cement, you also have a visible Air Unit and black rubber midsole accents.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Apricot Womens

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid has brought Jordan Brand some serious success over the last few years, and with colourways like the upcoming Jordan 1 Mid Apricot Orange, it's easy to see why. The sneaker has a similar look to the hugely successful Air Jordan 1 Mid Milan that released in 2020, and we expect the Jordan 1 Apricot Orange to be just as sought-after. The sneakers upper comes crafted from a mix of materials, with pebbled leather, suede and mesh all being used. The orange, pink and beige hues used gives the shoe a summer-feel, making it perfect for the upcoming hotter months—the Nike Swoosh detailing features, as does the iconic wings logo. Down below, a classic Air Jordan 1 sole unit features and houses Nike Air technology. The famous technology in our Jordan 1 Mid Apricot Orange guarantees comfort, whether you are wearing it on the court or the street.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Messy Room Gs
Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Dutch Green Womens

data.description: Get ready for Spring with these pastel hues of green, white, and a touch of pink. The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Dutch Green Womens is a celebration of the classic silhouette complemented by soft shades of green, both light and dark. The comfortable leather uppers include pale green, set against a black Nike swoosh and a pale pink wings logo on the collar. This is blended perfectly with the pale pink laces, adding a playful spark of colour to the darker green tones of the Womens Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Dutch Green. Enjoy traditional and comfortable Nike Air cushioning on the rubber sole in complementary shades of white and green. The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Dutch Green Womens are a must-have for the season and will look great with any outfit, especially the vibrant green offset against darker clothing tones.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Thunder Ps (2023)

data.description: Made from premium materials, the Air Jordan 4 Thunder PS (2023) revives a two-toned colourway first seen in 2006. Its upper features grid mesh panelling, classic Jordan branding and a handy pull tab for an easy on and off. Underfoot, the Air-cushioned midsole delivers comfort and the rubber outsole provides grip. Fastened with a secure lace closure, refresh your kid’s rotation with the Air Jordan 4 Thunder PS (2023).

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Atmosphere Womens

data.description: You can never have too many pairs of Air Jordan 1s, so add the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Atmosphere Womens to your collection now. With all the silhouette’s signature details, the upper is crafted from tumbled leather and breathable perforations are added to the toe box for enhanced ventilation. Jordan’s Wings logo sits on the ankle, while Nike’s Swoosh takes pride of place on the sidewalls for that instant brand recognition. Presented in an easy-to-wear pink and navy colourway, the AJ1 Retro High Atmosphere deserves a place in your everyday line-up. So, what are you waiting for?

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Red Quilt Gs

data.description: Step out in style with these Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Red Quilt GS sneakers, the perfect accompaniment to any look, and with the added Nike cushioned sole exclusive to Nike, these comfortable sneakers will be a favourite for every wardrobe this summer. The stylish red look of the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Red Quilt GS is complemented perfectly with tonal synthetic leather uppers and a textured design. The white bottoms and Air Jordan Jumpman logo add a nice bit of contrast, and the whole trainer has the bounce you know and love. The structure is there, the look and the silhouette are there and everything you’ve come to expect from the Air Jordan range is there, making the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Red Quilt GS the perfect sneakers to take your look to the next level.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Taupe Haze

data.description: The Air Jordan 4 is quickly becoming one of the most iconic sneakers within the sneaker industry, catching up with the Air Jordan 1 each release. The unbelievable upcoming Jordan 4 Taupe Haze release will only catapult the AJ4 further up the popularity ranks. A shoe that looks eerily similar to the Travis Scott Cactus Jack Air Jordan 4 that has been teased many times, we cannot get enough of the legendary Air Jordan 4 Taupe Haze. Premium, buttery suede is used for most of the upper, with brown hues completely covering the Taupe Haze Jordan 4. Black rubber accents are used throughout to emphasise the colour palette used. You can find the Jumpman logo on both the heel of the sneakers and the shoe's tongues. Underfoot, a classic Air Jordan 4 sole unit features in black and white. This unit houses Nike Air technology that we know guarantees comfort. The air bubble is again visible, a tribute to the legendary Tinker Hatfield design. The Jordan 4 Taupe Haze is going to be one of the best sneaker releases we see all year, do not miss your chance to own a pair.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Burgundy Dusty Pink Womens

data.description: An autumn-ready Jordan with endless styling potential, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Burgundy Dusty Pink Womens utilises premium fabrics, instantly recognisable branding and world-famous Air cushioning to deliver a sneaker that you’ll never want to take off. Up top, panels of plush suede in varying shades of pink steal the show, while Nike’s iconic Swoosh adds a point of contrast. Jordan Brand’s signature Wings logo sits on the ankle and, of course, no Jordan 1 would be complete without Michael Jordan’s Jumpman on the tongue. Underfoot, an Air unit delivers bounce and comfort both on and off the court, while the lace-up fastening lets you control the fit.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Crimson Tint Gs

data.description: Solid black always looks great when it combines soft suede-effect panelling with premium leather, and this pair of Air Jordan 1 Low Crimson Tint GS brings classic black style with a pop of colour. While the body of the sneaker is made up of seamless black moving from the side panels into the laces, eyelet panel, and tongue, this is contrasted boldly by a Nike Swoosh in a soft shade of pink crimson premium leather. The Air Jordan 1 Low Crimson Tint GS is a timeless Jordan sneaker that’s showing off its ability to combine dark with light in effective design. This sneaker is a celebration of colour-blocking, with layered black panels giving the shoe a sophisticated edge. The must-have Air Jordan Wings logo is stamped in bold black on the heel against the pink crimson leather, making the Air Jordan 1 Low Crimson Tint GS a highly sought after addition to the iconic Jordans collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Washed Pink Ps

data.description: Accented with soft pink hues, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Washed Pink PS also boasts vintage-inspired aesthetics. Crafted with a perforated toe box for ventilation, its leather base features suede overlays, sidewall Swooshes and Jordan branding. The yellowed Air midsole offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and padding in its collar adds extra cushioning. Fastened with a secure lace closure, elevate your kid’s everyday looks with the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Washed Pink PS.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Court Purple

data.description: The most famous and influential silhouette from the Jumpman brands extensive portfolio is unquestionably the Air Jordan 1. Not only their oldest, but also their most revered shoe, one that continues to impress year on year, and going into another new decade, representing the brand is the Air Jordan 1 High Court Purple. Building on the success of their "Purple Toe" aesthetic, this upcoming offering breaks up its colours with a white toe box and keeps its purple hues more consistent on the forefoot overlays for a clean look

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 95 Neon Grey Se

data.description: There is something about some sneakers that get our blood pumping just a little faster, and here at Laced, it’s the Air Jordan 4 95 Grey SE sneakers. Grey styling is contrasted by the pop of yellow, and that Air Max sole is just calling out for someone to take them to the courts for a game of hoops. Don’t be fooled by the funky look of these sneakers; they draw on the classic Air Jordan 4 95 design and give full credence to the legendary honour that they were. The innovative design pushed performance from runners and basketball players alike, and all in a silhouette that is classic and construction that is supportive and superior when it comes to comfort levels. If you're looking for a dependable sneaker for any situation, the Air Jordan 4 95 Neon Grey SE could well be perfect for you.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Flyease Gym Red

data.description: Boasting a bold colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Low FlyEase Gym Red is fastened with a wraparound zip closure for an easy on and off. Also featuring adjustable straps for added support, its leather upper is decorated with sidewall Swooshes and Jordan branding. The Air-cushioned midsole offers comfort, the textured outsole provides grip and perforations on its toe box allows for ventilation. Buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 Low FlyEase Gym Red with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Pure Money

data.description: Revamping the 2006 original, The Air Jordan 4 Retro Pure Money dropping 11 years later in May 2017 looks to breath new life into a truly OG colourway dressed on one of the Jumpman brands most important silhouettes to date. As the name would suggest, the ‘Pure Money’ colourway is about exuberance and luxury. It doesn’t take on the dollar bill green colourway but opts for something a little more refined. Featuring a white leather upper with a white rubber sole, chrome eyelets, a chrome Jumpman on the heel, and ‘Pure$’ on the inside of the back tabs. This colourway is essentially a triple white with bling. The chrome details at first glance might make someone think you've got diamonds for your high tops, and this shoes slick appeal is sure to see the 'Pure Money' carry hype through the majority of the year.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Space Jam

data.description: Taking on an iconic colourway inspired by the Space Jam film series, the Air Jordan Mid SE Space Jam is crafted with premium materials. Featuring a perforated toe box for ventilation, its leather base is decorated with patent overlays and subtle branding. The Air midsole offers comfort, the icy rubber outsole provides grip and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Finished with padding in its collar, the Air Jordan Mid SE Space Jam is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Stealth French Blue Womens

data.description: The minimal Air Jordan 1 Low Stealth French Blue Womens updates a Micheal Jordan-designed basketball classic with stylish simplicity. Its smooth white leather base features a perforated toe box and is decorated with cool-toned grey overlays. A French Blue shade washes over the collar, heel and sidewall Swoosh to complete this AJ1’s three-toned design. The versatile sneaker is also adorned with a white embroidered Wings logo on the heel and a tonal blue Jumpman on the nylon tongue. Effortless to style thanks to its understated colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Low Stealth French Blue Womens will elevate any outfit with its timelessly trendy charm.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Lightning 2021 Ps

data.description: Aptly named, the Air Jordan 4 Retro Lightning 2021 PS arrives in a colourway that blends vibrant yellow hues with light grey accents. A 2021 reissue of the 2006 classic, this particular rendition is built for kids and crafted from almost entirely smooth nubuck on the upper, with a few hints of premium leather that accent the overall shape and design. Rounded off with instantly recognisable branding, the 4's signature Wings logo is rendered in a dark grey finish that really pops against the majority yellow composition. Jumpman branding adorns the tongue and heel overlay, while the mid-top itself rides on a white foam midsole and grey rubber outsole, perfect for the hardwood.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Obsidian

data.description: Durable and timeless, the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Obsidian ticks every box for sneakers. Like its low-top AJ1 equivalent, this cool high-top features a mix of smooth and patent leather, soft suede, and rough textile. The colours are just as diverse as the materials, as it features a navy blue, ocean blue, and light grey colourway. The statement elements are the shiny patent leather toe box and Nike Swoosh on the sidewall, which accentuate the softness of the plush tongue with exposed foam and the suede heel tab. The white midsole breaks up the dark hues and complements the white laces. Don't forget to turn down the lights to watch the reflective grey insole Jumpman, eyestay, and heel tab glow in the dark.

fields.name: Air Jordan 2 Lucky Green

data.description: Crafted with premium materials, the Air Jordan 2 Lucky Green is elevated with vibrant touches. Featuring perforations which allow for ventilation, its layered leather upper is decorated with a TPU heel overlay and Jordan branding. The off-white Air midsole offers comfort, the textured rubber outsole provides grip and padding in the collar adds extra cushioning. Refresh your rotation with the Air Jordan 2 Lucky Green.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Hare

data.description: Inspired by Bugs Bunny himself, and dropping in celebration of the release of the highly anticipated Space Jam 2 set to star NBA sensation LeBron James. Bringing back this iconic colourway, this shoe is both a perfect homage to both a legendary cult classic film for fans of shooting hoops, and one of the Jordan brand's most iconic silhouettes. Featuring an ultra premium tumbled leather construction, painted in a grey and white colour palette as a reference to the beloved cartoon character's fur coat. The much appreciated and needed accent comes in the form of vivid red accents which brace the throat for a striking pop of contrast. Along the laces you'll find a rugged toggle switch that bears a striking resemblance to a carrot, and down below, the midsole has been infused with Air tech for an insane amount of comfort both on and off the court.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 X Psg White Neutral Grey Bordeaux Gs

data.description: This Grade School model of this stylish Air Jordan 4 x PSG White Neutral Grey Bordeaux GS sneaker offers the maximum in comfort and style for smaller feet. This sneaker shows off a clean white upper in premium leather, layered against white mesh on the sides and to the front of the shoe. The white is balanced with pops of playful purple, shown on the rubber midsole, perforated eyestays, and the heel leather tab. Across the side mesh panels is draped a black cage-effect strap, while the black continues for the rubber outer soler, offering height and comfort with every step. Also included on the Air Jordan 4 x PSG White Neutral Grey Bordeaux GS' sole is a visible Air Unit to the rear. The white collar and tongue are also given a tumbled leather finish for added texture, and the heel, side, and tongue include Nike and PSG branding.

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Gratitude Ps

data.description: Unveiling the Air Jordan 11 Gratitude PS, a pair that honours the Jordan legacy. It boasts a premium leather, while the glossy patent-leather mudguard pays homage to the original. Completing the look is the gold Jumpman, symbolising the pair's championship heritage. Cushioned with a white foam midsole and grounded by a see-through rubber sole, the Air Jordan 11 Gratitude PS is the perfect mix of timelessness and comfort for your little one.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Dark Concord

data.description: Updating the ‘80s basketball classic, the Air Jordan 1 Low Dark Concord sports a Lakers-inspired colourway. Its leather upper is complete with a perforated toe box for ventilation and is decorated with Swoosh detailing as well as Jordan branding. Underfoot, the Air midsole offers comfort and the rubber outsole allows for grip. Padding in the collar adds extra cushioning and the secure lace closure means for a tailored fit. Buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 Low Dark Concord with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Origin Story

data.description: The very same kicks worn by Miles Morales in the animated film 'Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse' the December 2018 release of the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Origin Story pays homage to the pair from the newly released film with the design mirrors excellently the updated Chicago colourway that stars, and with an icy translucent rubber outsole and a subtle pattern of reflective dots across the shoe's red leather overlays, this shoe oozes cool. The Jordan Brand excellently imbues the aesthetic of the Marvel's titular web-slinging comic book hero into this reworked Jordan 1 Chicago. My Spidey Senses are tingling with this one, and I predict this shoe to be an overwhelming success, because after all, who doesn't like Marvel?

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Zen Master

data.description: A cheerful take on 1989’s Air Jordan 4, the Air Jordan 4 Zen Master utilises industry-leading technology, eye-catching hues and instantly recognisable branding to deliver a sneaker that’s full of personality. The fabric upper boasts a pastel tie-dye print, with a grey mudguard added for a point of contrast. A secure lace-up fastening lets you create a fit that feels practically customised, while Michael Jordan’s Jumpman branding graces the tongue and heel. Underfoot, Tinker Hatfield’s legendary Air unit offers bounce, while evenly distributing your weight from heel to forefoot for stability. A must-have for spring, get your hands on the Air Jordan 4 Zen Master now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Panda

data.description: Sporting an iconic two-toned colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Low Panda puts a premium twist on the retro basketball model. Featuring a perforated toe box for ventilation, its leather upper comes detailed with sidewall Swooshes, Jordan branding and tonal topstitching. The Air-cushioned midsole offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Add the versatile Air Jordan 1 Low Panda to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Concord White Black

data.description: Taking inspiration from the Air Jordan 11 Concord, the Air Jordan 1 Low Concord White Black puts a modern twist on the ‘80s basketball model. Its leather base is decorated with patent overlays, Jordan branding and sidewall Swooshes. The Air midsole underfoot offers comfort, the icy translucent outsole provides grip and perforations on its toe box allow for ventilation. Fastened with a secure lacing system, add the Air Jordan 1 Low Concord White Black to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Black White Grey Gs

data.description: When considering a classic style of sneaker, not only does the Air Jordan 1 provide a timeless silhouette, but when using shades of black, white, and grey, you know you can’t go wrong. No matter what you’re styling the Air Jordan 1 Low Black White Grey GS with, this colour palette and silhouette are ready-made for anything. The black is shown in deep, bold shades, the white crisp and clean, and the grey as sleek as ever, presented on the Nike Swoosh displayed boldly against white leather panelling. The Air Jordan 1 Low Black White Grey GS sneaker provides a more chunky design which means balance, comfort, and durability at all times, whether on the streets or on the court. These minimalistic and sophisticated shades work seamlessly together throughout the shoe, with stylish panelling, lacing, and design. Comfort and style combine at the supportive ankle panel with an attractive grey bordering.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Dark Teal

data.description: If you’re a fan of the classic blue and white combination for your pair of Air Jordan 1s, then you may want to try the Air Jordan 1 Low Dark Teal colourway. This deeper shade of blue adds a richer tone to the sneaker, whether on the courts or on the streets, and the low silhouette means a versatile sneaker fit for any occasion. The Air Jordan logo is stamped on the heel panel in white, while the clean white panelling also continues to the sides, midsole, and toe tab of the Air Jordan 1 Low Dark Teal. This dark shade of teal is shown off again with the Nike Swoosh on the side, and a flash of dark teal is guaranteed to make an impression with every step of the Air Jordan 1 Dark Teal Low sneaker.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Arctic Pink Gum Womens

data.description: If you're looking for a dependable and versatile sneaker, then nothing works better than the Air Jordan 1 Low Arctic Pink Gum Womens, easily paired with any outfit or style. This playful pair of women's sneakers shows off a soft shade of arctic pink throughout the entirety of the premium leather upper for a seamless design. The refreshing shade of pink is broken only by the clean white Nike Swoosh along the leather side panels, as well as the embroidered white Nike Air Wings logo on the heel tab. Offering a variation of the clean white midsole common with Air Jordans is the orange-brown gum midsole and outer sole, a hue that works effortlessly with the refreshing shade of pink found across the Womens Air Jordan 1 Low Arctic Pink Gum. The laces come in a matching shade of soft pink to provide a consistent upper built for style and comfort, making every pair of Air Jordan 1 Low Arctic Pink Gum Womens a joy to wear, regardless of the occasion.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Cmft 2 University Blue

data.description: Showcasing updated sneaker technology, the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom CMFT 2 University Blue refreshes the retro basketball sneaker. Its mesh base is layered with premium suede panelling, Jordan branding and cut-out Swooshes. Underfoot, Zoom Air cushioning offers comfort and its rubber outsole provides grip. Complete with classic laces and a perforated toe box, shop the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom CMFT 2 University Blue with Laced now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Hemp White

data.description: Enjoy a fresh white look in classic Low silhouette, with accents of warm orange-brown with the brand new Air Jordan 1 Low Hemp White. The upper is made of an even mix of white and brown panels, which work together seamlessly, while the Nike Swoosh is given a fresh take displayed in white on colour. The rubber midsole of the Air Jordan 1 Low Hemp White remains white, while the outer sole continues the hemp beige colour theme. The cushioned sole is built for comfort and durability, meaning a sleek sneaker that not only looks great but feels great, too. The tongue, eyelet panel, and laces on the Air Jordan 1 Low Hemp White work together in one matching shade of deeper gold-brown, while the Jumpman logo stands out in white. The Air Wings logo follows the same colour on the white heel panel, and a perforated toe box comes in beige hemp for the ultimate finish.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Black Chile Red White

data.description: If you’re looking for a bold Nike swoosh to grab attention, then nothing better than an eye-catching red. Set against sleek black leather, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Black Chile Red White makes for a sophisticated sneaker with a touch of flair. Coupled with crisp white leather, this mid Air Jordan is for fans of the classic Nike design with an edge. These timeless sneakers are designed with expert airflow for comfort, with a leather dress upper and padded shape. The Air Jordan 1 Mid Black Chile Red Whites provide superior comfort with a cushioned sole and offer a striking design with both subtle tones and a bright red touch of personality. Get your hands on one of the most distinctive sneakers on the market whilst enjoying a pair of shoes that’ll pair well with any outfit.

fields.name: Air Jordan 36 Blue Ribbon Sports Clear Sole

data.description: Boasting a colourway reminiscent of the “Sport Blue” AJ6, the Air Jordan 36 Blue Ribbon Sports Clear Sole presents a basketball shoe with futuristic flair. Its mesh upper allows for ventilation and is decorated with Jordan branding and TPU accents. Zoom Air cushioning delivers comfort, the secure lace closure means for a tailored fit and the translucent outsole provides grip. Finished with pull tabs for an easy on and off, the Air Jordan 36 Blue Ribbon Sports Clear Sole is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Japan Midnight Navy

data.description: After the monumental success of the recent Jordan 1 High Neutral Grey, we are ecstatic to see the Air Jordan 1 Midnight Navy colourway receive a release date. The sneaker initially released back in 2001 as a Japan-exclusive. Fortunately for us all, the shoe is finally seeing a wider release. Premium white leathers are complimented perfectly by the midnight navy suede panels. The iconic swoosh is also emphasised due to the contrasting grey suede used—the premium materials used throughout back up the hype that surrounds this silhouette. The ankle of the shoe features the legendary wings logo, a signature piece for the Jordan 1. The tongues branding has the Nike Air logo, giving the Air Jordan 1 Japan Navy sneaker an, even more, OG vibe. Underfoot, we see the Nike Air technology run across the entire sole. This feature ensures you have optimum comfort, whether on the court or the streets. A black outsole completes the look, making this one of the most impressive Jordan's to release in recent times. A must-cop for sneakerheads around the globe, the Jordan 1 High Japan Midnight Navy will be an instant hit.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Seafoam High Og Womens

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 High is one of the greatest sneakers ever to release. Initially meant to be Michael Jordan's exclusive signature basketball silhouette, the AJ1 has quickly become a must-have lifestyle shoe. The upcoming Jordan 1 Seafoam Orange is guaranteed to turn the heads of collectors with its eye-catching aesthetics. Premium leather underlays come dressed in white, with Seafoam green hues covering the legendary paneling. Iconic branding can be found throughout, with Nike Swoosh detailing featuring across the lateral and medial sides of the Air Jordan 1 Seafoam sneaker and the OG Wings logo on the shoe's collar. Underfoot the Jordan 1 High Seafoam, a traditional Jordan 1 sole unit compliments the uppers perfectly, with a white midsole and green outsole. This sole unit houses Nike Air technology offering unparalleled comfort wear after wear.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Varsity Red Td

data.description: Start your mini-me’s collection off on the right foot with the bold Air Jordan 1 High OG Varsity Red TD. Its smooth white leather base is dressed in bright red overlays as well as a soft chenille-textured sidewall Swoosh. The grey-hued ankle panel is complemented by a matching cord-style tongue which is accented with a woven Nike-branded label. Signature Air cushioning in the midsole and a breathable perforated toe box will allow your kid to rock this scaled-down basketball classic all day long with ease. Finished with an iconic Wings logo stamped onto the collar, the Air Jordan 1 High OG Varsity Red TD is the perfect shoe for even the fussiest of little ones.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Reverse Yellow Toe Gs

data.description: Give your child’s wardrobe a stylish update with the Air Jordan 1 Mid Reverse Yellow Toe GS sneakers. The 2022 iteration is influenced by the 1985 Black Toe style that features the same colour scheme. The timeless Air Jordan 1 mid-top sneakers will stand out on your child’s feet, thanks to the university gold-yellow overlay and outsole. The vibrant shade is a stark contrast to the black toe box, sock liner, laces, and Nike Swooshes on the medial and lateral sides. Also, you cannot miss the black Jumpman on the university gold yellow tongue tab, and the black Air Jordan wings pop against the vibrant collar.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro Raging Bulls Red 2021

data.description: After a monumental 2020, Jordan Brand look to make 2021 just as iconic when it comes to re-releasing iconic silhouettes. The Raging Bull Air Jordan 5 released way back in 2009 originally and is one of the silhouette's legendary colourways. The uppers are crafted from buttery suede throughout, with a Raging Bull red hue used for the sneaker's colourway. Black accents complement the legendary design, with the Jumpman logo on the heel contrasting the shoe's upper. MJ's jersey number, 23, features on the sneaker's heels finishing the upper's design. Underfoot, a black sole unit houses Nike Air technology which guarantees comfort wear after wear. The shark tooth design across the midsole features, whilst a partly translucent outsole shows off another Jumpman logo. The Raging Bull Jordan 5 is as legendary as it comes, be sure to add this sneaker to your collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Fierce Pink Gs

data.description: Sporting a vibrant pink design, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Fierce Pink GS puts a modern spin on the ‘80s basketball icon. Its layered leather upper is accented with Jordan emblems and sidewall Swooshes. Perforations on its toe box allow for ventilation, Air cushioning underfoot offers comfort and its rubber outsole provides grip. Complete with a classic lacing system, add the Air Jordan 1 Mid Fierce Pink GS to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Stage Haze

data.description: Texture is the name of the game with the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Stage Haze. The upper is crafted from a mix of smooth leather, cracked leather and supple suede, while Nike’s Swoosh logo sits on the sidewalls for instant brand recognition. Jordan’s Wings motif steals the show on the ankle, and breathable perforations on the toe box allow air to flow freely around the foot to keep you cool. Easy to style thanks to the clean grey, white and black colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Stage Haze promises to pair with everything in your new-season wardrobe.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Se Black Canvas Gs

data.description: Update your collection with the Air Jordan 4 Retro SE Black Canvas GS. Available in GS sizes, the 2022 iteration provides the legacy silhouette with a cool new update, proving why it has been a popular choice among sneaker fans since 1989. The black canvas, suede overlay, and ventilated netting on the quarter adds texture to the iconic design. The all-black colourway is broken up with a light grey midsole and molded eyelet tabs. Also, you can trust the sneakers will feel instantly comfortable due to the visible Air-Sole cushioning in the midsole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Chile Red Gs

data.description: Add a touch of spice to your sneaker game with a flash of bright Chile red in this Air Jordan’s Nike Swoosh. With an otherwise more minimalistic design in white and black leather, this Air Jordan 1 Mid Chile Red GS sneaker is perfect for those who like classic design with a subtle twist of colour that celebrates the Chicago Bulls colour theme. The Air Jordan Wings logo is here displayed boldly in a stamp of black against white leather. The black outer sole adds the perfect border to the overall silhouette, while the white midsole allows the contrast to pop. A white leather heel panel hugs the back of the feet, while black laces stand out perfectly against a white eyelet panel. Ready made for smaller feet, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Chile Red GS is an attractive sneaker in iconic design built to last.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Curry Cardinal Red

data.description: Treat yourself to the striking Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Curry Cardinal Red, a balanced design that will add streetwear flair to any outfit. A smooth white leather base with peach-toned beige overlays makes up the majority of its upper, whilst a vibrant red Swoosh interrupts the otherwise neutral shoe’s sidewall. Dressed with matching red laces, collar panel and embossed Wings logo, its white Air-cushioned midsole is grounded with a bold black outsole. Crafted with a breathable perforated toe box to add to its reliable levels of comfort, this Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Curry Cardinal Red is the contrasting pair that your collection needs.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro Low Expression Womens

data.description: Laced with stylish versatility, the understated Air Jordan 5 Retro Low Expression Womens updates a ‘90s silhouette with an arty edge. The soft beige suede overlays which form its upper are decorated with a brown camo-style print to craft this creative pair with unique depth. An incorporated mesh panel features in the sidewall to allow for all-important ventilation which keeps the foot cool. Embroidered black Jumpman logos also sit on the tongue and heel to add a layer of branding to the muted sneaker. The classic AJ5 midsole takes on a matching off-white hue and is complete with a visible Air unit in its heel to ground it in complete comfort. Finished with a custom lace toggle, the Air Jordan 5 Retro Low Expression Womens is not one to be missed.

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Retro Jubilee Gs

data.description: Nothing beats the classic silhouette of the Air Jordan 11, and this pair of Air Jordan 11 Retro Jubilee GS is here to celebrate the 25th Jubilee anniversary of this stunning sillhouette. The Air Jordan 11 Retro Jubilee GS is constructed with solid monochrome black on the upper shoe, providing a seamless finish that looks and feels classy and comfortable. The shoe’s design continues with a highly traditional blend of mesh and leather, an iconic staple of the Air Jordan 11. The glossy black touch against the matte monochrome makes for a truly elegant piece, separating blacks with different fabric finishes, and all completed with subtle accents of white on the lace eyelets. A silver metallic Jordan Jumpman adorns the heel of the Air Jordan 11 Retro Jubilee GS in a style that speaks of silver birthday celebrations but also one which remains sophisticated and elegant for years to come. The comfortable white foam sole provides support and balance.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Infrared Ps

data.description: For this standout pair of sneakers, you have the incomparable retro vibes provided by the Air Jordan 4 silhouette paired with a deep and bold colourway in black, grey, and red. The Air Jordan 4 Retro Infrared PS' premium upper focuses on panels of matte leather, which are layered for a fuller look. This begins with a panel of light grey wrapping around the toe, moving to a darker grey for the curved panel above, for the eyestay panel, and around the collar, before switching to a black mesh fabric for the centre feature and at the bottom of the lacing strip. To the heel of the Air Jordan 4 Retro Infrared PS, you have a black strap accessory connecting to bright red eyestay additions and black laces for bold contrast. To the sole, black mudguard strips are included against a white rubber mid and a soft grey outer.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf Triple White

data.description: Nothing can beat a retro sneaker with timeless white styling; a versatile design guaranteed to work with any look, any place. For this pair of Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf Triple White sneakers in low shaping, you have a white tumbled leather finish for the premium upper, running from toe to heel. The toe box comes with a perforated panel for extra breathability and comfort, while the side of the Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf Triple White sneaker is adorned with a tumbled leather Nike Swoosh in matching white. The heel tab, eyestay panel, and tongue are all white, as are the fresh white laces. For the sole, built for maximum comfort and traction no matter where you wear them, you have a fresh white mid and a white rubber outer to complete the refreshing minimalistic look.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey

data.description: Translating the overwhelming appeal of the Dior custom to a more widespread audience, the Air Jordan 1 Mid ‘Light Smoke Grey’, which is set to drop in Spring 2020 is considered the prime base for one of the most luxury customs seen from the Jordan brand in quite some time. Aesthetically you can almost make a shot for shot comparison with its higher end counterpart and it is a comparison this more affordable model embraces with open arms. The colour palette of the Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey remains unchanged, dressing the white base with Light Smoke Grey overlays and crisp panelling. Elsewhere on the Jordan 1 Mid Smoke Grey, swooshes are struck with matte black in match to the darkened laces, lining, and staple Wings insignia, giving the Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey a truly breathtaking finish.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Berry Pink Womens

data.description: Black and white are guaranteed to look good on any pair of Air Jordans, no matter what you pair them with, and this pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid Berry Pink Womens sneakers shows off the power of pink with a soft nubuck finish along the premium upper. The Air Jordan 1 silhouette shows off a perforated white toe box and a white main mid-panel. Overlaid across is a sweeping Nike Swoosh in black, while the black continues for the rear collar panel and on the printed Air Jordan Wings logo shown on the ankle strap. The rest of the upper's panelling reveals a soft nubuck finish in berry pink, which is also revealed on the rubber outer sole. The black laces help the pink on the Women's Air Jordan 1 Mid Berry Pink sneaker to pop, while the white tongue and the white rubber midsole add a fresh addition to the colourway.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Hyper Royal Gs

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid is a sneaker that isn't a stranger to the shade of legendary royal blue, and with the Air Jordan 1 Mid Hyper Royal GS it mixes with bold black for a colourway that never goes out of fashion. The premium leather is constructed from panels of black on the sides, front, and collar, while the rest of the upper is made of a sleek and bold royal blue hue. The Nike Swoosh works seamlessly into the Air Jordan 1 Mid Hyper Royal GS design in the same shade of blue, while the Air Jordan Wings logo contrasts neatly in black on the blue ankle strap. Black laces against a royal blue eyelet panel create a neat contrast, while a fresh white midsole mixed with a black outer completes the look. This iconic Air Jordan 1 Mid Hyper Royal GS variation means the ideal sneaker for a narrower, smaller fit.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Spruce Aura White

data.description: Subtle and sublime, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Spruce Aura White drops as a women's exclusive, determined to make a splash for Spring/Summer 2020. Dressed from heel to toe in a colour palette so delicately chosen, as a passing glance you'd struggle to decipher the contrast, but look a little closer and you'll see a delightful coupling of pastel lime and chalk white. Made from luxe materials accompanied by soft suede this particular model is finished off with an Air-Sole cushioning within the tonal midsole, so you can not only look good but feel good too, whether you’re on the courts or the streets.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Court Purple 2.0 Gs

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Court Purple 2.0 GS is another attractive colourway in a deep shade of court purple coupled with white and black accents. This is a bold design suited for any place, any season, with cushioned Nike comfort with every step. The upper of the Air Jordan 1 Court Purple 2.0 GS is crafted from fine, sleek leather and tumbled-effect panels. The heel tab, eyelet panel, side-front, and ankle strap are all adorned with the rich plum shade. This is contrasted by a sleek white side panel and perforated toe box, with a narrower Nike Swoosh sitting on the side in black. The Air Jordan Wings logo, as well as the laces, mould subtly into the design in black within the deep purple panelling, and a fresh white midsole strip adds contrast and height to this popular variation.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low White Camo Gs

data.description: The classic Air Jordan 1 Low White Camo GS silhouette comes in muted shades of white and grey for a sleek and elegant look that never goes out of style. A more minimalistic sneaker, the Air Jordan 1 Low White Camo GS nevertheless still includes unique design elements to set this sneaker apart, most notably with the grey camo Nike Swoosh on the side. The majority of the upper is crafted from tumbled grey leather, offset by a smooth white fabric side panel and a white leather perforated toe box. Black is included on the heel Air Jordan Wings logo and the tongue logo, while the rest of the Air Jordan 1 Low White Camo GS sneaker incorporates white and grey. A grey outer sole adds a flash of colour to the bottom of the shoe, offset by the cushioned white midsole, and white laces allow the sleek silver-grey tongue and eyelet panel to pop.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Mmd Gs

data.description: This playful and vibrant Air Jordan 1 Low MMD GS sneaker provides loud fabric patterns for a standout look for those lovers of the bold and the brave. In classic Air Jordan 1 low styling, this sneaker begins with a square-patterned leather panel wrapping around the toe in black and pink. The perforated toe box then comes in clean white before switching to a squared-patterned panel in blue and black for the side front panels. The main mid panels show off fresh white in smooth leather, complete with coral pink Nike Swoosh, whose tail sweeps over the heel panel of yellow and black check design. The heel is also complete with a white Air Jordan Wings logo, while the panel above shows a white and black check design. Adding yet more colour are the bright yellow laces and the blue rubber outer sole, completing the look of the Air Jordan 1 Low MMD GS.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Frozen Moments Womens

data.description: Named after a Nike advert from 1996 which encapsulated what it was like to watch Michael Jordan play, the Air Jordan 4 Retro Frozen Moments Womens puts a premium twist on the classic AJ4. Featuring suede and leather panelling, its upper also showcases grid mesh panelling and silver accents. Air technology in its midsole offers comfort, its rubber outsole provides grip and secure laces round off the design. Shop the Air Jordan 4 Retro Frozen Moments Womens with Laced now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Og Neutral Grey 2021 Womens

data.description: If you’re looking for a stylish, minimalistic sneaker, then the classic shape of the Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG Neutral Grey 2021 Womens is what you’re looking for. This pair of sneakers also comes in a neutral and fresh palette of white and soft grey, which means a simple sneaker with a dash of colour, fit for any occasion. This Womens Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG Neutral Grey 2021 sneaker gives an altogether retro feel with its classic design, shade, and stitching pattern along the shoe. The Nike Swoosh is made up of soft grey suede, which is also continued on the heel tab, complete with Air Jordan Wings logo. The subtle grey addition continues on the outer sole, with a balanced and cushioned white midsole to offer maximum comfort every time. White laces complete the neutral look, while front toe cap air holes mean breathability with every step.

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Low Yellow Snakeskin Womens

data.description: Putting a premium twist on the retro basketball silhouette, the Air Jordan 11 Low Yellow Snakeskin Womens features faux snakeskin panelling. Its leather base is further decorated with stripped-back Jordan branding and elongated lace loops. Air cushioning in the midsole offers comfort, the textured outsole provides grip and padding in its collar adds extra support. Rounded off with a speed lacing system, add the Air Jordan 11 Low Yellow Snakeskin Womens to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Chicago Lost And Found Gs

data.description: Big kids can now get their hands on the Air Jordan 1 High OG Chicago Lost and Found GS colourway, which is one of the most popular iterations of all time. Released in 2022, this unique version of the much-loved sneaker has a white cracked leather upper, creating an aged aesthetic that will make people question if you've pulled them from a dusty attic. Complementing the crisp white leather upper are the crimson red overlays and black Nike Swooshes on the lateral and medial sidewalls. Other signature elements give the sneakers a stamp of approval, including a red and white Nike Air tongue tag and a black Jordan Wings logo on the red ankle flap. Adding to the vintage aesthetic is a faux oxidised effect across the crimson red rubber outsole. You can keep the sneakers in excellent condition throughout the years by storing them inside the special edition, pre-distressed box, which includes a sales receipt with a marked-down price.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low White Wolf Grey Womens

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 is, without a doubt, one of the most iconic sneakers of all time. Initially shooting to fame thanks to Michael Jordan's incredible career, the AJ1 is an absolute must-cop for sneakerheads. The latest Air Jordan 1 Low White Wolf Grey offering from Jordan is one of the cleanest colourways we have seen yet. The Air Jordan 1 Low White Wolf Grey draws clear inspiration from the much talked about Dior x Air Jordan 1. The uppers come crafted from premium leather throughout, with white underlays contrasted by wolf grey panels. The iconic Nike Swoosh features down both lateral and medial sides of the shoe, whilst the heel features the OG wings logo. A white midsole can be found at the bottom of the Jordan 1 Low White Wolf Grey, housing the Nike Air technology that makes the Air Jordan 1 so comfortable. An icy, translucent outsole completes the White Wolf Grey design.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Gorge Green

data.description: Updating an ‘80s basketball silhouette, the Air Jordan 1 High OG Gorge Green features colour blocking that’s reminiscent of previous AJ1 iterations. Its pebbled leather base is decorated with green leather overlays, classic Nike branding and a Wings logo. Air cushioning in the midsole delivers comfort, the perforated toe box allows for ventilation and the rubber outsole provides effective grip. Fastened with a secure lacing system, buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 High OG Gorge Green with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low New Emerald Womens

data.description: Refresh your collection with the two-tone Air Jordan 1 Low New Emerald Womens, an updated ‘80s basketball silhouette that will elevate any outfit. Its smooth white leather base is dressed in turquoise-toned green overlays and a matching sidewall Swoosh. An iconic Jumpman logo sits proudly on the nylon tongue, whilst an embroidered white Wings logo decorates the heel. The crisp white midsole is reinforced with reliable Air cushioning and is grounded by a textured tonal green outsole which allows for all-important grip both on and off the court. Complete with a perforated toe box for optimal ventilation, the modern Air Jordan 1 Low New Emerald Womens will become your new go-to.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og X Travis Scott Mocha

data.description: Featuring a fresh take on the timeless Air Jordan 1, and granted a surprise release in February 2019 the Travis Scott x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Mocha' attempts to go against the grain with this new school creation. The deviation from the norm comes in no small thanks to an oversized backwards-facing Swoosh on the lateral side of the Jordan 1 Travis Scott Retro High while a traditionally oriented Swoosh graces the medial side of the upper, which is built with a blend of white leather and brown suede. Fittingly nicknamed 'Mocha' this blend of brown and white is one of the most interesting takes on the Air Jordan 1 to date. Travis Scott is in no small way elevating his status as one of the most influential contributors to the trainer meta at the moment, and with each release being as easily anticipated as that of Kanye or Virgil I'm predicted a lot more to come from La Flame.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Craft Inside Out White Grey

data.description: Lovers of pastel colours and timeless style will want this pair of Air Jordan 1 Low Craft Inside Out White Grey sneakers for their wardrobe. The premium upper in classic low height comes with layered panels of varying soft colours for a playful finish. Light taupe is shown on the perforated toe box panel, the front side straps, the lower heel detailing, and around the collar. This is paired with clean white around the toe and the main mid-panel. A soft grey is shown in nubuck for the eyestay strip and for the heel tab, embossed with a white Air Jordan Wings logo.
