For the main ankle strap, you have a pastel grey-blue hue combined with soft pink laces on top. The side Nike Swoosh is shown in minimalistic fashion in white, including coral pink thread detail.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air Cmft 2 Grey Fire Red

data.description: Echoing the evolution of the Jordan Brand, the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air CMFT 2 Grey Fire Red delivers an updated rendition of the iconic silhouette. Utilising supple suede overlays, breathable perforations appear on the toe box and a foam tongue provides a comfortable fit. Cut-out Swooshes set this style apart from its predecessors, while Zoom Air cushioning underfoot offers all-day support. Buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air CMFT 2 Grey Fire Red with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Action Grape Womens

data.description: Boasting classic colour blocking inspired by OG AJ1 designs, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Action Grape Womens will never fail to impress. Its smooth leather upper is accented with purple-hued overlays, Jordan logos and sidewall Swooshes. Perforations on its toe box allow air to flow around the foot, Air cushioning in its foam midsole offers all-day comfort and its rubber outsole provides grip. Fastened with a secure lace closure, add the Air Jordan 1 Mid Action Grape Womens to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Craft Olive Gs

data.description: Style and comfort unite in the Air Jordan 4 Craft Olive GS. These sneakers are a fusion of layered nubuck and suede, in a khaki green colourway. The collar is lined with sleek black fabric, matching the eyelets and leather support wings. These shoes offer stability with a white foam midsole and a rubber outsole, featuring a herringbone pattern. Adding a dash of sophistication, the off-white Jumpman logos on the tongue and semi-transparent tab at the back elevate the look. Stylish path to comfort and sophistication with the Air Jordan 4 Craft Olive GS.

A black Swoosh adorns the sidewall with a touch of signature branding which works alongside the tonal Wings logo on the ankle and the standard Nike Air label on its tongue. Grounded by a white Air-cushioned midsole for all-day kind of comfort, the three-toned Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Yellow Toe promises to add a pop of personality to any outfit.

Versatile and timeless in equal measure, the Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Travis Scott Mocha Brown PS is easy to slot into your kid’s shoedrobe.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Cool Grey 2021 Gs

data.description: This retro Air Jordan 3 Retro Cool Grey 2021 GS sneaker combines stylish shades of stone grey with pops of bright orange for a standout finish. The premium upper shows off a block light grey finish running from the toe to the heel in tumbled leather. This then switches to a cement-patterned leather panelling in light and dark grey, which runs around the toe and across the side heel panels. This is complemented by a deeper grey panel on the heel tab, while the deeper grey continues for the perforated fabric additions running around the collar and down the eyelet panel. Pops of orange are included for the eyestays, including the extra-large eyestay at the top. For the rest of the Air Jordan 3 Retro Cool Grey 2021 GS sneaker, you have clean white laces, black mudguards, a white rubber midsole, a visible Air Unit, and a black rubber outer sole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Element Gore-Tex Sky J Purple

data.description: Introducing the Air Jordan 1 High  Element Gore-TEX Sky J Purple, a modern take on the classic Air Jordan 1 with advanced Gore-Tex weatherproofing technology which keeps your feet protected from all kinds of weather conditions. The colours are a mix of clay and tan for the base, while the overlays come in a bold Sky J Purple. The pair also have 3M reflective accents for better visibility, classic herringbone pattern laces, and the iconic Swoosh logos. Elevate your collection with the Air Jordan 1 High  Element Gore-TEX Sky J Purple.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air Comfort London

data.description: Jordan Brand looks set to release one of the best colourways we have seen in some time this week, with the Zoom Comfort London set to be a favourite amongst Jordan collectors and sneakerheads. The uppers come composed from a mix of tumbled and buttery, smooth leathers giving the silhouette an instantly elevated feel. A grey colour palette is used throughout, a similar blend of hues that Nike used for the Air Max 1 London in 2020. The Nike swoosh features across each sneaker's sides. However, it is embedded within the design rather than stitched on top of the upper. The collar of the sneaker comes in pastel pink, contrasting the minimalist upper expertly. Underfoot, a Nike Air sole unit features, dressed in a mix of cream and grey. This sole unit guarantees unbeatable support, making the Jordan 1 Zoom Comfort one of the market's comfiest shoes. The Jordan 1 London will be one of the shoes of the year, be sure to add to your collection before its too late.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Court Purple Womens

data.description: Jordan Brand returns once more with a women's exclusive Air Jordan 1 High, this time coming in an eye-catching court purple colourway. The AJ1 Court Purple features a minimalist white leather upper accentuated by pops of purple throughout. You can find the iconic Swoosh branding features across both lateral and medial sides of the shoe, whilst the Wings logo features on the sneaker's collar. You will also find the Nike Air logo on the shoe's tongue. Underfoot, Nike Air technology runs the length of the white and purple sole unit. This legendary technology guarantees unbeatable comfort whether you are wearing the silhouette on the court or the street. The Court Purple draws clear inspiration from the much anticipated Neutral Grey Air Jordan 1 released in February 2021. Fortunately, the Court Purple comes in smaller sizes giving everyone a chance to pick up a pair.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro White Midnight Navy

data.description: Nodding to the OG AJ4 design, the Air Jordan 4 Retro White Midnight Navy updates the ‘80s basketball silhouette with modern touches. The leather upper of the Jordan 4 Midnight Navy is complete with grid mesh cut-outs, speckled TPU accents and Jordan branding. Underfoot the Midnight Navy Jordan 4, the midsole is complete with an Air unit for comfort, while the rubber outsole provides grip. Padding in the collar of the Jordan 4 Retro Midnight Navy adds extra cushioning and the secure lacing system puts you in control of the fit. Guaranteed authentic and box-fresh, buy and sell the Air Jordan 4 Retro White Midnight Navy with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Black White Royal Gs

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid Black & White Royal Racer Blue is a sneaker that screams class, featuring the timeless colour combination of black, white and blue. With the perfect balance of royal blue streaks alongside contrasting white and black premium leather styling, it’s no surprise the Air Jordan 1 Mid White Black Royal GS is a firm favourite amongst fans of the classic Jordans style. The mid design comes complete with a bold white midsole and black outer sole, with air holes on the toe for breathability. With an eye-catching royal blue swoosh across the side of the shoe and iconic Jordans wings logo, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Black White Royal sneakers have it all; style, form and functionality rolled into one pair of sneakers.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Not For Resale

data.description: Released in November 2018 the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG NRG Not For Resale will be remembered for one feature which sets it apart from the rest, its use of not so hidden messages printed across the upper and midsole. They feature to embellish classic colour blocking that accents a white leather base with contrasting black overlays and a pop of Varsity Red around the collar. The phrases include ‘No Photos' embroidered across the heel of the left and right shoe, ‘Wear Me' across the tongues and ‘Please Crease' stamped on each toe box, as well as ‘Not For Resale' printed across the side of the white heel. This shoe almost seems to take inspiration from an instruction manual in its styling and definitely a playful but sly pop at the resale culture which has engulfed the trainer world, this kick is a satirical take on the way things are heading for the major brands and is clearly an acknowledgement that resale is on the up.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Comfort Aleali May Womens

data.description: Aleali May returns with her latest Jordan Brand collaboration, taking over the Air Jordan 1 Zoom Comfort and giving it a unique twist that only May can. Dubbed the Califia, the sneaker is composed of bold colour blocking, combining royal blue and green hues throughout the entire upper. The toebox, heel and swoosh detailing all feature in green, whilst royal blue panelling makes up the rest of the shoe. Aleali May A branding can be found on the shoe's tongue, whilst the extended collars give the Air Jordan 1 a contemporary look. The iconic wings logo features on the extended collar but has been replaced by a faux fur chenille material. Down below, a full-length zoom cushioned sole unit features in cream and green hues. The inclusion of this technology all but guarantees unparalleled comfort wear after wear. Aleali May is one of the most important figures within the sneaker industry; anything she touches turns to gold. Make sure to pick up a pair of the Aleali May Califia's, or you'll be sure to regret it.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Bulls

data.description: A sneaker that’s as legendary as it is iconic, the Air Jordan 1 Low Bulls was designed to pay homage to Michael Jordan’s original NBA team, the Chicago Bulls. Updating the original Peter Moore design, this latest iteration is constructed in full leather, rounded off by a mesh tongue and lining. The colour scheme includes a white base, set against shades of red on the toe cap, eyestay and Nike Swoosh. To contrast, hits of black adorn the heel, collar and laces. The supportive rubber sole delivers in durability, while lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of the encapsulated Air in the heel. Finally, this sneaker is given the Jordan stamp of approval with signature branding at the rear and atop the tongue. A negotiable must-have, make the Air Jordan 1 Low Red Bulls a mainstay in your collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Retro X Travis Scott British Khaki

data.description: Whenever Travis Scott looks set to release a new sneaker, the entire industry takes notice. The upcoming Air Jordan 6 in the British Khaki colourway is guaranteed to be an instant hit and catapult into the Sneaker of the Year debate. The sneakers upper is crafted from premium suede, with the shoe covered in the earthy khaki tone. A Travis Scott inspired design aspect is the inclusion of zip bag detailing on the inside collar of the shoe, whilst button closure bags are used on the outside collar. Jumpman logos feature on the sneaker tongue, whilst the heel features the Cactus Jack and Nike Air branding. Underfoot, Khaki and cream colourways dominate the sole unit design. This sole unit features Nike Air technology guaranteeing comfort and includes the iconic Tinker Hatfield air bubble detailing. Travis Scott is perhaps the hottest commodity in the sneaker industry today, be sure to grab a pair of the AJ6's before it's too late.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High J Balvin

data.description: Perhaps the craziest Air Jordan 1 to ever release, the J Blavin is guaranteed to turn heads. This OG version of the iconic silhouette is going to be thrown into the sneaker of the year discussion once released. The uppers come crafted from canvas materials, with the legendary Jordan panelling featuring jagged edges for a futuristic look. The cut-out edges are just one part of this bizarre design, with a rainbow colourway chosen too. J Balvin's signature smiley face logo features in place of the Nike Air logo on the shoe's tongues, whilst the swoosh still features down the lateral and medial side of the sneaker. Underfoot, Nike Air technology is housed within a powder pink sole unit. As we know, this classic technology guarantees unparalleled comfort. This shoe is going to be an instant grail for sneakerheads around the globe, be sure to add this silhouette to your rotation.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf Unc

data.description: Nothing beats the classic Air Jordan 1 Low silhouette in retro styling in bright shades of blue and white. The refreshing Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf UNC reveals a sleek matte leather upper, with light blue running around the toe, up the front side panels, along the eyelet strip and wrapping around the main heel panel. This is complemented by a matching blue leather heel tab, embroidered with a white Air Jordan Wings logo, and a swooping side Nike Swoosh in light blue. For the perforated toe box and main side panels, you have clean matte white to match the white rubber midsole. For the Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Golf UNC's rubber outer, the light blue hue returns for a striking step, while clean white on the laces allows the blue leather panels to really pop.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 White Stealth 2021

data.description: This pair of Air Jordan 5 White Stealth 2021 sneakers is the perfect example of a beloved, timeless design with updated features any Air Jordan fan will love. The comfortable and premium leather panelling is predominantly shown in clean white for a fresher look. This is joined by subtle hints of black on the tongue, as well as with the shark tooth graphic on the Air Jordan 5 White Stealth 2021 midsole. On the tongue of the shoe is the iconic Jumpman logo, included in luminescent silver fabric, and a bright dash of Royal Blue adds a pop of colour to the overall design. You can find the blue on the lining, lace eyelets, and treads. Mesh panelling is included on the sides, still in fresh white, and a grey midsole adds another dash of subtle colour. The Air unit behind the heel completes the cushioned, comfortable Air Jordan 5 White Stealth 2021 sneaker you won’t want to miss.

Timelessly trendy thanks to its white and ivory colourway, you can wear the Air Jordan 1 Mid Coconut Milk with everything.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Gs Diy

data.description: The Air Jordan 4 is one of the most iconic silhouettes to come out of the Jordan Brand. The upper comes crafted from premium leather throughout, with a crisp white hue covering the sneaker. Accents across the upper are outlined in black, designed to look like the sneaker has been drawn. Initially designed by the legendary Tinker Hatfield, the visible air bubble stars on the white midsole. The outsole finishes the design in black, giving this sneaker a sketched out appearance.

The must-have black Nike swoosh stands out boldly against the softer tones of beige, and the black bordering along the top gives it a perfectly accentuated shape to work well with any outfit. The tan-coloured sole of the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Particle Beige Womens finishes off this warm and versatile design.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid White Beige Red Gs

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Top 3

data.description: Having been initially postponed until June, the Air Jordan 5 Top 3 is now here, and looks damn good! Mixing together the Air Jordan 5s most iconic schemes, incorporating elements reminiscent of the series’ prior AJ1 or the somewhat similar “What The” AJ4. With this newly released Top 3 colourway, the pair in question takes a new lease on life by way of the past’s “Fire Red,” “Metallic,” and “Grape” notables. With vibrant hits of purple and aqua blue adding a pop of colour along the tongue and its embedded Jumpman insignia, to a mostly black dominated composition. A lightly hued sneaker that’s perfect for spring, the upper is crafted from a mix of suede, leather and mesh to deliver an on-trend multi-textured look. Perforations are added to enhance the shoe’s breathability, while hits of yellow and blue bring the design to life. Underfoot, carefully placed cushioning supports your every step, while the high-top collar hugs your ankle for the perfect fit. A must-have for any collector, add the UNION x Air Jordan 2 Retro SP Grey Fog to your everyday rotation now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 9 Fire Red

The unique sneaker design features a splash of Fire Red on its heel tab, lace eyelets, tongue, and the iconic Jumpman branding. Red accents pop against the white leather upper and grey patent leather panels along the collar and mudguard. The Jordan Brand continues to prove less is more for classic sneakers, as they have stuck with simple retro colourways that demand attention. The iconic Fire Red has previously appeared on other designs, such as Air Jordan 3, Air Jordan 4, Air Jordan 5, and many more Nike Swoosh sneakers.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Team Red

Underfoot, the Air midsole delivers comfort and the rubber outsole allows for effective grip. Buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 Mid Team Red with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 14 Retro Low Clot Terra Blush

data.description: Streetwear label CLOT look set to take over one of Michael Jordans lesser-known signature silhouettes, the AJ14. Drawing inspiration from the Terracotta Warrior statues in China, motivation is evident in this sneaker's design. The uppers are completely drenched in the dessert sand colourway, featuring across both the uppers and sole unit of the shoe. The heavy-duty upper is meant to mimic that of a warriors armour, whilst pops of orange on the midsole finish up the design. A suede toe cap gives the shoe a luxurious look, whilst you can find a slight contrast in the lighter sand coloured tongues and collars. Ferrari-inspired badges feature on the side of the shoe, too. After the amazing success of the CLOT x Air Force 1, we expect the Air Jordan 14 Terracotta to be an instant classic.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High X Spider-Man Across The Spider-Verse Red Black

Its leather and suede upper is detailed with branding as well as patterned panels inspired by the 3D elements in the movie. Perforations on the toe box allow for ventilation, the Air midsole offers comfort and the rubber outsole provides grip. Rounded off with a classic lacing system, find your size with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Turf Orange

The Air Jordan 1 Mid is a popular and iconic version of this classic sneaker, and the lifestyle-based colourway theme is continued here in shades of bright Turf Orange. The stand-out colour is highlighted in glossy panels of leather on the collar strap, heel, toe, and eyelets of the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Turf Orange, balanced out by clean and fresh white leather panels. This includes the midsole sole to finish off the silhouette and then contrasted by a sleek black outer sole. The turf orange is shown off even more by bold black laces to truly bring out this incredible colour. The black leather Nike swoosh is made more prominent by intricate orange stitching along the sides.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Light Smoke Grey

The smoky grey colour adds a touch of personality and style to a low sneaker that’s made for comfort, whether you're on the court or on the street. The Nike swoosh stands out in black against the smooth grey design of the Air Jordan 1 Low Light Smoke Grey, and a touch of boldness is added in subtle shades of red to the back and tongue of this exceptional sneaker. This one is for fans of subtle colour and classic design combined, with a low design and black laces which are offset perfectly by the shades of grey. Comfort meets shades of subtle colour with the popular Air Jordan 1 Low Light Smoke Grey.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement Gs

Its leather upper features grid mesh panelling, Jordan branding and TPU accents. The Air unit in its midsole offers comfort, its rubber outsole provides grip and classic laces round off the design. fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Rage Green

Of course, that is not the case, and what it actually is, is a kick started by the Jumpman’s FEARLESS ONES campaign from Autumn 2019. Dressed in a similar colour blocking as 2007’s “Brut” SB Dunk High. This offering of the Air Jordan 1 Zoom sports Green hairy suede on the toe and side panel with Black smooth leather overlays. While also featuring a Green liner, 3M reflective Swooshes, and a Zoom tag on the lateral side atop a White midsole and icy translucent outsole completes the design.

data.description: Enjoy vibrant panels of colour layered with smooth leather against the wrinkled-effect fabric. The Air Jordan 1 Mid "To My First Coach" Womens pair of sneakers is truly a sentimental item, with a hangtag labelled “Thank You” as a shoutout to the beginning of an exciting sporting career. This shoe pairs leather and suede for an ultimate textured look and comfort in mind. The Air Jordan 1 Mid "To My First Coach" Womens combines all the traditional features of legendary Jordan's and includes personality and vibrancy with shades of yellow, orange, blue, and grey, offset against white, which makes for a truly unique pair of sneakers. Included with Air cushioning technology and a full-length midsole, the Womens Air Jordan 1 Mid "To My First Coach" is ideal for a bright and vibrant mood when you want to depend on versatility and comfort every time you wear them.

fields.name: Air Jordan 12 Retro Stealth Gs

data.description: Elevate your outfits with the Air Jordan 12 Retro Stealth GS. The tumbled grey upper’s radial stitch lines add texture to the silhouette and provide an ideal contrast with the white lizard-textured synthetic leather overlays along the toe and midfoot. The contemporary sneakers might be minimalistic in design, but subtle branding appears across the shoe, such as the iconic Jumpman on the tongue, heel tab, insole, and outsole’s toe. The sneaker will remain comfy on your feet, as it has a full-length Phylon midsole with encapsulated Zoom Air cushioning in the heel. The sneakers will feel safe and secure thanks to the herringbone-traction rubber outsole.

fields.name: Jordan 1 Mid Barcelona Sweater Red Patent

data.description: This playfully iconic Jordan 1 Mid Barcelona Sweater Red Patent sneaker comes with a glossy red design that’s set to turn heads and make an impression on the courts or on the streets. The Jordan 1 Mid Barcelona Sweater Red Patent sneaker is complete with a sweater-pattern fabric around the main collar panels, behind a glossy red patent leather ankle strap embossed with a clean white Air Jordan Wings logo. The patent leather continues in red for the heel panel, side Nike Swoosh, eyelet panel, front side panels, and wrapping around the toe. This is contrasted cleanly by a matte white leather finish on the main side panels and perforated toe box. For the sole, you have a clean white rubber mid and a semi-translucent blue rubber outer sole. To finish, the laces and the fabric tongue both return to the rich, fiery red.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Grey Camo

data.description: Jordan Brand is having one of the best years within the sneaker industry, especially with the new release of the Air Jordan 1 Mid Grey Camo. The Air Jordan 1 High has always been a favourite amongst collectors, but the resurgence of the low and mid in 2020 sees the brand's popularity boom even more. The Jordan 1 Grey Camo silhouette comes dressed in a minimalistic take on camo print, featuring mostly white and grey hues throughout the design. The high-end leather is complemented by the iconic swoosh dripping in camo print. The usual legendary branding can be found throughout to ensure we know this is an Air Jordan 1. Underfoot a white and grey sole houses Nike Air technology to guarantee comfort wear after wear. With the current hype surrounding the Air Jordan 1, you'd better cop the mid grey camo Jordan 1's before they sell out.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Craft Inside Out White Grey

data.description: Lovers of gentle pastel hues and timeless style will want this pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid Craft Inside Out White Grey sneakers for their collection. The premium upper comes with layered panels of varying soft colours for a playful finish. The light taupe hue is shown on the perforated toe box panel, the front side straps, the lower heel detailing, and around the collar. This is paired with clean white around the toe and the main mid-panel. A soft grey is then shown in nubuck for the eyestay strip and for the heel tab, embossed with a white Air Jordan Wings logo. For the main ankle strap, you have a pastel grey-blue hue, combining with soft pink laces on top. The side Nike Swoosh is shown in minimalistic fashion in white, with coral pink thread detailing.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid University Blue Womens

data.description: Are you hoping to stand out? The Air Jordan 1 Mid University Blue Women's sneakers are exactly what you're looking for. These blue, white, and black Air Jordan 1s have the styling you've come to expect, with the great University look and a classical silhouette that Air Jordans are famous for. It's not just the striking looks that you'll love about the Womens Air Jordan 1 Mid University Blue either; the fit is perfect, with a mid-height boot and ankle support that comes with a premium quality sneaker. Getting the colours right on these sneakers was the most important thing after considering a good construction, evident by the perfect combination of blue against black and white. The added winged Air Jordan logo in white really finishes the Air Jordan 1 Mid University Blue Womens, contrasting perfectly above to the Nike swoosh, which blends seamlessly into the black leather.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Golf Court Purple

data.description: Presenting an ‘80s basketball icon adapted for golf, the Air Jordan 1 Low Golf Court Purple is defined by its vibrant purple overlays. Its all-leather upper is decorated with classic branding and is complete with a perforated toe box for ventilation. The Air midsole underfoot offers comfort, the updated rubber outsole allows for extra grip and the secure lace closure means for a tailored fit. Buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 Low Golf Court Purple with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 7 Se Black Olive

data.description: Celebrating the basketball model’s 30th anniversary, the Air Jordan 7 SE Black Olive takes on a unique, earth-toned colourway. Its suede upper features classic branding as well as scattered perforations for effective ventilation. Air cushioning in the jagged midsole offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Finished with a pull tab for an easy on and off, buy and sell the Air Jordan 7 SE Black Olive with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 2 Craft Sunset Haze Womens

data.description: Sporting a neutral colourway, the Air Jordan 2 Craft Sunset Haze Womens is crafted with premium materials. Its leather upper features Jordan branding, perforations for ventilation and a TPU overlay at the heel. The Air midsole underfoot offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and padding in the collar adds extra support. Fastened with a secure lace closure, the Air Jordan 2 Craft Sunset Haze Womens is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Ko Syracuse

data.description: Designed to honour the Michael Jordan’s amateur hoops heritage and the legendary defenders he faced along the way, the Air Jordan 1 KO Syracuse boasts a Syracuse orange hue, nodding to his ‘80s competitors. Crafted from durable denim-like fabric, the upper features Nike’s iconic Swoosh on the sidewalls, Jordan’s Wings insignia on the ankle and lightweight cushioning underfoot. Finished with a Sail midsole that offers a vintage look, the Air Jordan 1 KO Syracuse is the perfect blend of old and new school.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Midnight Navy Toddler

data.description: You're never too young for a cool pair of sneakers, and this Air Jordan 4 Midnight Navy colourway is the perfect pair to start. Your toddler will look effortlessly stylish when tackling the playground, dancing at a party, or strolling down the street. Released in 2022, the cool design emulates Tinker Hatfield's original silhouette released in 1989. The neutral white leather upper will match most looks in your little one's wardrobe, and the navy blue and speckled grey overlays add character and texture to the iconic design. You don't need to worry about comfort, as the sneakers feature an Air unit for a soft and supportive feel, which will help your child master those first shaky steps.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Red Thunder

data.description: The Air Jordan 4 is a silhouette from the Jordan Brand that has legions of fans. The sneaker was made world-famous by MJ, but the incredible colourways we have seen in recent years has solidified the sneaker as a grail for many collectors. The upcoming Air Jordan 4 Red Thunder is one of the cleanest takes we have seen of the shoe in quite some time. The stealthy Jordan 4 Red Thunder sneaker features a black nubuck leather upper, with an intriguing pattern across multiple panels. The premium-looking silhouette features red accents on the lacing system and outsole, earning the shoe its nickname. Traditional features such as the mesh panelling across the side of the sneaker features, as does the Jumpman logo on the heel and tongue. Underfoot the Jordan 4 Retro Red Thunder, the Tinker Hatfield designed air bubble is still very much intact, housed within a black midsole. Nike Air technology runs the length of the sole unit, making the Jordan 4 one of the most comfortable sneakers money can buy.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Brown Elephant

data.description: A modern twist on a timeless style, the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Brown Elephant blends beige suede with brown leather for durability and comfort. This pair includes an eye-catching elephant print Swoosh and collar, adding a unique touch to any of your outfits. Enjoy lightweight cushioning with the Nike Air unit, and walk comfortably with solid rubber outsoles. Step out in style with the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Brown Elephant where comfort meets uniqueness.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Anti Gravity Machines Womens

data.description: Bold red, blue and tasteful cream combine in this must-have Air Jordan 1 Mid Anti Gravity Machines Womens sneaker, with a constructed upper that provides an exciting variety, with alternating colours on the shoes - one in rich read and the other in bold blue. The Womens Air Jordan 1 Mid Anti Gravity Machines switches between a rich red on one shoe and bold blue on the other. These include tumbled leather on the heel, ankle strap, eyelet panel, and side front panels, while this is offset cleanly by soft suede panels in off-white. The warm colours and soft fabric give the sneaker an overall inviting look and feel, while the Nike Swoosh stands out distinctly in black tumbled leather against cream suede. Another fresh addition is included with the white laces, white fabric colour, and the white strip running along the midsole. The outer sole is chunky and cushioned translucent rubber in a neutral shade. The Air Jordan Wings logo blends in on the red heel strap in a matching hue to finish the Air Jordan 1 Mid Anti Gravity Machines Womens design.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Retro Georgetown Gs (2022)

data.description: The Air Jordan 6 Retro Georgetown GS sneakers provide the Jordan Brand’s sixth signature sneaker, College Navy, with a fresh, modern update. The high-top sneaker has swapped the white upper for a tumbled grey leather construction. The modern design has retained the touches of navy blue on the heel and midsole but has replaced the colour from the tongue to create an all-grey upper. Of course, you can expect many of Air Jordan 6’s signature elements, including its toggle lacing, rubber outsole, and visible Air cushioning. Also, Air Jordan branding appears on the tongue, and a navy Jumpman features on the heel.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High X Spider-Man Across The Spider-Verse Red Black Td

data.description: Boasting a Chicago-inspired colourway, the Air Jordan 1 High x Spider-Man Across The Spider-Verse Red Black TD was released alongside the highly anticipated Spider-Man: Across The Spider-Verse film. Featuring patchwork-style panelling, its upper also takes on faux 3D elements and classic branding. Perforations allow for ventilation, classic laces allow for a secure fit and padding in its collar adds extra cushioning. Refresh your toddler’s collection with the playful Air Jordan 1 High x Spider-Man Across The Spider-Verse Red Black TD.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Tropical Twist Gs

data.description: In a tropical shade of cool turquoise against clean white and deep black, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Tropical Twist GS is a sneaker that feels as good as it looks. With deep black leather panelling by the eyelets and around the front against matching black laces, you can enjoy a classic and sophisticated look whilst also indulging in a brighter burst of colour with the tropical turquoise around the heel. The bright turquoise shade also continues with the Nike swoosh on the side and altogether results in a cool and refreshing look you can take to the court, to the beach, or to the streets. The iconic Air Jordan wings logo stands out in black stamping on the Air Jordan 1 Mid Tropical Twist GS, and the front toe panel includes air holes to allow your feet to breathe easily.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Coconut Milk Grey Gs

data.description: This stylish pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Coconut Milk Grey GS sneakers not only offers a soft colour palette, but a soft textured upper, too. The premium Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Coconut Milk Grey GS sneaker combines suede with soft fabric for a standout look. The upper is constructed from grey suede wrapping around the toe, across the side front straps, and up along the eyelet panel. The colouring switches to a lighter dove grey suede for the main heel panel, the ankle strap, and the side Nike Swoosh. The ankle strap includes a white Air Jordan Wings logo. For the rest of the upper, you have creamy textile panelling running across the perforated toe box, the main mid-panel, and around the collar sides. The laces echo the deep grey-blue hue, which is also repeated on the collar fabric, while the sole shows off a fresh white midsole and a gum rubber outer sole to finish.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Pinksicle Gs

data.description: Featuring everything you love about the original Air Jordan 1 silhouette, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Pinksicle GS is ideal for casual streetwear and on the court, with a pink twist. The inclusion of white leather, as well as black, gives bold and clean contrast to the vibrant pink shade, with a standout white Nike swoosh that matches the white rubber midsole. The soft textile tongue offers comfort whilst also showing off the Air wings logo in bright white against pink, and black laces finish off the look. The cushioned collar is built for maximum comfort and support around the ankle, as well as a durable grip on the sleek black outer sole. The Air Jordan 1 Mid Pinksicle GS was built for style and stability that you’ll love showing off in shades of black, white, and pink.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Triple White

data.description: Sneakers don’t get much cooler than the Air Jordan 1 Mid Triple White. Fresh, timeless, and versatile, you can trust the crisp white silhouette will elevate your everyday style and boost confidence in an outfit. The AJ1 Mid Triple White offers a modern style while using classic Air Jordan 1 materials, as it features a white real and synthetic leather upper for a solid structure and durability. The signature Air-Sole unit offers superior lightweight cushioning that will make you feel like you are walking on air. Also, the textile tongue and mid-top will increase your comfort and support, and you can enjoy superb traction on many surfaces thanks to the solid rubber outsole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Inside Out Black Grey

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Low Inside Out Black Grey colourway follows the huge success of the White/Sail iteration. The classic silhouette receives a stylish shake-up as the overlays become underlays and vice versa. The deconstructed design is crafted from a mixture of tonal black leather and suede materials across the upper, and the lower half of the sneaker is dominated by a dark grey hue. One thing that remains unchanged is the famous Nike branding across the silhouette. The brand's synonymous Nike Swooshes appear in grey on the lateral and medial sidewalls, ensuring no one can question the stealthy kicks on your feet.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Zoom Cmft Psychic Blue Womens

data.description: Adding a touch of brown earth tones to pale pastel blue, this pair of Air Jordan 1 Zoom CMFT Psychic Blue Womens is an example of versatility at its best. This colour scheme is soft and palatable for any occasion or outfit, and the balanced supported design is ideal for all-day cushioning and comfort. The sleek leather panels combine a brushed suede effect for a softer look whilst adding subtle creases on the pastel blue leather. This is then combined with soft fabric mesh for the tongue and the collar for ultimate comfort. This colour palette brings to mind long days adventuring in the outdoors and luckily, the cushioned sole and balance of the Nike Air base means you can comfortably do so all day long. Soft brown laces complete the look, and air holes allow your feet to breathe.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid White Black Royal

data.description: If you’re a fan of timeless black and white on a sneaker but are looking for an impressive pop of colour, royal blue is a shade that works iconically with the timeless Air Jordan 1 Mid White Black Royal silhouette. This royal blue is displayed in all its glory on the Nike Swoosh and is also included on the ankle panel as well as with the Air Jordan Wings logo. The rest of the Air Jordan 1 Mid White Black Royal sneaker is made up of contrasting and sleek panels of black and white, with a white and black sole combination making for a classic shape. The black laces and eyelet panel form a bold and seamless continuation of the theme, and the cushioned sole offers the balance and durability that any Air Jordans fan will know by now for their collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Schematic Gs

data.description: This pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid Schematic GS sneakers in classic silhouette offers not only a sleek minimalistic sneaker but a unique and quirky design, too. Here in the Grade School model, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Schematic GS sneaker has thrown in a schematic theme with graphic design at the fore, with the individual sections of the sneakers labelled in black lettering. The premium upper comes in matte white leather, providing that timeless and classic look, with a perforated toe box, white laces, white mid, and white tongue. For the overlay ankle strap, also in white leather, you have an Air Jordan Wings logo printed in fine black. The rest of the Air Jordan 1 Mid Schematic GS sneaker’s sections are labelled, including the mudguard and toe, and for the Nike Swoosh you have a sketched black outline with the Swoosh labelled in the centre. The sole comes in white rubber for the mid, while the rubber outer comes in black.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Black Cat Gs

data.description: Built with a pure black design and a sleek finish, the Air Jordan 4 Retro Black Cat GS are for the elegant, bold and minimalistic, which packs an impressive design punch nonetheless. The silhouette of this sneaker provides a pure retro feel, supported by the clear air bubbles seen in the heel of the shoe. The black rubber sole connects effortlessly to the black sneaker for a design that’s sleek, comfortable, and completely versatile. Being all black, you can be sure that the Air Jordan 4 Retro Black Cat GS will match any occasion or outfit you want to try. The pure black design of the Air Jordan 4 Retro Black Cat GS is broken up subtly by the crosshatch side panelling and complemented by black plastic wings on the sides. A high back and tongue mean comfort, style, and support around the ankle, as well as a cushioned heel.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Marina Blue Womens

data.description: Dressed in one of Jordan’s most in-demand blue hues, the Air Jordan 1 Low Marina Blue is perfect for the new season. Crafted with synthetic leather underlays, bold blue overlays enhance the shoe’s durability, while breathable perforations scattered across the toe box enhance ventilation. Nike’s instantly recognisable Swoosh sits in its usual place on the sidewalls, while Jordan’s Wings branding is stitched into the heel for good measure. Of course, no Jordan would be complete without Michael Jordan’s Jumpman motif, which is featured on the tongue of this Air Jordan 1 Low Marina Blue.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Grey Camo Gs

data.description: If you're looking for a more minimalistic, sleek sneaker, then a white pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid Grey Camo GS sneakers is always going to be a great choice. With this pair, you get the added detailing of soft shades of grey as well as a stylish addition of a grey camo print on the side Nike Swoosh, adding a flair of personality without taking away from the more simplistic design. The majority of the Air Jordan 1 Mid Grey Camo GS' upper is built from premium white leather for a fresh, clean look, which includes a tumbled leather effect around the front. The heel and ankle strap panels are shown off in delicate grey shading, while the Air Jordan Wings logo is printed in a fine-line black. White laces and a white midsole complete the elegant, clean look of the Air Jordan 1 Mid Grey Camo GS, perfect for any occasion.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Electro Orange

data.description: Nothing says bright and stylish more than electro orange! Offset against sleek silver leather panelling, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High Electro Orange is the ultimate retro look in an Air Jordan silhouette that never fails to make an impression. This sneaker combines style and nostalgia all in one, with shiny metallics and pops of bold colour. Electro orange adorns the outer sole and collar panel, while silver, black and white even out the colour and add a classic touch. The eyelet panel and laces work seamlessly in matching black, which continues onto the Nike Swoosh, front panels, and around the collar. This black bordering on the collar works perfectly against the bright orange, allowing the colour to shine. Air holes in the white toe cap mean complete breathability and comfort every time you’re rocking these Air Jordan 1 Retro High Electro Orange sneakers, perfect for any outfit or occasion.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High White University Blue Black Gs

data.description: Whenever an Air Jordan 1 releases, the entire sneaker community takes notice. The upcoming University Blue AJ1 has the potential to be one of the best releases we see all year. Whenever Jordan Brand use that UNC hue, the sneaker instantly becomes a fan favourite. The uppers are crafted from premium leathers, with white underlays perfectly complimented by the UNC coloured panels. You can see the iconic Nike Swoosh branding across both lateral and medial sides of the sneaker in black, and classic Nike Air branding on the shoe's tongue. The legendary Wings logo also features on the sneaker's collar giving this Jordan 1 an exceptionally OG feel. Underfoot, a white midsole is contrasted with a slightly darker blue outsole. This sole unit houses Nike Air technology which guarantees unparalleled comfort. Any UNC Jordan will instantly become a Sneaker of the Year candidate, and this AJ1 is no different. Be sure to add a pair to your rotation.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro X Dj Khaled We The Best Sail

data.description: The collaboration between the Jordan Brand and DJ Khaled was a dream come true for the American DJ, as he once stated he was a "sneakerhead from birth" and owns a sneaker collection worth a reported $8 million. The music mogul's passion for sneakers is clear in this latest Sail-coloured interpretation of the Air Jordan 5 Retro, which is a part of his "We The Best" collection with the sneaker giant. The sail colourway is likely the most suitable sneaker for everyday wear from the collection. The muted upper balances the hits of colour across the design, such as a bubble gum purple midsole, gold-speckled blue spikes, a black mudguard at the heel, and a translucent outsole with a hint of orange at the forefoot. You can't help but notice the silver padded tongue with the signature black Jumpman, which serves as a symbol of quality.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Se Tie-Dye

data.description: One of the most in-demand silhouettes from Jordan Brand’s capsule, the Air Jordan 1 Low has been refreshed in a yet another covetable colourway. Featuring a full-leather design, the Air Jordan 1 Low SE Tie-Dye arrives with a white base and black overlays on the toes, eyestays and the Nike Swoosh logo. At the rear, tie-dye hits of mint, pink and purple update the design, creating a stand-out look that sets the tone for the season. This shoe strikes a balance between comfort and style thanks to the perforated toe box and the Air-fitted sole for comfort on or off the court. To finish, Jordan’s signature Wings branding has been added to the heel counter, making the Air Jordan 1 Low SE Tie Dye instantly recognisable from every angle.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Bred Sail Womens

data.description: Taking on an iconic Jordan colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Low Bred Sail Womens is crafted using premium materials. Its leather upper is decorated with classic touches of branding. Perforations on its toe box allow air to flow around the foot, Air cushioning in the off-white midsole offers comfort and the rubber outsole offers grip. Rounded off with a classic lacing system, refresh your rotation with the Air Jordan 1 Low Bred Sail Womens.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Og Starfish

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Low Starfish OG is one of the most iconic colourways to come out of the Jordan Brand camp. This version of the Jordan 1 Low Starfish looks like a true throwback; white leather underlays are contrasted expertly by the eyecatching orange hue across the legendary Jordan panels. You can find the OG wings logo on the heel tab, whilst Nike Swoosh branding features across the lateral and medial sides of the shoe. Underfoot, a traditional Jordan 1 sole unit compliments the uppers perfectly dressed in a white and orange combination. This sole unit houses Nike Air technology, making this the perfect sneaker for the street or the courts.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid University Blue Grey

data.description: Air Jordan continues to provide fresh twists on its much-loved University Blue colourway, and this latest iteration is no different. Released in August 2022, the Air Jordan 1 Mid University Blue Grey sneaker features a vibrant blue outsole, toe cap, Nike Swooshes, eyelets, lining, and sock liner. Also, the collar and heel feature a light grey suede material that pops against the vibrant white upper, midsole, tongue, and laces. It’s almost impossible for people to miss the iconic Michael Jordan Jumpman logo at the top of the tongue in the University Blue shade. The sporty shoe is finished with embroidered an Air Jordan Wings logo on the collar.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Se Knit Gs

data.description: Offering up a fresh take on the classic design, the Air Jordan 1 Low SE Knit GS is playful and practical in equal measure. Drawing on the original silhouette, this iteration is crafted with a white leather upper, contrasted by purple knitted accents on the Swoosh and ankle collar. The overlays receive a stitched trim — magenta decorates the eyelets, while aqua surrounds the heel counter. Underfoot, a traditional Air Jordan 1 sole unit features the same purple and white hues as the upper. Branding comes courtesy of a Wings motif at the back and the Jumpman on the tongue. The Nike Air Jordan 1 Low SE Knit GS is then capped off by bracelet-like JORDAN dubraes.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Pine Green

data.description: Adopting the clean and simple colour blocking of the famed Shattered Backboard Air Jordan 1's and replacing the orange hue with a ‘Pine Green’ option for a variant of 2009’s ‘Celtics’ colourway the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Pine Green released in September 2018 has quickly become one of the most coveted retro drops of the year. This shoe takes some of Jordan Brand’s classic features and combines them with a clean and contemporary design to create a model that feels very familiar but in a lot of ways different to some of its predecessors. This colours major selling point is its Pine Green colour, Air Jordan has a way of making the use of colour so significant, and this one is sure to stick in your memory and become synonymous with the brand like others have previously. This kick is great for the streets or the court, and definitely a retro worth its salt in the modern world.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Cmft 2 Blackened Blue

data.description: Presenting an updated take on the ‘80s basketball silhouette, the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom CMFT 2 Blackened Blue also boasts retro-inspired aesthetics. Made from a mixture of suede and mesh, its upper is detailed with cut-out Swooshes and Jordan branding. Underfoot, Zoom Air cushioning offers comfort and the rubber outsole provides grip. Complete with a perforated toe box for ventilation, the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom CMFT 2 Blackened Blue is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Rookie Year Gs

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid Rookie Year GS sneaker encourages people to dream big. Released in 2022, the sneakers take inspiration from Michael Jordan's rookie season when he scored the league's highest number of points and ensured he was named an NBA All-Star during his first season at the Chicago Bulls. As a homage to his basketball success during the 1984-85 season, the sneakers feature Michael Jordan's autograph on the medial and lateral mudguards, as well as his position, date of birth, weight, height, and draft pick number on the foxing.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Dark Mocha Neapolitan Womens

data.description: Inspired by the signature chocolate, strawberry and vanilla hues of Neapolitan ice cream, the Air Jordan 3 Retro Neapolitan Womens features all the eye-catching details the AJ3 is famed for. Up top, smooth leather is offset with the shoe’s famous elephant print, while breathable perforations on the lace-up unit and ankle enhance the shoe’s breathability. Pops of baby pink feature on the heel, sole and removable tag, while an off-white midsole adds the perfect point of contrast. An easy-to-style pair that ticks every box, add the Air Jordan 3 Dark Mocha Womens to the very top of your Wishlist.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro Dark Concord

data.description: Add undeniable freshness, style, and versatility to your wardrobe with the Air Jordan 5 Retro Dark Concord. The AJ5 has proved popular with sneakerheads since its initial release in 1990, and this new design is sure to continue its popularity among fans across the world. The smooth white leather stylishly clashes with the dark concord blue shade. Also, futuristic elements feature across the shoe, such as an iced outsole and a reflective tongue. Also, the flame-like spiky purple midsole will draw attention to the kicks on your feet, and the black outsole provides balance and durability. However, it is the transparent lace lock tie that unites the unique elements. The AJ5 Retro Dark Concord is a modern take on a classic sneaker silhouette, which is sure to enhance many outfits in your wardrobe.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air Cmft Bred Womens

data.description: Designed for exceptional comfort as well as a bold statement colourway, this pair of Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air CMFT Bred Womens sneakers is the perfect choice for the courts or for the streets. The premium leather upper is constructed of sweeping panels of matte black leather, running across the perforated toe box, side mid panels, front side panels, along the eyelet strap, and across the main heel tab. A cut-out design in black leather is featured to reveal the deep red fabric behind in the shape of a side Nike Swoosh. For the collar, you have a black leather ankle strap adorned with a red Air Jordan Wings logo, while the rich red repeats for the back panels. The Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air CMFT Bred Womens shoe is complete with a black tongue, black laces, white rubber midsole, and striking red outer sole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Metallic Red Gs

data.description: The punch these Air Jordan 4 Metallic Red GS sneakers give cannot be underestimated! In just one pair of trainers, you can experience heritage styling, an iconic silhouette, and the classic look of the Air Jordan 4s, as well as intricate red detailing. Shine on home with the metallic red lace holders standing out proudly against the minimalistic white leather shoe and classic Air Jordan sole. With an incredibly comfy sole, feel like you’re walking on pure air and get your bounce on with this patented look and feel. The Air Jordan 4 Metallic Red GS are perfect for a pounding gym session or a run on the streets, and thanks to their good looks, they're the perfect accompaniment to any style.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Retro Carmine 2021

data.description: Jordan Brand continues its stellar 2021, releasing a retro of the Jordan 6 in Michael Jordan's favourite colourway. The Carmine Jordan 6 has been worn multiple times by MJ himself, so we can all but guarantee these will be a fan favourite. The uppers are composed of a mix of red and white materials, making these the perfect shoe for Chicago Bulls fans. The padded ankle detailing features whilst the heel-pull tab also features in black and red. The iconic Jumpman logo features on the sneaker's heel while the shoe's tongue features the Jumpmana logo and the legendary pull-tab. Underfoot, a retro-looking sole unit houses Nike Air technology. The mix of black, white and silver emphasises the colourway perfectly. An air bubble features reminding all of us that Tinker Hatfield created this iconic silhouette. A real 90s throwback, be sure to add the Carmine to your collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid White Light Iron Ore Womens

data.description: Texture is the name of the game with this Air Jordan 1 Mid White Light Iron Ore Womens. Nodding to the OG design with its streamlined shape and functional elements, this AJ1 iteration elevates the style with jersey overlays and a pastel pink Swoosh. Tumbled leather makes up the sides and toe box, while Michael Jordan’s Jumpman logo steals the show on the tongue. data.description: Released during the 2016 NBA All-Star weekend in Toronto the Air Jordan 4 Retro OG 'Cement' is a revival of one of the original four colourways released for the Air Jordan 4 in 1989. The 'Cement' aptly named for its speckled cement grey accents also features its original white, fire red, black, and tech grey colour palette. This trip down memory lane has been granted a retro release in 1999, 2012 and now 2016 and has become a staple success for the Jumpman brand with the newer versions featuring the ‘Nike Air’ branding on the heel, just like the 1989 OG.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Smoke Grey Black

data.description: You can never have too many pairs of Jordans, and the muted Air Jordan 1 Mid Smoke Grey Black is the next iteration to demand a place in your collection. Epitomising stylish versatility, the all-leather upper is crafted with grey, black and white hues which cater this sneaker towards any occasion. Nike’s iconic Swoosh and the Jordan Brand’s Wings logo add just the right amount of detail, whilst reliable lightweight cushioning underfoot ensures comfort all day long. Destined for your everyday rotation, get your hands on the Air Jordan 1 Mid Smoke Grey Black whilst you can.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Oreo Gs

data.description: You don’t have to be a lover of the popular snack to appreciate the sleek and clean colour scheme on this pair of Air Jordan 4s. Speckled grey and white combine for a fresh look, and the GS sizing means narrower or smaller feet don’t ever have to miss out on the stylish Air Jordan 4 Oreo GS. This sneaker is built up of the premium leather any Air Jordan fan expects and also includes mesh detailing. The visible Air unit is included on a clean white midsole, and grey cushioning adds a pop of colour as well as added comfort and balance, resulting in a stylish and muted colour scheme on a versatile sneaker. White laces complete the look of the Air Jordan 4 Oreo GS, offset perfectly against the grey.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Lucky Green Womens

data.description: Refreshing the retro basketball model with a vibrant colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Low Lucky Green Womens is crafted using premium materials. Its leather upper is detailed with sidewall Swooshes and touches of Jordan branding. The Air-cushioned midsole offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and the perforated toe box allows for ventilation. Fastened with a secure lace closure, update your collection with the Air Jordan 1 Low Lucky Green Womens.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Purple Aqua

data.description: This tasteful pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid Purple Aqua sneakers includes shades of soft pastel colours compelted with bright white styling. The pastel tones work hand-in-hand for an aesthetically pleasing look, complete with pastel purple on the rubber sole to complete the look. If you're looking for sneakers to wear out and about in the summer, a pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid Purple Aqua's are perfect for you.The mid-rise offers structured support in the leather panels, with a bouncy sole to ensure you're comfortable every time you wear them. A pastel purple Nike swoosh keeps the classic Air Jordan branding in the shoe, and contributes to the pastel vibes throughout. White laces keep the entire design clean, with the pastel stitching tieing the whole Air Jordan 1 Mid Purple Aqua design together.

fields.name: Air Jordan 8 Retro Playoffs

data.description: Born during Michael Jordan's '92–'93 championship season, the Air Jordan 8 Retro Playoffs is an enduring classic that pays homage to its iconic design. Crafted from resilient leather and textile, it ensures enduring support. The encapsulated Nike Air sole unit brings featherlight cushioning, while the midfoot straps promise stability and a snug fit. The Air Jordan 8 Retro Playoffs merges enduring style with unmatched comfort, offering a timeless tribute to basketball history.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Grey Green Gs

data.description: Soft grey meets bold green for this sophisticated pair of fresh Air Jordan 1 Mid Grey Green GS sneakers from the Air Jordan 1 Mid silhouette. The Air Jordan 1 Mid Grey Green GS shoe shows off a smooth white leather for the ankle strap, main mid panels, and across the toe box, which is also perforated for extra breathability and comfort. The white is complemented by rich green on the Air Jordan Wings logo stamped on the ankle strap, the green running along the side Nike Swoosh and the green collar panels behind the strap. Soft dove grey is shown in warm nubuck, running around the toe, front side panels, eyelet strip, and lower heel panel. Grey is also included on the tongue, behind clean white laces. For the sole, you have white rubber for the mid and a return to bold green for the Air Jordan 1 Mid Grey Green GS' outer.

fields.name: Jordan 1 Mid Black White Womens

data.description: Originally landing in 1985, the rich history of the Nike Air Jordan 1 has made it one of the most famous sneakers to ever exist. Designed to be a functional basketball shoe, the AJ1 has transformed into a lifestyle shoe with endless styling potential. One iteration that deserves a place in your collection is the Jordan 1 Mid Black White Womens. Crafted from smooth leather with breathable perforations on the toe box, the sidewalls are simply detailed with Nike’s Swoosh and Jordan Brand’s Wings motif. No AJ1 is complete without Michael Jordan’s Jumpman on the tongue which adds depth to the design. Presented in an easy black and white hue, add the Jordan 1 Mid Black White to your everyday rotation.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Craft Olive Td

data.description: Ultimate comfort and style are combined in the Air Jordan 4 Craft Olive TD. This pair sports a black leather on the support wings, eyelets and Jumpman logos on the tongue. Instead of the usual netting, the side has an embossed grid pattern in suede. These sneakers have a white foam sole and a sturdy rubber outsole in black and grey. Comfort is guaranteed for your little one with the Air cushioning underfoot and the rubber outsole that delivers grip, traction and the classic lacing system ensures a secure fit. The Air Jordan 4 Craft Olive TD effortlessly blends style and performance, making them a must-have for your toddler’s collection.

fields.name: Jordan 5 What The

data.description: We see the return of one of Nike's most ludicrous colourways this week, the 'What The' Air Jordan 5. With the current boom in popularity the Air Jordan 5 is having, it comes as no surprise to see Nike and Jordan Brand drop this outrageous colourway on the silhouette. The 'What The' Air Jordan 5 celebrates the 30th anniversary of the legendary sneaker. Borrowing design aspects from several previous releases, including the Tokyo, Shanghai, Raging Bull, Bel-Air, Laser, Green Bean, Army Olive and Quai 54 colourways. The Tinker Hatfield designed shoe comes covered in luxurious suede uppers, dressed in vibrant shades of reds and yellows. You will find iconic Jumpman logos on the tongues of the sneaker, whilst the emblems from the Tokyo and Shanghai AJ5's feature on the heels. You will also find the graphic patterns from the Bel-Air and Laser silhouettes borrowed for the sneakers sock liners. A sneaker guaranteed to get you noticed, do not miss out on the chance to add a 'What The' sneaker to your rotation.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Celtics Gs

data.description: Boasting a design inspired by the Boston Celtics, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Celtics GS stays close to the model’s basketball roots. Its leather upper is accented with Swoosh detailing and Jordan branding. Air cushioning underfoot offers comfort, padding in its collar adds extra support and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Finished with a grip-enhancing outsole, refresh your rotation with the Air Jordan 1 Mid Celtics GS.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Union Guava Ice

data.description: After a two year hiatus, Union LA has once again joined forces with Jordan to deliver another great collaboration. After the massive success of the Union x Jordan 1, the LA boutique store this time takes over Tinker Hatfield creation the Jordan 4. This time we see Union use an exciting mix of pinks, reds and blues to create the perfect combination. A colourway they have named Guava Ice. The sneaker features a mostly pink and red upper with blue detailing. The sail coloured sole features, emphasising the Guava Ice colourway. On the heel, you will find the Nike Air branding favoured over the Jumpman logo. As with its Off Noir brother, the most irregular part of the Jordan 4 comes in the shape of a tongue that folds to show the typical Air Jordan branding stitched inside of it. Contrary to what people first thought when images began to surface, you can have the tongue at full length as you would generally see on Jordan 4 models. Union founder Chris Gibbs has also added his usual personal touch with the addition of the Union LA yellow tab featured on the side panelling of each shoe. The Union LA x Jordan 4 Guava Ice is sure to follow on from the success of the Jordan 1 collaboration from 2018, a sneaker all serious collectors will want to own.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Low Arctic Pink Womens

data.description: Refresh your rotation with the Air Jordan 5 Low Arctic Pink Women’s, a pastel-toned pair that will complement any outfit. A pretty pink kick with endless styling potential, the Jordan brand blends premium fabrics with expert craftsmanship to deliver a sneaker that you’ll never want to take off. The upper is crafted from textured leather and the silhouette’s signature perforated panel graces the sides. A hot pink midsole perfectly complements the light pink upper, whilst a toggle on the lace-up fastening delivers a secure and customisable fit. Rounded off with Nike’s famous Air unit underfoot, the understated yet bold Air Jordan 5 Low Arctic Pink ticks every single box.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Gs Mid Laser Orange

data.description: Complete your retro sneaker collection with this sleek and attractive pair of Air Jordan 1 GS Mid Laser Orange sneakers. The rounded and streamlined silhouette is not only a timeless classic but is now also perfect for a narrower fit in this GS edition. The upper is dominated by fresh white and a deep, bold blue that always looks good on a pair of Air Jordans. What gives the Air Jordan 1 GS Mid Laser Orange sneaker even more of a retro finish is the bold flashes of bright yellow and red on the fabric collar. The white midsole is given chunky height, support and balance, matched perfectly by the bold blue repeated on the rubber outer sole. A clean and sleek Nike Swoosh is included against the blue side panel of the Air Jordan 1 GS Mid Laser Orange, and the premium-crafted upper shows off sleek white and blue leather with fresh white laces to complete the look.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Black Gym Red

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid Black Gym Red continues its quest to become one of the hottest sneakers in the game. Jordan Brand continue to deliver unbelievable colourways, making the Air Jordan 1 Mid Gym Red an absolute must-have. This Metallic Red version is guaranteed to turn heads. The Jordan 1 Gym Red sneaker features the usual white underlays with the panelling that makes the shoe instantly recognisable. A mix of premium materials gives this silhouette a luxurious feel, with a red satin fabric used for the iconic swoosh branding, wings logo and the shoe's collar. Black panels contrast the red perfectly, giving the Air Jordan 1 Mid Black Gym Red sneaker a reverse Chicago feel. Underfoot the Gym Red Jordan 1, a Nike Air sole unit features in a red and white colourway. The Nike Air technology in the sole guarantees unbeatable comfort, whilst the colourway flawlessly complements the upper, completing the design of this legendary sneaker.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Wheat Watermelon

Made from a blend of leather, canvas and suede materials, its upper is decorated with signature Jordan branding. Perforations on its toe box allow for ventilation, while its rubber sole unit offers both cushioning and grip. fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Triple Black Tumbled Leather Gs

data.description: When one shade of black isn’t enough, try triple! Fans of classic, minimalistic, and stylish sneakers will simply love this pair of Air Jordan 1 Low Triple Black Tumbled Leather GS sneakers. You have everything you love about the classic Air Jordan 1 Low silhouette whilst embracing layered panelling of premium black leather and tumbled leather for a sophisticated look that is going to match any location and outfit. The Air Jordan 1 Low Triple Black Tumbled Leather GS is a reliable shoe that’s going to stand the test of time, staying clean, comfortable, and stylish. You can enjoy a natural-grain effect in tumbled black leather along the front, side, and eyelet panels, working seamlessly with smooth leather around the sneaker. The Nike Swoosh is subtle in black, and black laces complete the look for a sophisticated finish.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Atmosphere Ps

data.description: Arriving in smaller sizes for the little ballers, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Atmosphere PS keeps things traditional, dressing the iconic Air Jordan 1 silhouette in a contrasting colour palette that will push this model into contention to be part of most sneakerhead's daily rotations. The familiar premium leather panelling on the shoe’s upper pairs white quarter panels with an Obsidian coloured Swoosh. The latter hue is then repeated on the eye stays and forefoot overlays, while the toe box, heel and collar overlays join the party in a rendered pink patent leather, a subtle nod to the bubble gum that Michael Jordan favoured through his NBA career. A detail that only further deepens the lore surrounding the Air Jordan brand, and the depth of the lineage created by the expansive and diverse selection of designs bracing the release calendar every year.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Metallic Purple

Matching purple Jumpman logos can be seen on its woven tongue tab and heel which brands this updated basketball design.Layered with luxury, the Air Jordan 4 Retro Metallic Purple features premium touches that transform this sporting classic into a streetwear staple.

The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Sisterhood is perfect if you're looking for a shoe that will look great no matter where you go.

The Air Jordan 4 Military Black is officially a must-have for your off-duty collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Multi-Color Womens

A clean, smoother rubber sole in white on the midsole and black on the outer completes the look and provides all the balance and comfort you need. This combination of yellow-gold and white makes for a bright summer look, a warm autumnal twist, or even to brighten up those winter days. A versatile sneaker in a bold colour option, the Air Jordan 1 Mid University Gold GS is a pair of shoes ready to make an impression.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro Fire Red 2020 Gs

Silver, reflective accents on the tongue retains the famed colourway, while hits of red adorn the lining, sole and Jumpman insignia. Underfoot, icy blue hues reveal the Air-cushioned unit, providing proof of Nike’s heritage and world-renowned comfort at work. Complete with fresh white laces, the Air Jordan Retro Fire Red White 2020 GS is a welcome addition to your kid’s collection.

fields.name: Jordan 4 Retro Metallic Orange

The rear of the Jordan 4 Retro Metallic Orange shoe also includes an overlapping ankle strap with a cut-out design, which then connects to extra-large eyelet accessories in a stunning metallic orange finish. The sneaker has another metallic orange eyelet to the bottom of the lacing panel, complementing the clean white laces on top. The bottom of the shoe reveals a visible Air Unit to the rear against a white rubber mid and outer sole. A pop of orange returns on top for the tongue’s border.

This Jordan 1 UNC patent leather build is intended as a women's model and looks set for All-Star weekend, the UNC Patent Leather is another beautiful addition to the Air Jordan family which is oozing with history and looks incredible while doing it.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Zoom Cmft Crater Purple
