Featuring a perforated toe box, its chenille-textured base is decorated with leather overlays, cut-out Swooshes and Jordan branding. Complete with an Air-cushioned midsole, a grip-enhancing outsole and secure laces, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Purple Chenille Womens is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Golf High X Eastside Golf Burnt Sunrise

data.description: Made in partnership with retailer Eastside Golf, the Air Jordan 1 Golf High x Eastside Golf Burnt Sunrise comes dressed in an understated colourway. Its leather upper is accented with Swoosh detailing as well as branding. The perforated toe box allows for ventilation, the Air midsole offers comfort and the secure lacing system means for a tailored fit. Finished with a textured rubber outsole, the Air Jordan 1 Golf High x Eastside Golf Burnt Sunrise is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Se Barely Green Womens

data.description: Green is an incredible colour when it comes to sneakers; the muted green of the Air Jordan 1 Low SE Barely Green Womens is light enough to be mistaken for the classic minimalistic white that the Air Jordans are famous for. When the light green is paired with the dusky light pink, it makes for a great combination, and really shows off this classic sneaker look to the best of its ability. These Womens Air Jordan 1 Low SE Barely Green sneakers have the perfect balance of stylish colours and classic construction, while making the most out of the iconic silhouette, with the comfort level you expect from Jordans. Womens Air Jordan 1 Low SE Barely Green's are the perfect sneakers for any look, casual or formal, on the street or in the gym.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Mulberry Purple Womens

data.description: Feel like royalty in this pair of Air Jordan 1 Low Mulberry Purple Womens sneakers with a premium leather upper in deep shades of mulberry purple. Embrace the classic design of the Jordan 1 silhouette, where black and purple combine for a bold finish. The premium leather upper runs with rich mulberry purple throughout, from the perforated toe box – perfect for extra breathability – right through to the heel. The side panel includes a black tumbled leather Nike Swoosh overlaid on the purple, while the heel tab includes an embroidered Air Jordan Wings logo in black. The top of the Womens Air Jordan 1 Low Mulberry Purple sneaker shows off deep black laces, black collar detailing, and a purple tongue. To the sole, you have a creamy white rubber midsole, complete with purple stitching, while the rubber outer sole returns to the bold mulberry shade.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Varsity Purple

data.description: After a hectic few months for the Jordan 1 Mid, we had a few weeks off from new colourways releasing. Fortunately enough, though, Jordan Brand is back with a brand new colourway of the highly sought after silhouette - the Jordan 1 Mid SE Purple The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Varsity Purple will most definitely be a fan favourite, looking to capitalise on the success and drawing inspiration from its high counterpart the Court Purple. The uppers are crafted from an eclectic mix of leathers, suedes and mesh. The iconic swoosh and wings logos of course feature, with the striking Jumpman logo featuring on the tongues of the shoes. At the bottom of the sneaker, we are greeted with a classic AJ1 midsole. This houses the full-length Nike Air unit that we already know guarantees comfort and enhances performance, whether on or off the court. If the Jordan 1 Mids recent success is anything to go by, the Jordan 1 Varsity Purple is guaranteed to be an instant classic.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro True Blue (2011)

data.description: The Air Jordan Retro True Blue dropped in 2011 in celebration of the popular silhouette’s 23rd anniversary. The Air Jordan 3 Retro True Blue 2011 sneakers stayed true to the original 1988 design, featuring a tumbled white leather upper contrasting with True Blue accents on the midsole, sock liner, eyelets, and the iconic Jumpman on the heel. A grey elephant print overlay along the toe, eyestay, and heel add texture and personality to the retro sneakers. Also, a pop of red on the tongue tab’s Jumpman adds vibrancy to the design. It’s a must-buy for any passionate sneaker fan’s collection, offering a retro design synonymous with Air Jordan 3.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Gs Light Smoke Grey

data.description: Translating the overwhelming appeal of the Dior custom to a more widespread audience, the Air Jordan 1 Mid GS ‘Light Smoke Grey’, which is set to drop in Spring 2020 is considered the prime base for one of the most luxury customs seen from the Jordan brand in quite some time. Aesthetically you can almost make a shot for shot comparison with its higher-end counterpart and it is a comparison this more affordable model embraces with open arms. The colour palette on the Jordan 1 Mid GS Light Smoke Grey remains unchanged, dressing the white base with Light Smoke Grey overlays and crisp panelling. Elsewhere, swooshes are struck with matte black in match to the darkened laces, lining, and staple Wings insignia, giving this shoe a truly breathtaking finish.

fields.name: Off-White X Air Jordan 2 Low White Red

data.description: A collaboration for the history books: Virgil Abloh, Michael Jordan and Nike’s Phil Knight have teamed up to bring you the Air Jordan 2 Low x Off-White White Red. The Air Jordan 2 was released with a softer midsole and more bounce to protect the ankle, but with a luxurious leather upper to bridge the gap between fashion and sports. Off-White’s rendition of the AJ2 nods to the original with its white and red colourway and Jordan’s signature sketched onto the side. No Off-White collab would be complete without the brand’s signature typography on the medial side walls which this iteration stylishly sports. Finished with a custom hang tag, the collaborative Air Jordan 2 Low x Off-White White Red is not one to be missed.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Black Royal Blue

data.description: Introducing a fresh take on a classic favourite, the Air Jordan 1 Low Black Royal Blue features a striking colourway making it a must-have for your sneaker collection. Crafted with premium leather, these shoes showcase a stylish mix of black, varsity blue sitting on a white rubber outsole, creating a nice contrast to this iconic design. Enjoy unmatched comfort with the padding in the collar that delivers extra cushioning, while the lacing system ensures a secure fit. Elevate your sneaker game with the Air Jordan 1 Mid Black Royal Blue.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Atmosphere Td

data.description: Taking on a colourway inspired by the vast amount of gum that Micheal Jordan chewed on-court, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Atmosphere TD is a muted must-have made for your kid’s collection. Smooth navy leather overlays dress the pair with versatility, with a matching deep blue Swoosh decorating its white central panel. A bubblegum pink patent collar, heel and perforated toe box add a glint of personality to this mini AJ1, whilst a stamped Wings logo and Nike Air tongue label brand it with simple Nike excellence. An Air-cushioned midsole and a dusty pink outsole ground this delicate sneaker with signature comfort as well as all-important grip. Treat your mini-me to the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Atmosphere TD, a versatile shoe with a playful story that your little one will love.

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Retro Concord 2018

data.description: Channelling the 1995 original pair in a lot of ways, this December 2018 release is a welcome reboot of a classic kick. The Air Jordan 11 Retro Concord 2018 stands alone as an iconic trainer, sporting the "45" on its heels as a nod to Michael Jordans and the number he wore upon his return to basketball following his first retirement, and the rest of this shoe isn't short of nostalgia either. This 2018 edition of a fan favourite, endeavours to keep all the shoe's signature details intact, including a white ballistic mesh upper and black patent leather that overlays an icy translucent outsole underfoot. The Jordan 11 Concord will also come in the OG box, something that will please a lot of old school sneakerheads, this shoe isn't just a collector's item, it is very much on trend, and will put you on point for 2018, whether be in the streets or on the court.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Varsity Red Ps

data.description: Treat your kid to the classic Air Jordan 1 High OG Varsity Red PS, an iconic ‘80s basketball silhouette laced with retro appeal. Crafted with a smooth white leather base, this scaled-down AJ1 is decorated with vibrant red overlays as well as a soft chenille Swoosh on its side. A grey ankle panel adds subtle depth to the bold shoe and is complemented by the matching corduroy-style tongue and the Wings logo that sits on the red collar panel. An Air-cushioned midsole works alongside the perforated toe box to allow for ultimate levels of reliable comfort, meaning that your little one will never want to wear any other sneaker. Grounded by a grippy red outsole, the Air Jordan 1 High OG Varsity Red PS is the perfect pair to kick start your mini-me’s collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High X Spider-Man Across The Spider-Verse Red Black Ps

data.description: Celebrating the release of Spider-Man: Across The Spider-Verse, the Air Jordan 1 High x Spider-Man Across The Spider-Verse Red Black PS comes dressed in vibrant superhero-inspired tones. Utilising a mixture of materials, its patchwork-style upper features patterned overlays and touches of branding. Offering classic Air cushioning and a grippy rubber outsole, the playful Air Jordan 1 High x Spider-Man Across The Spider-Verse Red Black PS is the perfect addition to any kid’s collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Washed Denim Gs

data.description: This fashionable pair of classic Air Jordan 1 Low Washed Denim GS sneakers comes in Grade School sizing for a playful and stylish look. The Air Jordan 1 Low Washed Denim GS sneaker comes in timeless acid wash denim in a light blue hue, running around the toe, across the main front straps, up along the eyelet panel and around the collar. It’s also wrapped around the main heel tab, on which is embroidered a white Air Jordan Wings logo to the back. The rest of the Air Jordan 1 Low Washed Denim GS' upper shows off a smooth white premium leather across the mid sides and along the perforated toe box. A striking blue Nike Swoosh in leather adorns the side, while the blue repeats for the laces, fabric collar detailing, and for the eye-catching rubber outer sole combined with a clean white rubber midsole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Low X Psg Light Bone

data.description: Introducing a collaboration that pays tribute to the iconic Paris Saint-Germain football club, the Air Jordan 6 Low x PSG Light Bone celebrates legends on both the court and field. It sports a leather upper, complemented by suede touches. Notable details include a mix of grey tones inspired from the Champs-Élysées, while the heel label shouts out to Paris Saint-Germain's stadium. The Nike Air delivers breathability, making each step feel like a breeze. Completed with a translucent rubber outsole, the Air Jordan 6 Low x PSG Light Bone Perfectly unites both sport and style in one special pair.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Craft Inside Out Tan Brown

data.description: Sporting a muted colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Low Craft Inside Out Tan Brown puts a deconstructed twist on the retro basketball model. Crafted with suede and canvas materials, its upper is accented with stitched detailing, frayed edges, sidewall Swooshes and Jordan branding. Underfoot, the Air midsole offers comfort and the rubber outsole provides effective grip. Padding in the collar adds extra cushioning, while the secure lace closure puts you in control of the fit. Find your size with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro White Cement Reimagined (2023)

data.description: Celebrating the model’s 35th anniversary, the Air Jordan 3 Retro White Cement Reimagined (2023) pays homage to the OG AJ3 from 1988. Boasting retro aesthetics, its leather upper features elephant print overlays, perforated sections, iconic branding and TPU eyelets. The visible Air unit in the midsole offers comfort, the rubber outsole allows for grip and padding in the collar adds extra support. Buy and sell the Air Jordan 3 Retro White Cement Reimagined (2023) with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Black Cactus Flower Womens

data.description: The Nike Air Jordan 1 is one of those silhouettes that’ll never go out of style, and the next pair to add to your collection is the Air Jordan 1 Low Black Cactus Flower Womens. The upper is crafted from smooth leather with supple suede overlays, while the tongue boasts a nylon composition. The toe box is scattered with breathable perforations and Nike’s Swoosh sits in its usual place on the sidewalls. Underfoot, Air cushioning delivers the comfort and bounce the AJ1 is known for, while Michael Jordan’s signature Jumpman and Wings motif are featured on the heel and tongue. Presented in a black, white and pink finish, the Air Jordan 1 Low Black Pink will brighten up any everyday rotation.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Fire Red Td (2022)

data.description: The Air Jordan 3 Retro Fire Red TD colourway is the perfect place to start when selecting your toddler's first AJ3 sneakers. After all, it was the original colourway that introduced the world to the iconic Jumpman logo, which appears in red on the white tongue. The crisp white tumbled leather upper allows the crimson red collar, mudguard, and eyelets to pop. Adding balance to the design are the light grey eyestays and elephant print overlays on the forefoot and foxing. Finishing off the design is the red Nike branding at the heel, ensuring people can't help but notice the cool brand on your child's feet. In addition to appearing effortlessly stylish, your toddler will feel comfortable due to the two-tone foam midsole that provides lightweight, responsive cushioning to support them as they run, walk, and play.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Cardinal Red

data.description: The first Jordan sneaker to don the now-famous Jumpman logo, the Air Jordan 3 remains to this day a fan-favourite silhouette - and the Air Jordan 3 Cardinal Red is an icon. Crafted from tumbled leather, instantly recognisable elephant-print panels are added to the heel and toe for extra texture. Pops of red can be found on the mudguard, insole and Jumpman branding, while Tinker Hatfield’s world-famous Air unit sits underfoot to deliver optimised comfort and performance. A legendary shoe that deserves a place in your collection, get your hands on the Air Jordan 3 Cardinal Red and reserve them for those special occasions.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Neutral Grey Gs

data.description: A tonal take on the original basketball silhouette, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Neutral Grey GS is an effortless everyday essential. Crafted with premium leather, the upper hosts Swoosh and Wings branding, breathable perforations and a secure lace-up fastening. Underfoot cushioning delivers comfort and support, while a textured tread rounds off the design. Buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 Mid Neutral Grey GS with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Palomino Gs

data.description: Offering stylish versatility and premium materials, the Air Jordan 3 Palomino GS puts a luxurious twist on the retro basketball model. Its suede and leather upper features tan-toned elephant print panelling, perforations and Jordan emblems. Air cushioning underfoot delivers comfort, the textured outsole provides traction and classic laces allow for a secure fit. Elevate any everyday look with the Air Jordan 3 Palomino GS.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Zoom Space Hippie

data.description: This week's Jordan 1 release sees the brand take a step toward sustainability with the release of the 'Zoom Space Hippie'. The sneakers are packed with environmentally friendly elements to ensure you are not only looking fresh but protecting the planet too. The sneaker is crafted mostly from a sustainable charcoal canvas upper with a contrasting white and multicoloured sole. The shoe also features exposed red stitching on the heel, a design aspect that we have seen previously on the hugely successful Union Jordan 1's. A zoom tab features just below the wings logo on the ankle of the silhouette. The top of the sneaker and the tongue have exposed foam, a look made famous with Virgil Abloh's Off-White collaborations previously. Nike's GRIND initiative produces the midsole of the sneaker, constructed from rubber scraps. The white outsole is made up of recycled plastic too. If you are looking to add a fresh pair of Jordans to the rotation and want to keep it sustainable, this is the sneaker for you.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Se True Blue Gs

data.description: Loosely inspired by the shape of the AJ3s released in 1988, the smaller-sized Air Jordan 1 Low SE True Blue is a bold addition to the iconic Air Jordan collection. With the striking True Blue colour being showcased in the shoe's lining and outsole, muted grey overlays and a ‘colourless’ white base balance the pair to create this quirky classic. True Blue elements are also incorporated throughout the shoe, such as the embroidered Jumpman on the tongue and Wings on the textured elephant print mudguard and eyestays. The distinct Air Jordan 1 Low SE True Blue will make a statement in your collection, are you brave enough to take them on?

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Cool Grey Gs

data.description: Taking its cues from the original ‘Cool Grey’ Air Jordan 11, the Air Jordan 6 Cool Grey GS utilises premium leather and advanced technology to deliver a functional yet fashionable sneaker. The upper is crafted with tumbled leather panels, while carefully placed perforations are added throughout for optimised air flow. Underfoot, Air cushioning ensures comfort and performance, while up top, a toggle fastening, Jumpman branding and extra padding work together to round off the design.

fields.name: Air Jordan 12 X Eastside Golf Cream Brown

data.description: Nike is changing golf style one sneaker at a time, which is why you shouldn't overlook this unique iteration of the Air Jordan 12. In collaboration with East Side Golf, the sneaker giant has created a more modern AJ1 design that will allow you to stand out on any golf course for the right reasons. Crafted from premium leather, you can trust the sneakers will feel comfortable and supportive on your feet, which is ideal for completing an 18-hole golf course. The cream upper with metallic gold accents allows the sneakers to match many outfits and blends stylishly with a mud-splatter burnt orange effect at the heel with a matching toe and outsole. Eastside Golf gives the design its seal of approval with its logo on the tongue and colourful hangtag. You'll find the iconic Jumpman and Jordan brand on the black heel pull, finishing the shoe's sleek design.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Se Craft Olive

data.description: Championing premium aesthetics, the Air Jordan 4 SE Craft Olive puts a stylish spin on the ‘80s basketball silhouette. Sporting a khaki-toned colourway and classic Jordan branding, its upper is made from a mixture of suede and leather materials. Its rubber sole unit houses Air cushioning and offers effective grip on a range of terrains, while secure laces put you in control of the fit. Rounded off with collar padding for extra comfort, elevate your off-duty looks with the Air Jordan 4 SE Craft Olive.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Shadow 2.0

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 High OG Shadow 2.0 draws clear inspiration from one of the most iconic AJ1 colourways of all time. The mix of black and grey makes the shoe instantly recognisable, and despite the slight difference in colour blocking, we expect the Jordan 1 Shadow 2.0 to be one of the best releases this year. Black leather underlays are the foundation of this sneaker, with the legendary Jordan 1 panelling featuring in a grey hue. However, these panels feature in a buttery suede material differing from the leather used for the Jordan 1 OG Shadow. Underfoot, a classic Air Jordan 1 sole unit features in a crisp white colourway for the midsole and a black outsole. This sole unit houses Nike Air technology which runs the entire length of the sole. This technology makes the Air Jordan 1 Retro High Shadow 2.0 one of the most comfortable sneakers on the market.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low 85 Neutral Grey

data.description: Embrace a clean and minimalist design with the Air Jordan 1 Low 85 Neutral Grey. These shoes feature a base of white leather complemented by grey accents on the tongue branding, Swoosh, heel and rubber outsole. The yellowed midsoles bring a vintage touch and classic style. Crafted from genuine leather, the upper ensures long-lasting wear, while the solid rubber outsole provides superb traction on various surfaces. The Air sole unit guarantees light cushioning for all-day comfort, making the Air Jordan 1 Low 85 Neutral Grey, the perfect mix of functionality and sophistication.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Midnight Navy Ps

data.description: Boasting a versatile colourway, the Air Jordan 4 Retro Midnight Navy PS presents a smaller-sized Jordan packed with the same big impact. Its leather base is decorated with speckled overlays, grid mesh cut-outs and Jumpman detailing. Underfoot, the Air midsole offers comfort and the rubber outsole provides effective grip. Complete with navy eyestay accents, the Air Jordan 4 Retro Midnight Navy PS is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Gs Arctic Punch

data.description: If you’re a fan of playful pastel colours you can make an impression with, this pair of Air Jordan 1 Low GS Arctic Punch sneakers is set to stun. This shoe combines soft pink with delicate lilac to contrast with clean white panelling, providing a bright and exciting look. The GS model means a more comfortable fit for those with narrower feet, and its cushioned sole means maximum durability every time. The pastel colours of the Air Jordan 1 Low GS Arctic Punch are balanced by accents of white included on the laces, side panels, midsole, and toe tab, giving an altogether clean and fresh look, no matter the season. A lilac collar and tongue edge give an attractive border to the Air Jordan 1 Low GS Arctic Punch sneaker’s silhouette, and a soft lilac outer sole completes the look.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Ko High White Black

data.description: A must-have from Nike’s celebrated Jordan collection, the Air Jordan 1 KO High White Black arrives in a neutral colour scheme, perfect for slipping into your daily rotation. Crafted with a breathable canvas base in white, fabric grey overlays run across the toe box, side panel and eyestays for contrast. On the side, Nike’s Swoosh tick sets the tone in black, with further branding is found on the collar and tongue. The cushioned sole plays host to the world-renowned Air unit for optimised comfort and performance, while a functional pull tab allows you to slip this kick on and off with ease. A fresh all-round shoe, make the Air Jordan 1 KO High White Black Grey a mainstay in your shoedrobe.

fields.name: Air Jordan 2 High Chicago

data.description: Heavily inspired by the Chicago edition from 1986, the Air Jordan 2 High Chicago puts a modern spin on the iconic design. The smooth leather base is decorated with textured overlays, classic branding and touches of red. Perforations allow for ventilation and the rubber heel piece offers added support. Underfoot, the Air midsole delivers comfort and the textured outsole provides effective grip. Padding in the collar gives extra cushioning and the secure lacing system puts you in control of the fit. Find your size with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Golf Shattered Backboard

data.description: With its renowned colourway and tailored features, the Air Jordan 1 Low Golf Shattered Backboard is guaranteed to have you swinging into action. Crafted with Air midsole cushioning and an intricate toothy tread, this shoe has carefully been formed to deliver maximum performance. With licks of tangerine on the perforated toe box, heel and outsole, as well as textured white leather panels, this AJ1 model delivers high-quality style. Highlighting MJ’s love for the sport, the Air Jordan 1 Low Golf Shattered Backboard is a must-have, whether you’re into golf or a fan of iconic sneaker culture.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Motorsports

data.description: The Air Jordan 4 Motorsports was released to the general public in March 2017 and draws inspiration from the 2006 Friends and Family designed to commemorate the 4th Anniversary of Michael Jordan Motorsport Racing team. Incorporating the teams' white, black and varsity blue colours, but removes the Mars Blackmon heel accent that graced the '06 originator. Despite being several decades old, there’s something timeless about the Jordan 4 silhouette. When it first debuted, it was way ahead of its time, and even now it boasts impressive comfort and durability. As such, you can expect a shoe which more than rivals the modern day releases.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Fierce Pink Ps

data.description: Introducing a timeless favourite that stands the test of time, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Fierce PS boasts a leather upper, harmonised with a vibrant and pastel pink that envelops the Wings, the Swooshes and the iconic Jumpman logo on the tongue. Rounded off with a rubber outsole that delivers good traction, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Fierce PS perfectly blends superior comfort and classic style for active feet.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Brushstroke Paint Splatter

data.description: The Nike Dunk is one of the most sought-after sneakers in the game currently. With colourways like the recent Dunk 'Cider', it is easy to see why. The upper combines a mix of materials, with luxurious leather and plush suede both used. A colour combination of burnt orange, chocolate brown, and stealthy black earn the shoe its nickname. Legendary Dunk details feature throughout, with the iconic Nike Swoosh branding stars across the lateral and medial sides of the silhouette. Nike Air branding is also present on the tongue and heel tab. A Dunk sole unit completes the sneakers design, complimenting the uppers perfectly with a black midsole and brown outsole. This sole unit houses Nike Air technology, guaranteeing comfort wherever you rock them.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Volt Gold Gs

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 had an excellent 2020 with some of the year's best releases falling under the Jordan Brand banner. Well, Jordan shows no signs of slowing down, starting 2021 with an incredible take on the iconic silhouette. The sneakers uppers feature the signature panelling that is one of Jordan Brands most iconic designs. White underlays are emphasised by an eclectic mix of blacks, yellows and volt. Legendary brandings such as the swoosh and wings logo feature in their usual spots on the shoes' lateral and medial sides. Down below, a traditional Jordan sole unit houses Nike Air technology that guarantees comfort whether you rock them on the court or the streets. Start the year off right by picking up a pair of Air Jordan 1's; you won't regret it.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 X Psg White Neutral Grey Bordeaux

data.description: Paris Saint-Germain again join forces with Jordan Brand to bring us the incredible PSG Air Jordan 4. The French football giants have teamed up with Jordan Brand for collaborations previously, bringing out an apparel line alongside an Air Jordan 5 back in 2018. The Air Jordan 4 is an iconic silhouette, having seen multiple exquisite collaborations this year already with Union LA and Off-White. But the PSG x Air Jordan may be the best of the bunch. The sneaker comes dressed in an extremely clean white and grey upper, with pops of Bordeaux burgundy throughout to contrast the minimalist design perfectly. This collaboration ventures away from the traditional colours of PSG for the first time, opting to tone it down for a sleeker appearance. A tag on the front of the Air Jordan 4 PSG features the wording 'PANAME', a nickname for the French capital city. The heel of the sneaker features the iconic Jumpman logo but is inside of the PSG club badge. Two legendary logos become one in this co-branding. Underfoot, Air Max technology features to ensure these sneakers are ready for the court or the streets. The air bubble is once again visible to give you them OG feels. The PSG Air Jordan 4 collabs always attract fans from all over the world; we expect the same for this Jordan 4. A must-have for sneakerheads around the globe.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Georgetown Gs

data.description: The Air Jordan 3 will forever be a favourite silhouette amongst sneakerheads. This upcoming Midnight Navy version may be the best new colourway we have seen in some time. The uppers are dripping in the Midnight Navy colourway, with premium, buttery leather used throughout the design. That same Midnight Navy is used for the iconic Jumpman logo that features the shoe's tongue. The blue hues are complimented perfectly by the elephant print accents that feature on the sneaker's toe box and heel. Underfoot, a white sole unit houses Nike Air technology, which is on show due to the legendary visible air bubble that Tinker Hatfield used in the OG model. The Air Jordan 3 will always have a place in the history books, be sure to add a pair to your collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 2 X J Balvin Blue

data.description: The Jordan Brand has embarked on another exciting collaboration with J Balvin, a famous Colombian singer. You’ll feel like you’re walking on air when donning a pair of Air Jordan 2 x J Balvin Blue sneakers. The sky-inspired colourway reflects the original silhouette with a fresh update, as it has a cloud-filled heel counter that complements a light blue leather and synthetic upper. The cloudy scene appears again on the plush sock liner and insoles, which will boost your comfort and support when walking down the street or shooting hoops on a basketball court. A yellow smiley face features on the heel counter and even features J Balvin’s lightning symbol to create the eyes.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Cacao Wow Gs

data.description: Make room in your wardrobe for a pair that effortlessly bridges the gap between trendy design and functionality. The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Cacao Wow GS boasts a suede upper transitioning from a soft sandy tone to a deep brown, while pale yellow Swooshes adorn the sides and Jordan logos. The design is completed by a two toned rubber sole that delivers both durability and comfort. In the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Cacao Wow GS, heritage and style take centre stage, promising a timeless touch to your everyday look.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Red White Gs

data.description: A classic red and white colourway stands out on this even more classic silhouette, with this vibrant pair of Air Jordan 1 Low Red White GS sneakers. Here, in a GS edition for smaller and narrower shoe sizes, the Air Jordan 1 Low Red White GS sneaker combines a premium leather upper with a cushioned rubber sole for maximum comfort and style. The upper is crafted from sleek red leather panels on the eyelet strip, front side panels, and heel tab. The iconic Nike Swoosh is shown vibrantly in the same shade of bold red, a colour that is replicated on the rubber outer sole for a more eye-catching step. White premium leather is then included on the side panels and the perforated toe box. Crisp and clean white laces allow the red eyelet strip to pop, while a white cushioned tongue with red labelling completes the look of the Air Jordan 1 Low Red White GS sneaker.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Infrared 2022

data.description: One of the most in-demand silhouettes of the moment, the Air Jordan 4 is taking over the game and the Air Jordan 4 Infrared 2022 is no exception. Sporty, versatile and bang on trend, the Jordan 4 Infrared sneaker utilises premium materials, instantly recognisable branding and industry-leading technology to deliver a kick that you’ll want to wear every single day. The upper of the Jordan 4 Infrared 2022 is crafted from supple nubuck, while caged panels cover breathable mesh that’s added for enhanced ventilation. Sporting a clean grey design with hits of Nike’s legendary “Infrared”, Michael Jordan’s Jumpman motif rounds things off on the tongue and heel. A kick that deserves to be right at the top of your wishlist, add the Air Jordan 4 Infrared 2022 to your rotation now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Stage Haze Gs

data.description: Meet the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Stage Haze GS, a simple pair that you’ll swear by. Its smooth white leather base is layered with cracked black leather overlays and a matching Swoosh, complete with its soft suede heel panel and a coordinating grippy outsole. Trademark Air cushioning makes this sleek shoe a must-have for completing any everyday task. Adding subtle detail to the sneaker’s grey-scale colourway, the shoe is finished with a black Wings logo stamped on the crisp white collar panel and light pink stitched Nike Air branding on the tongue tab. The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Stage Haze GS is an essential for anyone who craves a switch-up from their existing go-to pair.

fields.name: A Ma Maniere X Air Jordan 2 Sail Burgundy

data.description: This pair of A Ma Maniere x Air Jordan 2 Sail Burgundy sneakers gives off a luxuriously formal design, with an elegant soft shaping and soft fabric upper you’ll want to wear time and again. The shoe reveals an overlapped light grey suede upper, running from toe to collar, with subtle perforated detailing running in a line from the toe cap to the mid. The black laces add a bold touch to complement the soft grey hue behind, while the heel tab shows off a rich brown leather. For the sole, you have a black reptile-skin finish for another touch of luxury, coupled with white and soft-grey rubber for the outer sole. Detailed with Jordan emblems and Swooshes, its leather upper also features a perforated toe box for ventilation. Air cushioning underfoot offers comfort, its rubber outsole provides grip and classic laces allow for a tailored fit. Update your kid’s collection with the Air Jordan 1 High OG University Blue PS.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Strawberries And Cream Womens

data.description: Sporting a pink-toned colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Strawberries And Cream Womens presents a playful take on the retro basketball model. Made with high-quality leather, its upper is decorated with branding and features a perforated toe box for ventilation. The Air-cushioned midsole offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Update your collection with the Air Jordan 1 Mid Strawberries And Cream Womens.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Varsity Royal

data.description: Designed by living legend Tinker Hatfield, the Air Jordan 3 is receiving new love in the way of the Varsity Royal colourway dropping for Summer 2020. Crafted from premium quality grained leather and mesh, the uppers take on a clean Royal Blue look, with grey and black detailings showcasing the legendary cracked effect. The padded tongue showcases a blue Jumpman logo, while the heel is also embellished with this iconic logo. Underfoot, a white rubber midsole unit encases a visible Nike Air unit at the heel alongside additional cushioning to make these a solid option for both on and off the court.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Where The Wild Things Are Gs

data.description: Dubbed one of the greatest Jordan silhouettes of all time, the Air Jordan 4 Retro Where The Wild Things Are GS is no exception to this statement. A sturdy sneaker with endless styling appeal, this Jordan silhouette is famed for being one of Michael Jordan’s personal favourites. The cosy sneaker nods to the original 1989 design with its caged inserts, Air cushioning and Jumpman logo detailing. This grade-school iteration is also elevated with toasty shearling panels, bold lace anchors and an ultra-wearable beige upper. A muted must-have pair, add the playful Nike Air Jordan 4 GS “Wild Things” to your collection and you’ll never want to take them off.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High University Blue Td
Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Diy Gs

data.description: If you’re a fan of customisable Air Jordan options, then this pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid SE DIY GS takes that to a whole new level. With a premium leather upper that acts as a colouring book for your own design inspiration, complete with artistic shapes and doodles, this is a shoe you can truly make your own. This is emphasised by the completely clear Nike Swoosh included on the side, which ensures that any Swoosh colouring won’t affect your own personal design scheme. The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE DIY GS is a sneaker that looks good even without personal updates, with a fresh white background and thin black design shapes to make an impression. This is topped off by a black heel strap, black ankle strap, and black laces, finished with a sleek black collar. The Air Jordan Wings logo completes the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE DIY GS' creative retro feel by coming in a neon shade of yellow.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Multi Patent Womens

data.description: This pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid Multi Patent Womens combines not only a variety of colours but also a variety of fabric textures. This pair of sneakers comes with a colour palette bordering on retro vibes, with a vibrant combination of red, green, blue, grey, and orange, as well as an elegant black panelling that helps the other colours to stand out. The textured and layered appearance of this versatile sneaker is also made more interesting by the inclusion of glossy black leather as well as the coloured panels. The Nike swoosh stands out prominently in white against the rainbow of colours, and this works to match the white outer sole, which is cushioned for maximum comfort. Black laces work cohesively to run into the black leather panels, and the grey tongue adds a contrast at the top of the Womens Air Jordan 1 Mid Multi Patent.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Dark Iris

data.description: Retro and sporty in equal measure, the Air Jordan 3 Retro Dark Iris is an essential addition to your collection. This Air Jordan 3 iteration consists of a sleek white upper, offset by deep purple accents at the collar, eyelets and midsole. As expected, the iconic Jumpman logo features on the sneaker's tongue, also coming in Dark Iris. The grey elephant pattern found at the toe and heel balances perfectly with the white backdrop for an exciting addition. Underfoot, the chunky sole houses the visible Air unit Tinker Hatfield used in the OG model. The Air Jordan 3 Retro is soon to earn its place in the history books — be sure to add a pair to your shoedrobe.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Triple White (2022)

data.description: Freshen up your wardrobe with the timeless Air Jordan 1 Low Triple White (2022) sneakers. Released in September 2022, the sleek iteration banishes colour in favour of an all-white design. The cool footwear is covered in a smooth white leather from heel to toe, which includes its tongue tab Jumpman, lateral and medial Nike Swooshes, and the embroidered wings logo on the heel counter. There isn't a primary colour in sight, but it doesn't stop the sneaker from appearing bright and bold on the feet. If anything, the crisp hue elevates the classic silhouette, as it appears fresh, modern, and sophisticated, helping the sneakers to stand the test of time. The Nike Air cushioning decreases the shoe's weight and improves its flexibility, creating a more comfortable, lightweight feel.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Fire Red 2020

data.description: Finally, we get to see a re-release of one of the most iconic Air Jordan 4 colourways. We first saw The Air Jordan Fire Red's gracing the court back in '89 when Michael Jordan donned the Chicago Bulls coloured shoe. Little did any of us know that MJ and the Jordan Brand would become some of the biggest names in their respective industries. The Tinker Hatfield creation recently celebrated its 30th Birthday, indicating the perfect time to retro a classic. The Jordan 4 Fire Red comes crafted from only the best leathers, with a clean, white colourway dominating the colour palette. Black and red accents that feature throughout contrast the crisp upper perfectly. The branding used mirrors the OG exactly, with a Jumpman logo on the tongue and Nike Air on the heel. Sneakerheads love it when the Nike Air branding replaces the Jumpman on the heel, giving the Jordan 4 Retro Fire Red an even more retro feel. Down below, a red, white and black sole houses Nike Air technology to ensure these stand the test of time. A visible air unit also features, leaving no doubt this is a retro of the '89 original. It has been thirty-one years since we have seen an Air Jordan 4 Retro Fire Red, do not pass up the opportunity to add this legendary silhouette to your collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Zoom Cmft Fossil Stone

data.description: Just when you thought the Air Jordan couldn’t be more covetable, Nike go ahead and design the Air Jordan 1 Zoom CMFT Fossil Stone. Reworking the original basketball silhouette, the perforated toe box and side panel come in a neutral canvas, overlaid by a clay-coloured mudguard and heel panel. Nike’s signature branding is highlighted through the white Swoosh on the side and Wings insignia on the collar. The unfinished edges running across the laterals create a deconstructed design, enhanced by the speckled crater foam midsoles and black-mint outsoles. To finish, the padded collar cups the heel for a secure and comfy fit. Easy to style and even easier to wear, make the Air Jordan 1 Zoom CMFT Fossil part of your main collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Coconut Milk Grey Ps

data.description: Bringing a fresh take to the classic formula, the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Coconut Milk Grey PS is a prime addition to your little one’s sneaker collection. Air Jordan’s famed Wings branding appears on the ankle strap, complemented by a Jumpman tongue tag. Finished with a functional pulling tab, the Nike Air base and cushioned sole provide all-day comfort and support. Dark laces complete the look and air holes allow their feet to breathe. Easy to style thanks to the neutral palette, dress them up in the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Coconut for their next play date.

Easy to style and even easier to love, add the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Red Pomegranate to your sneaker shelf now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air Comfort Black Monarch

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 High Zoom CMFT is the latest offering from Jordan Brand, and it is one of the best releases we will see in 2021. The colourway has similarities to the Nike Dunk Ceramic, which sneakerheads were so excited to see release last year. The uppers come crafted from buttery suede, with black underlays and a burnt orange hue used for the legendary Jordan panels. The iconic swoosh detailing features down both lateral and medial sides of the sneaker and come in white to contrast the uppers perfectly. Nike Air branding on the tongue has been switched out for Zoom Air, with Zoom Air cushioning running the length of the sole unit. The Zoom Air unit is housed within an OG Jordan 1 sole unit, rounding off the design of the shoe. A must-have for Jordan collectors, the Black Monarch is seriously impressive.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Spruce Aura Womens

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Low silhouette is a classic, and no matter the colourway, it's always going to be a versatile wear for the courts or for the streets. The Air Jordan 1 Low Spruce Aura Womens edition comes in a soft colour palette with fresh white and dove grey for a more minimalistic look. The premium leather upper of the Women's Air Jordan 1 Low Spruce Aura sneaker comes in a matte finish throughout, with a white perforated toe box and a white main mid-panel. The rest of the upper is crafted from soft grey leather, shown around the toe, front side panels, eyestay strip, collar detailing and main heel tab. The side Nike Swoosh comes in the soft grey hue against white, while the Wings logo on the heel comes in soft flecked fabric. Soft grey laces and a light grey fabric tongue come on top, with a white midsole and grey outer sole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Chicago

data.description: For an authentic classic design in an elegant silhouette, go for the Air Jordan 1 Mid Chicago in rich shades of red, offset by panels of white and black features. The prominent Nike swoosh is displayed in black, looking bold against the minimalist colours of the rest of the sneaker. An air-cushioned sole means maximum comfort all day long, whether you’re hitting the courts or the streets. The cushioned sole is brought to life by the deep red colouring on the outer sole of the Air Jordan 1 Mid Chicago, contrasted perfectly by the white midsole. Black laces blend attractively against the red eyelet panel, and a mid collar reach means exceptional support and comfort, bordered by black panelling. The Air Jordan wing logo is stamped in black against red leather to finish the Air Jordan 1 Mid Chicago.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid University Gold

data.description: Flashes of gold leather make the Air Jordan 1 Mid University Gold's a truly special pair of sneakers for those who love bolder, royal colours. The statement gold colour is included on the ankle leather, the toe, the heel, and most prominently on the iconic Nike swoosh. A clean, smooth rubber sole in black and white wraps up the Air Jordan 1 Mid University Gold and contrasts perfectly with the rich autumnal colours to give a warm look with exceptional comfort in mind. Black laces and a black collar adds bold and sophisticated contrast for a versatile pair of sneakers ready to make an impression — a must-have for lovers of yellow, gold, and black.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Alternate Bred Gs

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid Alternate Bred GS is a reimagining of the brand’s famous Black Red (abbreviated to Bred) colourway. Crafted from premium materials, the sneakers will look and feel soft and luxurious on your feet. The predominately all-black leather upper adds stealth and sophistication to the silhouette while helping the design match most everyday outfits. Splashes of red give the sneakers vibrancy and personality, as the hue appears on the toe box, laces, ankle flap, sock lining, insoles, and Nike Swooshes on the lateral and medial sidewalls. A crisp white midsole helps balance the competing colours to create an attractive aesthetic to match many tastes. The sneakers won’t disappoint for comfort and support, offering a padded ankle collar, an encapsulated Air-Sole unit, and a durable red rubber outsole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Golf Bred

data.description: This timelessly retro Air Jordan 4 Golf Bred sneaker here gets a bold and deep upgrade with a stylish black finish with subtle pops of red and light grey. The soft nubuck upper shows off curved panels in stylish black, which break in the middle for a mesh fabric panel, also in black. This is overlaid by a black strap accessory, leading to extra-large eyestays in light grey against the black lacing panel. The tongue shows off a border of rich red, complementing the light grey fabric of the collar. To the sole, you have light grey mudguards, as well as black mudguards behind, and a white midsole revealing a visible Air Unit. For the rubber outer sole of the Air Jordan 4 Golf Bred sneaker, you have grey semi-translucent panelling to the centre, while the front and heel of the sole reveal a subtle red hue behind.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Satin Black Toe Womens

data.description: 2019s edition of one of the most popular colourways for Michael Jordan's first silhouette. The Air Jordan 1 Satin Black Toe comes as a womens exclusive decorated in black, white and Varsity Red with an upper that's constructed of leather and satin. Putting an exclamation point on this excellent design, the shoe comes complete with the iconic wings logo presented in metal with the everpresent swoosh dressed in black. Completing the look is a white midsole and red outsole with a pivot point tread pattern.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Team Red Gs

data.description: If you're searching for a unique pair of sneakers to elevate your daily style, you'll not regret choosing the Air Jordan 1 Mid Team Red GS colourway. The smooth leather upper replaces its signature white colour with a light grey hue and stylishly contrasts with Team Red leather overlays, such as the heel counter, collar flap, toe cap, and eyestay panel. Yet, the crisp white midsole creates a fresher aesthetic and is balanced with a light grey rubber outsole. In addition to the Nike Swooshes, people are sure to notice the white wings motif on the collar flaps and the white Jumpman on the red tongue and insoles.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Cmft Cool Grey Light Blue Womens

data.description: The premium upper of this pair of Air Jordan 1 High Zoom CMFT Cool Grey Light Blue Womens sneakers shows off delicate grey nubuck in premium quality for a smooth, luxurious look. The perforated toe box, front side panels, main mid-panel, heel panel, and ankle strap all come in this soft grey shading, which is overlaid over a back section of light blue nubuck, revealed by the Nike Swoosh cut out along the side. The soft blue hue returns for the Air Jordan Wings logo on the ankle strap, as well as on the layered collar panel behind. The laces, eyelet panel, and fabric tongue also get the same soft grey treatment, while the rubber midsole breaks up the colour with a flash of clean white. The rubber outer sole then returns to the light shade of blue.

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Retro 25Th Anniversary

data.description: Celebrating the iconic silhouettes 25th Birthday, we see the Jordan 11 release in a limited-edition Anniversary colourway. The sneaker made famous by Michael Jordan way back in 1995, this Jordan 11 is certain to turn the heads of passers-by. The sneaker comes composed from a mix of patent leather, mesh and natural leathers with these premium materials ensuring you get that luxurious vibe. You will find the iconic Jumpman logo on the heels of the shoe, coming in shiny, silver metal. In a further nod to the OG silhouette, Jordan lettering features on the shoe eyelets. One noticeable switch up, however, is the number 23 changes to 25 in honour of the anniversary. Underfoot, a white midsole is finished off with a translucent outsole. This sole houses Nike Air technology that will give you optimum comfort whether you are on the court or the street. This 25th Anniversary sneaker is most definitely going to hit grail status amongst Jordan enthusiasts, be sure to add them to your collection.

The Jordan Brand is taking the time to transform golf attire for the better, creating unique AJ12 designs to boost confidence and comfort on the golf course. It doesn't matter if you're on the green or streets; you can trust this modern interpretation of the 1996 silhouette will turn many heads. The premium tumbled white leather upper will pop on any course and helps the French Blue reptilian leather mudguard to stand out even more. The metallic silver eyelets create a little luxury and flank the French Blue Jumpman on the white tongue. Of course, the finest feature for golf fans is, without question, the semi-translucent outsole with seven removable spikes, which will improve traction on a golf course.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Black White Multi-Color Womens

Moving along the upper, you have a rich green eyelet panel, blue collar, brown ankle strap, and glossy black leather panelling for a multi-coloured design finish that truly packs a punch. The Nike Air Swoosh is included with intricate black stitching along the white leather panel for a distinctive look, and the Nike Air Wings logo stands out in bold green against brown leather. If you're looking for a smart combination of colours, you can't go wrong with a pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Black White Multi-Color Womens sneakers.
