data.description: Jordan Brand continues its stellar 2021, releasing a retro of the Jordan 6 in Michael Jordan's favourite colourway. The Carmine Jordan 6 has been worn multiple times by MJ himself, so we can all but guarantee these will be a fan favourite. The uppers are composed of a mix of red and white materials, making these the perfect shoe for Chicago Bulls fans. The padded ankle detailing features whilst the heel-pull tab also features in black and red. The iconic Jumpman logo features on the sneaker's heel while the shoe's tongue features the Jumpmana logo and the legendary pull-tab. Underfoot, a retro-looking sole unit houses Nike Air technology. The mix of black, white and silver emphasises the colourway perfectly. An air bubble features reminding all of us that Tinker Hatfield created this iconic silhouette. A real 90s throwback, be sure to add the Carmine to your collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Volt Gold

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 had an excellent 2020 with some of the year's best releases falling under the Jordan Brand banner. Well, Jordan shows no signs of slowing down, starting 2021 with an incredible take on the iconic silhouette. The sneakers uppers feature the signature panelling that is one of Jordan Brands most iconic designs. White underlays are emphasised by an eclectic mix of blacks, yellows and volt. Legendary brandings such as the swoosh and wings logo feature in their usual spots on the shoes' lateral and medial sides. Down below, a traditional Jordan sole unit houses Nike Air technology that guarantees comfort whether you rock them on the court or the streets. Start the year off right by picking up a pair of Air Jordan 1's; you won't regret it.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Bred Toe 2.0 2023

data.description: Always on trend and able to reinvent any style, the Air Jordan 1 Low Bred Toe 2.0 2023 boasts a fusion of red, white and black in a sleek leather silhouette. It is named for its vibrant red toe box, adorned with sunburst perforations paying homage to the '80s classic. Signature details include a red Jumpman logo on the tongue and white Wings insignia on the heel. Enjoy unmatched comfort for your daily stride with a plush sock liner, grounded by a robust rubber sole. The Air Jordan 1 Low Bred Toe 2.0 2023 effortlessly blends style and practicality, making it a must-have in your collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Se Take Flight Gs

data.description: Offering up a fresh take on the classic design, the Air Jordan 1 Low SE Take Flight GS is playful and practical in equal measure. Drawing heavily on the original silhouette, the white base is crafted from smooth leather and features a clean white colourway. The graphic ‘Take Flight’ overlays take inspiration from Nike’s 3D glasses theme, dressed in a White Blue Hero and Bright Crimson colour scheme. Dual Swooshes in red and blue sit on the side, while the Jumpman logo takes pride of place tongue. Up top, breathable perforations on the toe box ensure optimised air flow, balanced with lightweight cushioning underfoot for all-day comfort. The Air Jordan 1 Low SE Take Flight Red GS is the perfect choice for your little one’s collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Triple Black

data.description: If you have always wanted to own one of Michael Jordan's original AJ1 designs, you shouldn't overlook the Mid Triple Black colourway. Despite releasing various new updates of its classic silhouette, the Jordan Brand understands you often cannot beat the originals. You may expect many changes to one of the brand's bestselling mid-tops, but it has received minor alterations ahead of its re-release. The smooth leather, all-black construction features its signature flat laces, black branding, and nylon tongue. Also, the solid sole units remain the same. The only difference you might notice is the Jumpman logo on the tongue tab is now black to maximise the stealthy aesthetic.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Metallic Silver Gs

data.description: Originally released as a low-top in 2002, the Air Jordan 6 Metallic Silver GS colourway made a welcome return as a high-top in 2022. The almost futuristic sneaker features an all-black synthetic leather upper to match most looks in your wardrobe. Air Jordan 6 fans will spot various heritage details, including an extended heel pull tab, perforated underlays, and a moulded tongue. Metallic silver accents shine a spotlight on the synonymous Air-Sole unit and foam midsole, helping the comfortable kicks stand out even more on your feet. The Metallic Silver colourway puts a stealthy, modern twist on the much-loved classic, which made its debut in 1991.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air Comfort Pink Glaze Womens

data.description: The construction of the elegant Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air Comfort Pink Glaze Womens shoe adds more depth and volume, with carefully crafted leather panels that have been layered more prominently over the side and back of the sneaker. The Nike Swoosh is given something a little different with this effect, as the Swoosh sits behind the side panel rather than atop it: the break in the white side panel reveals the brown-orange under layer in the Swoosh shape. The tumbled leather effect in soft pink combined with fresh white creates an attractive colourway, offset perfectly by the inclusion of black on the collar in patterned leather. A white perforated toebox provides extra breathability to the Womens Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air Comfort Pink Glaze, while a white midsole and pink glazed outer sole provide cushioned support with every step, resulting in a timeless High silhouette in a sophisticated hue.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey Ps (2022)

data.description: With its versatile colour palette and sleek aesthetic, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey PS is the monochromatic must-have for your little one. Light Smoke Grey overlays and a matching outsole contrasts the distinct black Swoosh and collar, adding depth to this classic design. More intricate details include the Jumpman featured on the label on the tongue and the classic Wings logo stamped on the collar’s overlay. Inspired by the very first AJ1, this Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey PS is the perfect shoe for your child’s introduction to the sneaker game.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement

data.description: Drawing inspiration from the White Cement colourway from 1989, the Air Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement champions heritage style and sporty aesthetics. Defined by its speckled red accents, grid panels and classic Jordan branding, its premium leather upper is complete with rubber overlays. The Air unit in its midsole delivers unmatched comfort, while its durable outsole provides grip. Rounded off with a secure lacing system, the Air Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement will never fail to impress.

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Cherry Ps

data.description: Updating the retro basketball shoe, the Air Jordan 11 Cherry PS is crafted using durable materials. Its mesh upper features patent mudguard panelling, Jordan branding and elongated lace loops. Air cushioning in its midsole delivers comfort, the icy rubber outsole provides grip and the speed lacing system allows for a secure fit. Refresh your kid’s rotation with the Air Jordan 11 Cherry PS.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Metallic Pack White Red

data.description: The metallic effect was first seen way back in 1986, when the same four colourways released as Air Jordan 1’s to great success. Since then, the Metallic Pack has been retroed twice, once in 2009 and once in 2016. For 2020, Nike will lend the effect to the AJ4, another legendary silhouette that was designed by the highly-coveted Tinker Hatfield. Each pair is crafted from high-quality tumbled leather for a luxury look throughout, while technical mesh and synthetic panels are also present. Red detailing features on the details including embroidered Jumpman logos at both the tongue and heel, while the model’s iconic visible Air unit is present as ever, offering both functionality and razor sharp looks.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Twist 2.0 Womens

data.description: Released in 2022, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Twist 2.0 was released to give its 2019 iteration a refresh. At first glance, you might believe the design has remained true to its original, but some clear differences make this iteration unique. For instance, the Twist 2.0 sneaker has replaced the Panda-style colour blocking for a more muted grey upper, which complements the black faux fur overlays. Another small but obvious change is the white Jordan Wings motif is replaced with a premium metallic silver alternative. The 2022 release features a grey sock liner. Finishing off the design is the white midsole that features the brand's signature Air cushioning and a black outsole for improved traction.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Se Celestial Gold Womens

data.description: Updating the classic AJ1 model, the vibrant Air Jordan 1 Low SE Celestial Gold Womens puts a modern twist on the retro basketball silhouette. Made from a mixture of canvas and suede, its upper features a perforated toe box, Jordan logos and embroidered Swooshes. Air cushioning underfoot offers comfort, its rubber outsole provides grip and secure laces complete the design. Buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 Low SE Celestial Gold Womens with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Starfish Ps

data.description: Made from premium materials, the Air Jordan 1 High OG Starfish PS takes on a colourway which is inspired by a variation of the iconic Hermès Birken Bag. Featuring a perforated toe box for ventilation, its leather upper is decorated with touches of signature branding. Air cushioning underfoot offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and the classic lacing system allows for a secure fit. Update your kid’s collection with the Air Jordan 1 High OG Starfish PS.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Nike Swoosh On Tour (2020)

data.description: Fans of a more minimalistic sneaker will love this fresh white offering, here in a special edition design in the Air Jordan 1 Mid silhouette. The premium upper of the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Nike Swoosh On Tour 2020 comes complete in white, with smooth white leather panels running from toe to heel. The leather switches to a breathable mesh fabric around the collar and behind the ankle strap. The white continues for the fabric tongue, laces, and sole. For the side Nike Swoosh, also in white, you have a more jagged cut variation on the classic Swoosh. At the toe of the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Nike Swoosh On Tour 2020 sneaker, you also have another small Nike Swoosh embroidered in white. The heel of the sneaker includes a silver label denoting European cities, while a touch of red is included for the Air Jordan Wings logo stitching on the heel strap. A white rubber mid and outer sole finishes this clean design.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Shimmer Womens

data.description: The Air Jordan 4 is one of the most striking silhouettes to come out of the Jordan Brand camp. The iconic design has lasted the test of time, with each colourway that drops exciting fans of the brand. The latest offering draws clear inspiration from the Off-White AJ4, and we expect the Jordan 4 Retro Shimmer to be an instant sell-out. The uppers of the Jordan 4 Shimmer come crafted from premium leather throughout, with a clean beige hue dominating the design. The legendary mesh panels and lace stays feature in the same colourway, whilst the Jumpman logo on the tongue comes dressed in metallic silver. Laces and the shoe's sock liner come in a white hue, contrasting the rest of the Air Jordan 4 Shimmer silhouette perfectly. Underfoot, the Tinker Hatfield designed AJ4 sole unit features, combining all the uppers' colours. A visible air bubble completes the design, making the Women's Jordan 4 Shimmer the must-have summer sneaker.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Cmft 2 Blue Electric Green

data.description: Refreshing the retro basketball model with updated cushioning, the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom CMFT 2 Blue Electric Green takes on a contrasting colourway. Its mixed-material upper features cut-out Swooshes, Jordan branding and neon touches. Zoom Air cushioning underfoot offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and the classic lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Finished with a perforated toe box, the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom CMFT 2 Blue Electric Green is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 13 Retro Gym Red Flint Grey

data.description: If you’re looking for your next pair of sneakers for the courts, gym, or streets, then this Air Jordan 13 Retro Gym Red Flint Grey offering in rich red is a sure head-turner. The upper is crafted from cushioned dimpled red fabric for a more tailored look, offset nicely against a suede grey fabric strip along the bottom of the upper and across the heel. The wavy grey fabric moulds seamlessly into the white rubber midsole and is complemented by the tractioned black outer sole. The fresh white continues for the toe box alongside the vivid red, while the laces and tongue both come in clean white. The heel is finished by a holographic logo on the side tab. Red eyestays and a red collar complete the bold look of the Air Jordan 13 Retro Gym Red Flint Grey.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low University Blue Womens

data.description: Voted the fan-favourite hue of 2021, University Blue takes over the Air Jordan 1 Low University Blue Womens, sitting alongside pastel grey. The upper on this kick is crafted from smooth leather with supple suede panels added to create a clean multi-textured look. Nike’s world-famous Swoosh sits in its usual place on the sidewalls, while Jordan Brand’s Wings motif is embroidered onto the heel for good measure. Underfoot, lightweight cushioning extends from front to back for support from toe to heel. Easy to style and perfect for the warmer months, your collection deserves the Air Jordan 1 Low University Blue Womens.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Retro Midnight Navy

data.description: A stealthy silhouette that deserves a place in your new-season collection, the Air Jordan 6 Retro Midnight Navy boasts premium materials, rich hues and industry-leading Nike technology. The leather upper comes in a smooth finish with perforated panels added for enhanced breathability. The oversized tongue features cut-outs and the lace-up fastening is finished with a toggle so you can adapt the fit if you need. Underfoot, Nike’s iconic Air cushioning offers bounce both on and off the court, while a strap on the heel allows you to get them on and off without squashing down the back. Versatile enough to go with everything thanks to the clean white and blue colourway, add the Air Jordan 6 Retro Midnight Navy to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Purple Gs

data.description: While black, white, and purple are already a highly popular colourway with any pair of Air Jordans, it's easy to see why this special edition pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Purple GS sneakers offers something a little different. The upper incorporates the dependable premium leather you'll be accustomed to from this brand, in clean white on the side panel, ankle strap, and perforated toe box. The Air Jordan Wings logo is printed in bold purple on the side strap. The rest of the upper on the Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Purple GS is crafted from soft tufted suede, which adds texture, volume, and warmth to this unique pair of sneakers. The heel panel shows off this material in vibrant purple, while the front side panels, eyelet panel, and even the Nike Swoosh itself are shown off in tufted black suede. A flash of orange is included on the tongue's logo, and a soft grey fabric addition around the collar helps the purple to stand out. Get your hands on a pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Purple GS sneakers for your rotation today!

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Crimson Tint Gs

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid Crimson Tint GS includes accents of pale pink without overpowering the classic feel of black and white leather. Tinted in an attractive shade of soft pink on the sole, heel, and eyelet strap, the colouring of this sneaker works in harmony with the more neutral black and white panelling without being too minimalistic. You can also see the Nike swoosh here in matching soft pink, standing out against the white. The Air Jordan wings stamp is printed boldly in black against the pink, and the mid design means comfort, support, and versatility every time you wear the Air Jordan 1 Mid Crimson Tint GS out and about. Black laces help to finish off the design of the Air Jordan 1 Mid Crimson Tint GS, contrasting impressively with the pink colouring and flowing seamlessly into the black leather panelling. This is an Air Jordan style you won’t want to miss.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement Td

data.description: Taking on an iconic colourway, the Air Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement TD tailors the retro basketball model towards toddlers. Decorated with speckled leather overlays, its upper also features grid mesh panelling and Jumpman logos. Underfoot, the cushioned midsole offers all-day comfort and its rubber outsole provides grip. Complete with elasticated laces and a padded collar, refresh your little one’s rotation with the Air Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement TD.

fields.name: Air Jordan Delta 2 Sp X Clot Flint

data.description: Meet the Air Jordan Delta 2 SP x CLOT Flint. It is a 2022 collaboration between the Jordan Brand and CLOT, a Hong-Kong based streetwear label, to give the popular futuristic silhouette a sleek makeover. The navy textile overlay complements the Flint grey colour on the nubuck heel panel. Freshening up the aesthetic are the white leather toe, tongue, and eyestays, which work in harmony with the layered mesh-foam construction. On the right sneaker, embroidered CLOT branding in light blue appears on the lateral sidewall, and Michael Jordan's lucky number, 23, features on the medial side. However, minimal branding appears on the left shoe, apart from the collectable Asian-inspired CLOT hangtag that features a jade green print with a lucky red strap.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Lv8D Elevated Bred Womens

data.description: For a bold and rich colourway, look no further than a black and red combination in a timeless Air Jordan 1 styling. The Air Jordan 1 LV8D Elevated Bred Womens sneaker comes with a premium upper in smooth leather, shown across the red perforated toe box, red heel panel, and the main mid panels in black. Black also wraps around the toe, while the side Nike Swoosh is shown in striking red against black. The laces are deep red along the black eyestay panel, while the tongue repeats the smooth black leather. For the sole of the Air Jordan 1 LV8D Elevated Bred Womens, you have a chunky elevated mid in creamy white and a larger rubber outer sole which shows off the striking red shade. Both are elevated for a more comfortable lift, better support, and durable traction with every step.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Alternate Bred Toe Gs

data.description: Dressed in an iconic colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Low Alternate Bred Toe GS stays close to the model’s ‘80s basketball roots. Made from premium leather, its upper features a perforated toe box for ventilation and is decorated with classic branding. The Air-cushioned midsole delivers comfort, the rubber outsole offers effective grip and the secure lacing system allows for a tailored fit. Add the Air Jordan 1 Low Alternate Bred Toe GS to your collection now.

fields.name: Nike Air Jordan 1 Low X Travis Scott Cactus Jack

data.description: Taking similar design cues to the high top variation the Travis Scott x Nike Air Jordan 1 Low Cactus Jack brings the levels with the same oversized backwards-facing Swoosh that has become the biggest take away from the collaboration. Featured prominently on the lateral side of the shoe, while a regular Swoosh graces the medial side. While Black and Dark Mocha nubuck dominate the upper, with a few pops of University Red adding a nice contrast. Travis Scott's signature details are subtly dotted across this design with the ‘Cactus Jack’ logo appearing on the tongue, medial side panel and sock liner.

fields.name: Air Jordan 12 Low Golf Cherry

data.description: Tailored towards golf, the Air Jordan 12 Low Golf Cherry is crafted using premium materials. Its pebbled leather base is accented with linear stitch detailing, silver eyelets, red snakeskin-textured overlays and Jordan branding. Spikes on the outsole allow for effective grip on the golf course, padding in the collar adds cushioning and the pull tab makes for an easy on and off. Update your collection with the Air Jordan 12 Low Golf Cherry.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Pink Shadow

data.description: The Jordan 1 Mid Pink Shadow is a testament to the fact that Air Jordan 1 Mids have had one of their best years within the sneaker industry this year. Interesting colour combos and premium materials have sky-rocketed the popularity of the silhouette. Jordan Brand has not missed with their colourways this year, and the Air Jordan 1 Pink Shadow is no different. Jordan looks to inject some colour into your winter rotation. Blacks and greys mostly dominate the uppers, but pops of pinks ensure the Jordan 1 Mid Pink Shadow sneaker still turns some heads. Jordan Brand go against their usual combination of suedes, mesh and leathers to give us an utterly leather take on the AJ1. The iconic swoosh is dripping in pink and features down both lateral and medial sides of the Air Jordan Mid Pink Shadow shoe. The tongue also features the Jumpman logo in pink to ensure the legendary logos are visible from a distance. The OG white sole houses Nike Air technology for optimum comfort wear after wear. Jordan Brand shows no sign of slowing down with these majestic Air Jordan 1 Mid releases, with the Air Jordan 1 Mid Pink Shadow guaranteed to be a fan favourite.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro Anthracite

data.description: After the Off-White x Air Jordan 5 collaborations' monumental success, Jordan Brand look set to release some unbelievable colourways of the iconic silhouette, the latest being the Jordan 5 Anthracite. The Air Jordan 5 Anthracite has a clean, minimalist aesthetic which sneakerheads worldwide are going to love. A mix of materials is used for the sneakers upper, dressed in a dark grey colourway, with pops of silver throughout complimenting the Anthracite uppers perfectly. Michael Jordan's number 23 features the sneaker's heel, whilst the iconic Jumpman logo features the sneaker's tongue. Underfoot, the Tinker Hatfield designed Sharktooth pattern features on the shoe's midsole, while a visible air bubble finishes off its design. Nike Air technology features, guaranteeing unbeatable comfort. The Air Jordan 5 looks set to have a massive 2021, so be sure to add the Air Jordan 5 Anthracite Retro sneaker to your collection before its too late.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Diamond

data.description: Versatility and timelessness are the name of the game with the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Diamond. Crafted from plush fabrics with instantly recognisable branding seen throughout, the Air Jordan 1 Diamond sneaker boasts a clean black and white finish that promises to pair with all your favourite outfits. Up tip, smooth leather and butter-soft suede create a multi-textured look, while Swoosh and Jumpman branding nod to the shoe’s partnership. Underfoot the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Diamond, lightweight cushioning delivers on bounce and comfort, while breathable perforations are added to the toe box for enhanced breathability. A must-have addition to your new-season rotation, get your hands on the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Diamond now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Praline Womens

data.description: Inspired by luxury handbags, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Praline Womens puts a stylish spin on the retro basketball model. Made from premium leather, its upper features caramel-coloured overlays and touches of Air Jordan branding. Perforations on its toe box allow for airflow, while Air cushioning underfoot offers all-day comfort. Fastened with ribbon laces, add the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Praline Womens to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High 85 Neutral Grey

data.description: One of the most highly anticipated Air Jordan 1's in recent years finally sees a release. The Jordan 1 Hi 85 Neutral Grey returns for the first time in thirty-five years this year, and we expect this drop to be one of the biggest we see in 2021. This silhouette's vintage style is making sneakerheads across the globe want the Neutral Grey, a true archival piece. The clean, white uppers are enhanced by the use of premium leathers throughout the design. The iconic Nike Swoosh detailing features across both lateral and medial sides of the sneaker in buttery, grey suede. We also see the Wings logo feature on the collar, whilst the tongue has the legendary OG Nike Air branding instead of the Jumpman logo. This sneaker looks as if Jordan Brand plucked it straight from the 80s. Underfoot, a Nike Air sole unit features, guaranteeing comfort whether you are on the court or the streets. This technology is housed within a white and grey sole which compliments the uppers perfectly. Despite its minimalistic aesthetics, we expect the Neutral Grey AJ1 to be in the Sneaker of the Year debate. Be sure to add a pair to your rotation.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Golf X Travis Scott Olive Black

data.description: Collaborating once again with industry icon Travis Scott, the neutral-toned Air Jordan 1 Low Golf x Travis Scott Olive Black is tailored towards enhancing performance on the golf course. Its premium leather upper is accented with reverse Swooshes, signature Jordan logos and co-branded touches. Perforations on its toe box allow for effective ventilation, Air cushioning underfoot provides comfort and its textured outsole provides grip on a range of terrains. Fastened with classic laces, the Air Jordan 1 Low Golf x Travis Scott Olive Black is next to deserve a spot in your collection.

fields.name: Dior X Air Jordan 1 High

data.description: The Dior x Air Jordan 1 High is the iconic collaboration between the luxury fashion brand and the sportswear legend you know and love. Combining two powerhouses in their own industry, this sneaker is the perfect representation of what can be done when luxury fashion meets a sportswear giant. The result is an extremely stylish and branded design that includes the best of Dior without compromising on the classic Air Jordan design. The Nike swoosh is made prominent by Dior-logo fabric, and the fashion label is printed on the soft blue rubber sole of the shoe. The Dior x Air Jordan 1 High is created in smooth, luxury leather in a soft shade of grey and complemented by classic white. The high ankle is padded for ultimate comfort, and the original Air Jordan wing logo gets a revamp here with a stylish Air Dior instead.

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Low Cement Grey

data.description: Sporting a muted colourway, the Air Jordan 11 Low Cement Grey puts a modern twist on the retro basketball silhouette. Its mesh base is accented with patent mudguard panelling, Jordan branding and elongated lace loops. Air cushioning underfoot offers comfort, the icy rubber outsole provides grip and the speed lacing system allows for a secure fit. Add the Air Jordan 11 Low Cement Grey to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Dark Iris Gs

data.description: A bold addition to Jordan’s extensive portfolio, the Air Jordan 3 Retro Dark Iris GS is the latest sneaker to demand a place in your collection. Crafted with tumbled leather on the upper, hits of purple update the collar, eyelets and branding. Taking inspiration from previous iterations, the grey elephant pattern found at the toe and heel contrasts with the white backdrop. Underfoot, lightweight cushioning courtesy of the visible Air unit delivers all-day comfort, while a textured tread ensures grip. Topped with fresh white laces and a Jumpman insignia on the tongue, the Air Jordan 3 Retro Purple GS is a must-have for off-duty days.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Space Jam Gs

data.description: Crafted with premium materials, the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Space Jam GS pays homage to an iconic Jordan colourway inspired by the Space Jam films. Featuring a perforated toe box for ventilation, its leather base is decorated with patent overlays and understated branding. The Air midsole delivers comfort, the icy rubber outsole provides grip and padding in its collar adds extra cushioning. Fastened with a classic lace closure, the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Space Jam GS is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Retro Low 72-10 Td

data.description: Nodding to Michael Jordan’s sneakers from the legendary 1996-96 season, the Air Jordan 11 Retro Low 72-10 TD puts comfort at the forefront of the design. Crafted with a premium leather upper, it features a wavy mudguard, Jumpman branding and a secure lace-up fastening. Underfoot, lightweight cushioning is provided by a white Phylon midsole, fitted with full-length Air-sole cushioning. Buy and sell the Air Jordan 11 Retro Low 72-10 TD with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low X Travis Scott X Fragment

data.description: In perhaps the most insane collaboration we have seen in sneakers, Jordan Brand joins forces with Travis Scott and Fragment Designs for a unique take on the Air Jordan 1 low, making the brand new Travis Scott Fragment Jordan 1 Low sought after around the world. The Travis Scott Fragment Low silhouette picks the best design aspects from previous Scott and Fragment releases. The colourway is reminiscent of the legendary Fragment Design AJ1 released in 2014, with premium white, blue and black leather throughout. The staple design from Scott's Jordan drops is the backwards swoosh, which features on the lateral side of each shoe. Dual branding can be found throughout, with the Cactus Jack, Fragment Designs and the Jordan Brand logos all featuring. You will find The OG Jordan Brand wings logo on the heel tab on the low version. Underfoot the Travis Scott Fragment Jordan 1 Low, a traditional Jordan sole unit features fully covered in a sail colourway. This sole unit houses Nike Air technology to guarantee optimum comfort wear after wear. Don't miss out on a chance to get your hands on a pair of Travis Scott Jordan 1 Fragment sneakers!

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Wizards

data.description: Taking on a basketball team-inspired colourway from 2001, the Air Jordan 3 Wizards also boasts retro-style aesthetics. Its leather upper is decorated with elephant-print overlays, Jordan branding, tonal topstitching and gold touches. The Air unit underfoot offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and padding in its collar adds extra cushioning. Fastened with a secure lace closure, update your collection with the Air Jordan 3 Wizards.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Cmft Fire Red Curry Womens

Expertly crafted with an all-leather base in orange, bright red overlays in suede adorn the toe cap, ankle and mudguard. fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Retro Velvet Midnight Navy Ps

Air cushioning underfoot delivers comfort, the secure lacing system allows for a tailored fit and padding in its collar adds extra support. Complete with a grip-enhancing outsole, update your kid’s collection with the Air Jordan 11 Retro Velvet Midnight Navy PS.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro Burgundy (2023)

data.description: Bringing back a colourway last seen in 2006, the Air Jordan 5 Retro Burgundy (2023) boasts premium aesthetics. Detailed with signature Jordan branding and contrast stitching, its upper consists of nubuck panelling and TPU grid sections. The Air unit in its midsole offers comfort, its rubber outsole provides grip and its lacing system is complete with a clear lace lock. Complete with a padded collar, elevate your everyday looks with the Air Jordan 5 Retro Burgundy (2023).

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Green Toe Gs

data.description: Make room in your collection for yet another pair, because the Air Jordan 1 Low Green Toe GS is here to demand a place in your daily rotation. A streamlined sneaker with endless styling appeal, the upper is crafted from smooth, luxe leather and breathable perforations offer ventilation. Dark green panels sit alongside white and black to create a winter-ready look, while branding steals the show with Nike’s Swoosh, Jordan Brand’s Wings logo and Michael Jordan’s Jumpman all sitting in their usual spots. Underfoot, Nike cushioning provides the comfort and stability this sneaker is known for, while a lace-up fastening up top puts you in control of the fit.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Camo Green Brown

data.description: Camo shades never go out of fashion, and when combined with this timeless Air Jordan 3 silhouette, you have a sneaker you can make an impression with time and again. Not only does the Air Jordan 3 Camo Green Brown sneaker bring together the quintessential camo shades of soft browns and greens, but it also combines a variety of materials. With smooth leather panelling on the outer sole and midsole and layered panelling of textured suede, this sneaker brings a full and durable look. Each material panel on the Air Jordan 3 Camo Green Brown has a different design, includes your classic camo pattern, as well as subtle lines and stripes. The midsole is complete with a visible Air Unit, reiterating the comfort and bounce of this sneaker. The cool blue shades in premium leather adorn the outer sole, side panels and also allow the classic Jumpman logo to shine brightly. After various adult reissues in 2000, the popular iteration makes its return in GS sizing, introducing a whole new generation to the timeless kicks. It's easy to understand the colourway's global appeal, as it has a clean white leather construction with sidewall perforations for improved comfort and breathability. The neutral design is elevated with hits of Midnight Navy on the tongue, heel, and midsole. Heritage details help the sneakers retain a vintage vibe, such as a toggle lacing system for added support, visible Air cushioning for responsive cushioning, and the famous Jumpman on the heel.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Prototype

data.description: It is undeniable; the Air Jordan 1 is one of the best sneakers ever to release. The iconic basketball turned lifestyle silhouette has seen a boom in popularity over the last few years, and with colourways like this, it is easy to see why. The vibrant colour combination is similar to the legendary Shattered Backboard AJ1s, with white underlays complemented by orange and black accents. The front panels feature an eye-catching orange hue, as does the Nike Swoosh detailing across the lateral and medial sides of the sneaker. The heel panels come in a stealthy black with the OG wings logo featuring in white on the ankle collar. Underfoot you will find a traditional Air Jordan 1 sole unit housing Nike Air technology. Nike Air makes the AJ1 one of the most comfortable sneakers around, whether you are looking to hoop in them or wear them on the streets.

Just the right amount of cushioning is added underfoot for optimised comfort, while the textured tread ensures grip both on and off the court when you wear the Air Jordan 1 Mid Brown.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Rookie Of The Year

data.description: Michael Jordan in 1985 received the honour of being named NBA Rookie of the Year after launching his career in his debut season with an impressive point per game average and an immediately apparent drive for success. Air Jordan decided to commemorate this achievement with the November 2018 release of the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Rookie of the Year. This high top tribute features white-based leather upper with tan overlays lifted straight from the 'Gold Harvest' colourway which appear on the mudguard, ankle, eyestay, and heel. Hidden on the inside of each strap on the upper are callouts to MJ’s outstanding rookie season. ‘1984-85 R.O.Y. 2313 POINTS 28.2 PPG’ can be found on the inside of one strap, and a quote from Jordan can be found on the other. This shoe is another excellent celebration of the Jumpman Brands main man's breathtaking career and is as historical for sports than as it is stylish for fashionistas.

The low-top AJ5 iteration offers an attractive grey, black, and ice blue colourway. Plus, the sneakers have been designed to resemble the quality and sophistication of Parisian fashion. The iced outsole and spiked midsole add texture and character, while the iconic Jumpman on the tongue tab and the stamped PSG logo on the heel provide a premium finishing touch.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Ex Black Smoke Grey

data.description: The durable yet deconstructed Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Ex Black Smoke Grey is one of the most unique iterations released in 2022. Coined an "unfinished" masterpiece by Nike, it's easy to see why sneaker fans are eager to get their hands on the inside-out aesthetic. Offering exposed materials, frayed edges, and a foam and textile upper, you can rest assured it will add plenty of texture to an outfit. Plus, the black and smoke grey colourway has a neutral colour scheme to ensure it matches many clothes in your wardrobe. You can still expect the same comfortable Air unit and foam midsole underfoot.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Gs Coral Chalk

data.description: Pretty in pink, the Air Jordan 1 Mid GS Coral Chalk is made for summer days. Designed to steal the show, the Coral Chalk Jordan 1 is bright, bold and easy to love. Up top, tumbled leather comes in varying shades of pink - from fuchsia to coral - with black panels offering a point of contrast where needed. Nike’s Swoosh sits in its usual place on the sidewalls of the Jordan 1 Mid GS Coral Chalk, with Jordan Brand’s Wings logo following suit on the ankle and Michael Jordan’s Jumpman graces the tongue. Underfoot the Air Jordan 1 Coral Chalk, Nike’s expertly crafted Air cushioning ensures comfort and bounce, and the textured tread provides the optimised grip this hoops shoe is known for.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Pale Vanilla Womens

data.description: Style meets comfort in the Air Jordan 1 Mid Pale Vanilla Womens. It sports a off-white leather base accentuated by yellow overlays. Special detail includes the metallic Wings adorning the mid-top collar and Swooshes shining in a golden finish, for a unique touch. Crafted from premium leather, this pair offers durability and structural support. Your comfort is guaranteed with the Nike Air sole unit, delivering lightweight cushioning, making every step a breeze. Completing the look is the robust rubber outsoles which provide reliable grip. Experience both functionality and sophistication with the Air Jordan 1 Mid Pale Vanilla Womens.

fields.name: Air Jordan 12 Playoffs

data.description: Brought back to celebrate the shoe’s 25th anniversary, the Air Jordan 12 “Playoffs” 2022 edition stays true to the shoe’s origins. The original kick was worn by Michael Jordan during the 1997 All-Star game, where he dropped the first ever ASG triple-double. This iteration is crafted with the same quilted leather upper, textured mudguard and polished lace holders at the top of the fastening. Jordan’s signature Jumpman motif comes in red on the tongue, while the textured tread ensures optimised grip both on and off the court. A must-have for any collector, get your hands on the Air Jordan 12 “Playoffs” now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Triple White Gs

data.description: Nothing says a timeless, classic sneaker more than a clean white finish. Enjoy the beloved Air Jordan 1 stylish silhouette with panels of fresh white throughout. The Air Jordan 1 Low Triple White GS is such an iconic silhouette that's going to provide style, comfort, and durability, no matter what. Subtle contrast is shown in the Air Jordan 1 Low Triple White GS through the variation of white leather panels, both smooth as well as grained, for a layered and attractive finish. The Nike Swoosh is included in white on the side panel, with clean white laces and air holes for maximum breathability. The chunky white mid and outer sole means comfort and balance with every wear. If you’re looking for a pair of Air Jordan 1s that are sleek and avoid bold colours, then the Air Jordan 1 Low Triple White GS sneakers could well be the pair for you.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Og Starfish Womens

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Low OG Starfish Womens - also known as the Air Jordan 1 Shattered Backboard - is an eye-catching sneaker that deserves a place in your collection. Nodding to the AJ1’s OG roots with its leather upper, breathable perforations and instantly recognisable branding, this sneaker is fitted with Air cushioning underfoot to deliver comfort and bounce both on and off the court. Detailed with Nike’s Swoosh logo on the sidewalls, Jordan Brand’s Wings motif on the heel and extra branding on the tongue for good measure, this is the kind of sneaker you’ll want to reserve for special occasions.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Bright Citrus Womens

data.description: Add a splash of bright and warm citrus to your next pair of sneakers with this fun and summer-themed pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Bright Citrus Womens. If you’re a fan of dependable white sneakers, then add a touch of bright colour with this rich citrus shade showcased on the side leather panels and the front toe box — complete with air holes for full breathability, too. Your Nike swoosh is printed in clean white against a backdrop of lively citrus, and to contrast, the Air Jordan wings logo is stamped in orange against white. White laces with a subtle stitching effect complete the fresh and clean look, with cushioned comfort and support at all times with the Nike Air sole. Clean white panelling and midsole around the bottom of the sneaker break up the bright citrus shade of the Womens Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Bright Citrus.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Og Black Toe (2023)

data.description: Reminiscent of Michael Jordan’s basketball sneakers from 1985, the Air Jordan 1 Low OG Black Toe (2023) effortlessly fuses sporting heritage with modern appeal. With a full leather construction, Varsity Red tones adorn the heel, lace and sole. Nike’s Swoosh dominates the sidewall in black, while advanced cushioning underfoot provides the comfort this silhouette is known for. Buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 Low OG Black Toe (2023) with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Bred Patent

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 High OG Bred Patent sneaker presents the iconic combination of red and black with a glossy edge in the form of shiny leather panelling throughout the shoe. The black is sleeker, the red silkier, and the overall look of patent leather shows the Air Jordan 1 High OG Bred Patent shoe was built for purpose. This is a sneaker that will reflect any weather to give you an edge on the streets or on the court. The Nike Swoosh is displayed in a deep shade of red, matching with the heel tab, ankle strap, toe cap, and rubber outer sole. The rest of the sneaker is shown in black, apart from the clean line of white on the midsole. Deep black laces complete the look of the Air Jordan 1 High OG Bred Patent, and the Air Jordan Wings logo is stamped black on red.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Split Black White Womens Two Tone

data.description: Updating an iconic ‘80s basketball silhouette, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Split Black White Womens presents a modern twist on a two-toned sporting classic. Alternating black and white pebbled leather panels decorate this AJ1 in a checkerboard-like effect. Signature sidewall Swoosh detailing subtly brands this pair, which works alongside a white Wings logo on the collar panel and split Jumpman-branded tongue label. Grounded by a white Air-cushioned midsole for classic comfort, this understated sneaker is finished with a black grippy outsole for ultimate grip. With its unbeatable colourway and unique divided formation, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Split Black White Womens is not one to be missed.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og X Travis Scott X Fragment

data.description: In perhaps the most insane collaboration we have seen in sneakers, Jordan Brand join forces with both Travis Scott and Fragment Designs for a truly unique take on the Air Jordan 1. The silhouette picks the best design aspects from previous Scott and Fragment releases. The colourway is reminiscent of the legendary Fragment Design AJ1 that released back in 2014, with premium white, blue and black leather featuring throughout. The staple design from Scott's Jordan drops is the backwards swoosh, which features on the lateral side of each shoe. Dual branding can be found throughout, with the Cactus Jack, Fragment Designs and the Jordan Brand logos all featuring. Underfoot, an OG Jordan sole unit features fully covered in a sail colourway. This sole unit houses Nike Air technology to guarantee optimum comfort wear after wear.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Og Ex Coconut Milk

data.description: Boasting a muted colourway and updating the retro basketball model, the Air Jordan 1 Low OG EX Coconut Milk takes on deconstructed aesthetics. Made from a mixture of materials, its upper features a dimpled toe box, touches of branding and exposed foam edges. Air cushioning underfoot offers comfort and the rubber outsole provides effective grip. Add the Air Jordan 1 Low OG EX Coconut Milk to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Chicago Lost And Found

data.description: Paying homage to its ‘80s roots, the Air Jordan 1 High OG Chicago Lost and Found celebrates one of the most iconic AJ1 colourways. Its white cracked leather base is complete with a perforated toe box for ventilation and is layered with red and black detailing. A classic Wings logo features on the collar, while signature Nike branding adds extra decoration. Underfoot, the off-white Air midsole offers comfort and the red outsole allows for effective grip. Rounded off with ankle padding for added support, the Air Jordan 1 High OG Chicago Lost and Found is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Ice Blue Td

data.description: Putting comfort at the forefront of the design, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Ice Blue TD stays true to the silhouette’s basketball roots. Dressed in blue, black and white, Nike’s Swoosh appears on the sidewall and a functional pull tab updates the ankle. Underfoot, advanced cushioning provides all-day support. Shop the Air Jordan 1 Mid Ice Blue TD with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Union Off Noir

data.description: After a two year hiatus, Union LA has once again joined forces with Jordan to deliver another great collaboration. After the massive success of the Union x Jordan 1, the LA boutique store this time takes over Tinker Hatfield's creation with the Jordan 4 Union Off Noir. The Jordan 4 Off Noir colourway features a black and blue upper with a sail coloured sole to emphasise further what sits on top of it. On the heel, you will find the Nike Air branding favoured over the Jumpman logo. Perhaps the most irregular part of the Retro Air Jordan 4 Union Off Noir this time around is the addition of a tongue that folds to show the typical Air Jordan branding stitched inside of it. Contrary to what people first thought when images began to surface, you can have the tongue at full length as you would generally see on Jordan 4 models. Union founder Chris Gibbs has also added his usual personal touch with the addition of the Union LA yellow tab featured on the side panelling of each Jordan 4 Retro Union Off Noir shoe. If the Jordan 1 release is anything to go by, the Union LA x Jordan 4 Off Noir is guaranteed to be a hit.

fields.name: Air Jordan 2 High Chicago Gs

data.description: Update your collection with the Air Jordan 2 High Chicago GS sneakers. The undeniably cool sneakers are steeped in history, as Michael Jordan made them famous when wearing the kicks to the NBA All-Star Dunk Contest in 1987. The retro high-top sneakers dropped once again in 2022 to celebrate Air Jordan 2's 35th anniversary. It's a must-buy for those who want to wear an effortlessly stylish silhouette that will never go out of fashion. This cool iteration has retained the original mid-1980s appeal, as it's crafted from a clean white leather upper with faux skin. The design speaks for itself, as it doesn't feature the iconic Nike Swooshes, Jumpman, or wings motif.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Washington Wizards Ps

data.description: Taking on a retro-inspired design, the Air Jordan 3 Retro Washington Wizards PS is crafted using premium materials. Its leather upper is decorated with elephant print overlays, perforated panelling and Jordan branding. Air technology underfoot offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and classic laces round off the design. Buy and sell the kids-sized Air Jordan 3 Retro Washington Wizards PS with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Gym Red Black Pebbled Gs

data.description: It’s time to hit the gym with these striking Air Jordan 1 Low Gym Red and Black sneakers. These shoes have everything you need to make you feel like the one true Michael Jordan, thanks to the iconic styling of these classic sneakers. The red and black is a nod to MJ’s time with the Chicago Bulls, and the air cushioning with rubber outsole make the Air Jordan 1 Low Gym Red Black perfect for shooting hoops, pounding the treadmill, or just wearing out on the street with whatever style you’re into. The low cut of the AJ1s gives enough support without making you feel strapped in, and the leather uppers ensure a durable yet stylish sneaker that works with any look and in any setting.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Dark Marina Blue Ps

data.description: Add a pop of colour to your little one’s collection with the Air Jordan 1 High Dark Marina Blue PS. Comfortable enough for them to wear all day, the upper is crafted from smooth leather that’s as flexible as it is durable. Breathable perforations are added to the toe box for enhanced ventilation, while Nike branding steals the show on the sidewalls and tongue. Easy to style thanks to the clean blue and black colourway, add the Air Jordan 1 High Dark Marina Blue PS to their collection and they’ll never want to take them off.

fields.name: A Ma Maniere X Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Ps

data.description: Crafted with sophistication, the A Ma Maniére x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG PS is laced with luxurious touches that your mini teenager will adore. This collaborative shoe’s soft off-white suede base is detailed with a deep burgundy snakeskin-patterned Swoosh and a matching ankle panel. These dark red-toned hits can also be seen in its laces and embossed Wings logo, as well as the ‘A Ma Maniére’ handwritten text etched across its heel. A beige-toned Air-cushioned midsole grounds this premium pair, with a final wash of burgundy running over its grippy outsole. With its high-end looks, the Atlanta boutique-designed A Ma Maniére x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG PS is the perfect sneaker to treat your kid to.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Cement 2011

data.description: The 2011 Air Jordan 3 Retro Cement colourway was released as part of a retro drop celebrating the famous silhouette's 23rd anniversary. It is almost identical to the Air Jordan 3 Black Cement sneaker, which was one of the four original 1988 colourways. If you weren't lucky enough to get your hands on the original 1998 release or additional drops in 1994, 2001, and 2008, you could finally get your hands on a pair from 2011. Sneaker fans will likely recognise the distinctive design on your feet, as the timeless black upper contrasts with an elephant print on the mudguard and heel counter. The non-OG version features the famous Jumpman logo on the tongue and heel tab.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Lv8D High Hyper Royal Womens

data.description: Offering a modern take on the retro basketball model, the bold Air Jordan 1 LV8D High Hyper Royal Womens features an added zip closure which allows for an easy on and off. Its leather upper is accented with minimalistic Jordan branding and sidewall Swooshes. The platform Air midsole delivers both height and comfort, while the textured rubber outsole provides grip. Finished with perforations on the toe box for ventilation, the Air Jordan 1 LV8D High Hyper Royal Womens is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Se Craft Gs

data.description: Boasting vintage-style aesthetics, the Air Jordan 4 Retro SE Craft GS presents a premium update of the retro basketball sneaker. Sporting an understated colourway, its suede and leather upper is accented with a rubber heel overlay and Jordan branding. Air cushioning in the midsole offers comfort, the textured outsole provides grip and padding in its collar adds extra support. Fastened with a classic lace closure, the Air Jordan 4 Retro SE Craft GS is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se All-Star Weekend Gs

data.description: After a monumental 2020, the Air Jordan 1 Mid returns in an epic 'All-Star Weekend' colourway. The monochrome colourway is guaranteed to turn heads; we expect the Jordan 1 Carbon Fiber to be an absolute must-have for collectors worldwide. The black and white colour combo, dubbed the Jordan 1 Mid Carbon Fiber, features white underlays with patent leather panelling. The iconic Nike swoosh features on both lateral and medial sides of the shoe in black, whilst the legendary wings logo features in contrasting white to really pop. You will also find the Jumpman logo on the tongue and insole of the sneaker. Underfoot, an OG Air Jordan 1 sole unit features and houses Nike Air technology. This technology guarantees comfort whether you are looking to rock the 'All-Star Weekend' on the court or the streets. We expect the AJ1 Mid to have another tremendous year, and this Jordan 1 Mid SE All Star Weekend GS Carbon Fiber version may be the best of them all.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Easter Regal Pink

data.description: Show off a playful pastel sneaker if you’re a fan of bright colours and a retro finish. The Air Jordan 5 Easter Regal Pink style is renowned for its perfect retro vibes, and this Easter Regal Pink variety comes with a colourful premium leather upper and chunky design. The smooth matte leather upper is dominated by pastel pink from toe to heel, while the mid panel includes a light pastel blue rubber panel with perforation detailing. This light blue hue repeats for the extra-large eyelet accessories against white-blue laces and a clear toggle accessory on top alongside a metallic silver tongue. The sole reveals a jagged shark-tooth design in speckled white against a light blue mid, a visible Air Unit to the heel, and a semi-translucent turquoise finish on the outer.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Multi Canvas Gs

data.description: Presenting a sustainable take on the retro basketball model, the Air Jordan 1 Low Multi Canvas GS is made using recycled materials. Boasting a pastel-toned colourway, its leather and canvas layered upper is further detailed with iconic Jordan branding and Nike Swooshes. The speckled Air midsole delivers comfort, the Grind rubber outsole provides effective grip and the classic lace closure allows for a secure fit. Refresh your rotation with the Air Jordan 1 Low Multi Canvas GS.

fields.name: Air Jordan 12 Retro Sp X A Ma Maniere Black Td

data.description: Made in collaboration with luxury streetwear store A Ma Maniére, the Air Jordan 12 Retro SP x A Ma Maniére Black TD is crafted using premium materials. Its nubuck base is detailed with sun ray-inspired topstitching, understated branding and plush suede overlays. Classic cushioning underfoot delivers comfort, while the textured outsole provides effective grip. Finished with a handy pull tab, elevate your toddler’s everyday looks with the Air Jordan 12 Retro SP x A Ma Maniére Black TD.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Gs Kumquat

data.description: This bold Air Jordan 3 Retro GS Kumquat sneaker is guaranteed to leave a lasting impression with its retro styling and vibrant pattern finish. The premium upper comes constructed of tumbled black leather, running across the toe, main side panels, and up across the ankle strap. This then switches to a cement-like finish around the toe and also towards the rear of the sneaker, shown in vibrant orange paired with black. You then have bright kumquat orange shown on the rear mudguard, the eyestays, around the fabric collar, and along the tongue bordering. The laces of the Air Jordan 3 Retro GS Kumquat come in bold black, complementing the bright orange eyestay detailing. For the midsole, you have clean white rubber with a visible Air Unit, while the outer sole completes the look in white painted with splashes of orange.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Split Cream Maroon Womens

data.description: Made with premium materials, the two-toned Air Jordan 1 Mid Split Cream Maroon Womens boasts a playful checkerboard-like design. Its pebbled leather upper is decorated with Jordan branding and Swoosh detailing. The Air midsole offers comfort, the rubber outsole allows for effective grip and the perforated toe box provides ventilation. Fastened with a classic lace closure, buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 Mid Split Cream Maroon Womens with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Blue Mint Gs

data.description: A bright take on an OG hoops icon, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Blue Tint GS pays homage to the original design with instantly recognisable branding, premium fabrics and functional elements. The leather upper comes in a blue and green colourway, while breathable perforations are added to the toe box to enhance the sneaker’s breathability. Nike’s famous Swoosh sits on the sidewalls, while Air Jordan branding graces the ankle and tongue for extra style points. Underfoot, lightweight cushioning supports your every step, so add the Air Jordan 1 Mid Blue Tint GS and you’ll want to wear them everywhere you go.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air Cmft Orange Black

data.description: Nodding to the OG AJ1 design with its instantly recognisable branding, the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air CMFT Orange Black elevates the design with premium materials and new-school detailing. The upper is crafted from brushed suede and Nike’s signature Swoosh comes in a cut-out finish on the sides rather than its usual stitched-on design. The ankle is padded for extra comfort and added support, while the textured tread delivers maximum grip both on and off the court. Easy to wear thanks to the clean orange and black colourway, add the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Air CMFT Orange Black to your everyday rotation now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Paris

data.description: The classic sandstone styling of these Air Jordan 1 Low Paris edition sneakers shows us what real sophistication in shoes looks like. There is an air of confidence in the muted tones of these trainers, mixing up the texture of the leather uppers to provide you with strong construction, a classic silhouette, and an iconic design that by now Air Jordan is famous for. The Paris vibe of these sneakers doesn’t go unnoticed, with the cloudy sky greys and blues rumbling against the minimalistic white look of one of the best sneaker designs on the planet. Get your Paris look on with the Air Jordan 1 Low Paris trainers that showcase the style and sophistication that Paris is known for and construction from Nike that we love.

fields.name: Air Jordan 13 Retro Wheat 2023
Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Black Infrared 23 Gs

data.description: Chicago style dominates in the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Black Infrared 23 sneakers. The smooth white leather upper adds a hit of luxury to the silhouette but features a deliberately faded, black overlay revealing a crimson finish. The weathered look provides a perfect contrast against the untouched jet-black Nike Swooshes, eye stay, laces, lining, insole, and tongue. Also, hints of red feature across the silhouette, as it appears on the signature Jumpman on the tongue tab and insole. fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Reverse Bred

The refined leather upper on the Air Jordan 1 Low Reverse Bred is constructed of black and red panelling in equal measure, with a black perforated toe box, side panel, tongue, and sleek black laces. The red premium leather is included on the side front panels, eyelet panel, collar, heel tab, and most prominently on the eye-catching Nike Swoosh. For a flash of personality with every step of the Air Jordan 1 Low Reverse Bred, the outer sole is complete in the same shade of rich red. An embroidered black Nike Wings logo is included on the heel tab, and a flash of red is added on the tongue's logo against the black. A white rubber midsole offers a break in bold colour while providing support and balance when you're out and about in your pair of Air Jordan 1 Low Reverse Bred sneakers.

fields.name: Air Jordan 13 Navy

data.description: The retro styling of Air Jordan 13 here comes with a stunning navy blue panelling, bold black, and touches of fresh white. The Air Jordan 13 Navy style is perfect for hitting the courts or the streets, with a supportive higher shaping and a boosted sole with maximum traction. Here, you have a breathable fabric panel running seamlessly from toe to heel in satin-like navy blue, with stitching indents running throughout for a more quilted look. The upper includes tumbled black leather around the toe cap, smooth black leather to the side rear, and a reflective rubber accessory on the heel collar. For the sole, white pairs with black for black mudguards, white curved sections, and a black rubber outer for a volumized finish to complete the retro look.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Se Light Steel Grey

data.description: Sporting a muted colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Low SE Light Steel Grey presents an updated take on the retro model. Made from a mixture of canvas and leather, its upper is detailed with embroidered branding and features a perforated toe box for ventilation. Air cushioning in the speckled midsole offers comfort, the textured outsole provides grip and padding in its collar adds extra support. Refresh your rotation with the Air Jordan 1 Low SE Light Steel Grey.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Sp X A Ma Maniére Violet Ore Womens

data.description: Streetwear boutique A Ma Maniere joins forces with Jordan Brand to release one of the best Air Jordan 3's we have ever set eyes on. Founder of A Ma Maniere James Whitner is a revolutionary within the streetwear scene, and the AJ3 perfectly reflects this. The exceptionally luxurious sneaker features tumbled white leather underlays combined with plush suede panels in grey. We see the A Ma Maniere logo feature on one of the shoe's tongue, whilst the other features the iconic Jumpman logo. Cream accents throughout, giving the shoe a premium, vintage feel. Nike Air technology features, guaranteeing comfort wear after wear. This A Ma Maniere collaboration truly is one of a kind, be sure to add a pair to your collection today.

fields.name: Sns X Air Jordan 1 Mid 20Th Anniversary

data.description: Marking the 20th Anniversary of the launch of Sneakersnstuff, the Jumpman brand has honoured this occasion with a very special Air Jordan 1 in homage. Remaining as one of the most coveted silhouettes on the market, the SNS x Air Jordan 1 Mid is crafted using luxe fabrics, accented with the silhouette’s signature design elements. A combination of smooth leather, and brushed suede overlays create a multi-textured design. While the pared-back ivory hue is perfectly complemented by pastel grey, and bright red is added to the ankle to really make this design pop.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Golf Royal Toe

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Low Golf Royal Toe is a celebration of Michael Jordan’s love of golf. Despite being world-famous for basketball, MJ has been known to hold his own on a course with pro golfers and plays almost every day. The low-cut AJ1 silhouette features a vibrant royal blue toe box, heel, outsole, and tongue Jumpman, ensuring the sneakers grab attention. The bright hue is played down by a jet-black toe cap, mudguard, eyestay, laces, and Nike Swooshes on the medial and lateral sides. The crisp white quarter and midsole add freshness to the design, ensuring it is a perfect choice for a day on the green. Also, you can trust your feet won’t ache after many hours thanks to its signature Air cushioning.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Bio Hack

data.description: The Jordan 1 High OG is back in one of the most insane colourways to grace the silhouette to date. The Bio Hack draws inspiration from the incredible UNDEFEATED x Nike Dunk High that released way back in 2006. The Bio Hack doesn't just flip the colourway on its head, but also the materials used are switched out for this shoe. Opting for a full suede construction instead of the traditional leather on the sneakers upper. The various panels come in Baroque Brown, Black, and Laser Orange, whilst the sock liner perfectly contrasts these in Racer Pink. The legendary swoosh comes in metallic silver. The sole, which houses the iconic Nike Air technology, contrast the upper perfectly in Mint Green. Any Jordan enthusiast will most definitely be clamouring over the Bio Hack. A must cop for sneakerheads around the globe, the perfect addition to your summer rotation.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 White Oreo

data.description: A shoe that initially released back in 1999 finally sees a re-release this year. The Air Jordan 4 'Oreo' has not been retro'd over the last twenty-two years, so sneakerheads will be ecstatic to see the silhouette release once again finally. A stealthy take on a classic, the Jordan 4 Oreo shoe's upper is entirely covered in luxurious black leather. The murdered out colourway is complimented perfectly by the grey cement design's inclusion on the shoe's midsole and eyelets, giving you them Oreo feels. Underfoot the Jordan 4 White Oreo, a mix of cement and black makes up the shoe's sole unit, which houses Nike Air technology. The iconic technology guarantees comfort and is visible due to the air bubble that features. The Oreo Jordan 4 will be a fan favourite the minute it releases, and after not seeing a release in over twenty years, we guarantee it will be an instant sell-out. Be sure to pick up a pair of Air Jordan 4 Oreo's today.

fields.name: Solefly X Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Carnivore

The black then switches to rich red for the perforated nubuck toe box which also allows for key ventilation to keep the foot cool. Wrapping around the toe, a beige and brown textured leather adds depth to the design, while the heel panel repeats the same texture in monochrome beige. Finished with a retro-style rubber outsole, the wild SoleFly x Air Jordan 1 Retro Low Carnivore will elevate any outfit with its animalistic flair.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Usa

The red, white and blue colourway comes crafted from high-end leather throughout, giving the sneaker an instantly luxurious feel. The iconic swoosh logo can, of course, be seen on the side panel of each sneaker. The iconic details do not finish there. The classic wings logo feature on the ankle while the Jumpman logo stars on the tongue. The sole comes in white, a look we have become accustomed to with Jordan 1's. The white bottom hides the famous Nike Air technology, which runs the length of the sneaker. You will not find a shoe better suited for both comfort and activity. Whether you are a collector of Jordan 1's or just beginning to assemble a collection, the Jordan 1 Mid USA is a must cop.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Black White Diamond

data.description: Another Air Jordan 1 Low for your collection, the Air Jordan 1 Low Black White Diamond is versatility at its finest. Boasting a premium vibe with instantly recognisable branding for good measure, this sneaker ticks every single box. The upper is crafted from a blend of smooth leather and supple suede and Nike’s iconic Swoosh steals the show on the sidewalls. Up top, breathable perforations on the toe box ensure optimised air flow, while lightweight cushioning underfoot delivers all-day comfort. A must-have for the new season, the Air Jordan 1 Low Black White Diamond promises to pair with everything in your wardrobe.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Black Glitter Gs

data.description: If you want a little more luxury and sparkle for your sneaker game, then look no further than this pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Black Glitter GS sneakers for smaller feet. The premium sneaker shows off a glossy glitter finish with the main side panels, across the toe box, and around the collar, in deep black and shimmering gold. The rest of the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Black Glitter GS' upper is crafted from smooth premium black leather, wrapping around the toe, front side panels, eyestay strips, heel tab, and main ankle collar. The side of the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Black Glitter GS sneaker includes a standout white Nike Swoosh, while laces replicate the gold and black glitter design. For the sole, you have a chunky white rubber mid and a bold black outer to finish the luxurious design.

The luxurious uppers feature white underlays and blue panelling with a worn-in effect. The Hyper Royal panels are contrasted expertly by a grey collar and swoosh branding. It does not get more classic than a clean pair of Air Jordan 1s; the Jordan 1 Hyper Royal is an absolute must-cop for the upcoming Spring and Summer.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Cardinal Ps

The Air Jordan 3 Retro Cardinal PS sneaker then reveals a smooth matte leather panel towards the bottom of the upper, contrasted with two panels of concrete-effect grey leather wrapping around the toe and to the main heel panel. Red is then included with a bold rubber mudguard running along the bottom of the sneaker and also along the collar fabric and tongue to the top. The concrete grey also returns for the eyestay detailing behind white laces. To finish the Air Jordan 3 Retro Cardinal PS' sole, you have a clean white rubber mid and a light grey rubber outer.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Co Japan Neutral Grey

The sneaker initially released back in 2001, as part of a Japan-exclusive CO.JP line. Now, after a twenty-year wait, the shoe is available in the UK for the first time. The highly anticipated shoe comes dressed in fresh grey tones throughout, crafted from high-quality leather. Scintillating silver panelling on the toe box and back of the shoe completes this luxurious colourway. The Nike Air branding is present on the tongue, while the wings logo on the ankle is cut out as a nod to the OG design from 2001. This sneaker is an absolute dream for collectors who missed out on the OG shoe in 2001. This classic colourway is sure to catch the eye of everybody looking to upgrade their rotation this summer. A must cop for enthusiasts everywhere.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Element Gore-Tex Light Bone College Grey Black

Presenting an understated pair dressed in an always on-trend colourway, the upper is crafted from supple suede coated in Gore-Tex to keep your feet warm and dry. The sidewalls are graced with Nike’s world-famous Swoosh emblems, while the Jordan Brand’s ‘Wings’ logo sits in its usual place on the ankle. Underfoot, Air cushioning ensures comfort both on and off the court, while the purple and ivory colour scheme up top makes sure the Air Jordan 1 Element Gore-Tex Light Bone College Grey Black is absolutely effortless to style.

The premium upper comes with panels of sweeping smooth white leather, running from the perforated toe box to the heel. The ankle strap, in white, comes with a black Air Jordan Wings logo, while the collar panel behind contrasts brightly with the coral leather panel. Finished with Nike Air woven label on the tongue and denim-backed Wings logo on the collar’s overlay, this Air Jordan 1 High OG Denim Womens is the ideal weekend shoe.

The sole on the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom CMFT Team Red combines a crisp, sleek inner with a bold blue outer for a stylish contrast, and your Nike Swoosh is in a muted shade of soft blue against a creamy-white leather background. The Air Jordan logo is stamped subtly in red which moulds into the matching red leather panel for a seamless look. The Air Jordan 1 High Zoom CMFT Team Red sneakers aren't ones to be missed!

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Obsidian

data.description: The first variant of this design dropped in 2017 the Jordan 1 Obsidian colourway pays tribute to Michael Jordan's college alma mater through a team-inspired (University of North Carolina), colour block palette on the leather upper. The 2019 revamp continues with the tradition, as matching branding notes and Swooshes play their part in the homage. As well as a Nike Air infused midsole and circular rubber outsole to supply classic comfort and traction, completing the Jordan 1 Retro High Obsidian.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Island Green

fields.name: Fragment X Jordan 3 White/Black

For this collaboration, the pair have decided to take over Tinker Hatfield creation, the Air Jordan 3. The shoe comes dressed in an 'Orca' colourway. The upper and midsole come in a crisp white colour scheme. Black panelling features in the middle of the silhouette to contrast the white perfectly. The use of tumbled leather throughout the entire sneaker gives it that luxurious feel as soon as you pick up a pair. Branding is kept to an absolute minimum with the Fragment logo only featuring on the heel of each shoe behind a transparent Jumpman logo. This sneaker is most definitely going to have sneakerheads going wild, a must-cop for anybody wanting to upgrade their collection with an incredibly sought-after collab.
