Mixed smooth and pebbled leather overlays dress this all-white classic, with a subtly textured Swoosh decorating its clean sidewall. Complete with midsole Air cushioning and a perforated toe box for optimal ventilation, this smaller-sized model makes no compromise on its signature AJ1 comfort levels. Branded with understated Jumpman and Wings logos, the light Air Jordan 1 Mid Triple White PS is a timeless classic that even your little one will want to keep clean.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Pollen

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid Pollen achieves the classic silhouette and comes in a more minimalistic colourway of white and black yet is offset perfectly with warm golden yellow accents. The smooth premium yellow upper is made to pop with a vibrant golden Nike Swoosh, which is topped by a yellow Air Jordan Wings logo on the black ankle strap. The golden yellow then continues to the ankle panel and also on the tongue’s Nike branding stamp. The rest of the Air Jordan 1 Mid Pollen splits between white and black evenly for a clean and timeless look. The eyelet panel and laces are both deep black, and the toe cap is bordered by a black leather panel. The perforated toe cap is white, along with the chunky rubber midsole, while the outer sole repeats the black. The Air Jordan 1 Mid Pollen is highly sought after, so don't miss your chance and get your hands on a pair!

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Pastel Pink Green Gs

data.description: The timeless Air Jordan 1 silhouette, here in Grade School sizing, gets an attractive pastel update with layered panels of fabric and flashes of clean white for a fresh look. For the Air Jordan 1 Low Pastel Pink Green GS sneaker, you have a perforated toe box, main side panel and eyelet strip in premium matte white leather, while this is combined with a textured fabric finish around the toe and across the Nike Swoosh in beige, across the front side straps and around the collar detailing in khaki brown, and around the main heel tab in a delicate baby pink. The tab is also embroidered with a white Air Jordan Wings logo. The Air Jordan 1 Low Pastel Pink Green GS' collar includes a soft green fabric finish and white laces to allow the pastel colours to really pop. For the sole, you have a white rubber mid and a grey semi-translucent outer sole flecked with colour.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Aqua

data.description: Marking the return of a timeless colourway, the Air Jordan 6 Aqua pays homage to the Michael Jordan-owned Charlotte Hornets NBA team. Featuring dynamic design lines and vibrant pops of colour, the supple suede upper delivers a premium spin on a classic silhouette. Fitted with an easy toggle fastening and breathable perforations, this design is rounded off with Air cushioning underfoot for enhanced performance on and off the court. Elevate your sneaker collection with the Air Jordan 6 Aqua.

fields.name: Air Jordan 12 Og Cherry 2023

data.description: Introducing a new take on the Tinker Hatfield design, the Air Jordan 12 OG Cherry 2023 is the first to introduce Zoom Air cushioning to Jordan's signature collection. Sporting a white upper wrapped in a varsity red pebbled leather, this pair is the perfect add of cherry aesthetic to your outfit. Stitch lines on the upper, inspired by the radiant sunrise, pay tribute to the original design. The phylon midsole and full-length Zoom Air cushioning ensure exceptional comfort with every step while the semi-translucent red rubber outsole reveals black herringbone traction pods, for impeccable grip. A carbon fibre shank plate enhances support and stability. Experience classic design with modern comfort in the Air Jordan 12 OG Cherry 2023.

fields.name: Jordan 4 Retro What The

data.description: One of Nike's most legendary silhouettes, the Jordan 4 has been refreshed to celebrate the model’s 30th anniversary. Combining the legendary colourways of the most timeless Jordan 4s into one, the Jordan 4 Retro What The arrives in White Cement, Military Blue, Fire Red and Black Cement. Crafted with a white leather base, it features a mismatched design that's sure to turn heads. The left shoe showcases a black base with white netting on the mid-panel for extra breathability, while vibrant eyelets create a futuristic look. The instantly-recognisable Jumpman on the tongue keeps things classic, balanced by a Nike Air badge at the back, reminiscent of the original pair from 1989. Complete with ever-present cushioning underfoot, the Jordan 4 Retro Blue White Red is a certified must-have.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Sashiko

data.description: Inspired by traditional Japanese craftwork, the Air Jordan 1 Low Sashiko takes on vintage-style aesthetics. Accented with touches of branding, its canvas base features frayed denim overlays detailed with decorative stitching. Its aged midsole houses Air cushioning for comfort, its padded collar adds extra support and its rubber outsole provides traction. Complete with an exposed foam tongue and classic laces, the Air Jordan 1 Low Sashiko is next to deserve a spot in your collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Tan Black Womens

data.description: Always on trend and able to reinvent any style, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Tan Black Womens is crafted from premium leather and synthetic materials, guaranteeing durability and support. The Air sole unit ensures plush cushioning, while the padded collar offers support. This colourway boasts white underlays paired with tan overlays, contrasted with black Swooshes adorning the sides. Walk the line between comfort and couture with the Air Jordan 1 Mid Tan Black Womens.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Pink Lavender Gs

data.description: Elevated with vibrant purple touches, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Pink Lavender GS is crafted using high-quality materials. Its leather upper is decorated with sidewall Swooshes and Jordan branding. The Air-cushioned midsole underfoot offers comfort, the textured outsole provides grip and padding in the collar adds extra support. Fastened with a secure lace closure, add the Air Jordan 1 Mid Pink Lavender GS to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Canyon Rust Womens

data.description: Enjoy softer, earthy colours offset by a deep rust tone with this pair of Air Jordan 1 Low Canyon Rust Womens. This sneaker is built with flexibility, balance, and comfort in mind with the sturdy Nike Air heel, shown in soft white to contrast attractively with the deep rust colour. The colouring of the Womens Air Jordan 1 Low Canyon Rust is ideal for the warmer summer or autumnal seasons whilst also offering a splash of colour for winter days. The Air Jordan 1 Low Canyon Rust Womens includes suede-effect leather panels for a softer look and combines rust-orange brown, white, off-white, and mauve. The laces are also designed in an attractive shade of mauve, and the sneaker is complete with a sturdy tongue of leather. The Nike swoosh is included in a faded-effect grey-black.

fields.name: Air Jordan 2 X Maison Chateau Rouge United Youth International

data.description: This iconic pairing presents the Air Jordan 2 x Maison Château Rouge United Youth International, a true celebration of modern African culture. This second collaboration between the two sees a Sail leather upper accented with bright orange details, complemented by the stitching in the laces and on the tongue. Debossed off-white panelling decorates the sneaker’s sidewalls, with the orange Wings logo sitting proudly on the shoe’s tongue. Finished with alternate lettered branding on each heel tab, this powerful sneaker has see-saw edging around the eyestay panels and a perforated pattern. A unique graphic of Michael Jordan on the insole completes the Air Jordan 2 x Maison Château Rouge United Youth International, a pair that promotes collaborative creativity in classic sneaker style.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Blueberry

data.description: A sneaker that’s full of flavour, the Air Jordan 1 Low Blueberry – also known as the Air Jordan 1 ‘Dark Violet’ – updates the iconic AJ1 Low silhouette with purple tones. Breathable perforations sit on the toe box for enhanced ventilation, while lightweight cushioning, a secure lace-up fastening and a unique textured tread work together to ensure this sneaker is highly functional. Rounded off with signature Jordan branding, the Air Jordan 1 Low Blueberry is an every-season staple.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Og Sp X Travis Scott Olive Td

data.description: Created in collaboration with Houston-born rapper Travis Scott, the Air Jordan 1 Low OG SP x Travis Scott Olive TD takes on muted tones and retro aesthetics. Made from a mixture of materials, its upper is decorated with reverse Swoosh detailing and touches of red branding. The Air-cushioned midsole delivers comfort, the perforated toe box allows for ventilation and the rubber outsole offers grip. Update your toddler’s collection with the Air Jordan 1 Low OG SP x Travis Scott Olive TD.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Jade Horizon

data.description: One of Jordan Brand’s most functional silhouettes, the Air Jordan 5 remains to this day one of the world’s best hoops shoes. Next in-line for a place in your collection is the Air Jordan 5 Jade Horizon. Crafted from plush, smooth leather with a perforated rubberised cage insert on the sidewalls, the oversized tongue serves to offer additional support and extra cushioning around your ankle. Underfoot, a visible Nike Air unit nods to Tinker Hatfield’s original design, while the light green colourway adds a new-school spin to the sneaker. An absolute must-have for Jordan collectors and sneaker lovers alike, add the Air Jordan 5 Jade Horizon to your collection and you’ll never want to take them off.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Kentucky Womens

data.description: Whenever the iconic Kentucky colourway graces a silhouette, the entire sneaker community take notice. The blue and white combination became famous thanks to the Nike Dunk representing the University of Kentucky. However, Jordan Brand has borrowed the schools' colours for a new take on the AJ1 Mid. The uppers of the Air Jordan 1 Kentucky Blue come crafted entirely from premium leather, with white underlays expertly contrasted by the Kentucky blue panels. Legendary branding features throughout the design of the shoe. You will find Swoosh detailing on the lateral and medial sides of the sneaker, whilst the OG wings logo features on the ankle collar. You can also find the Jumpman logo on the Jordan 1 Kentucky Blue's tongue. Underfoot the Jordan 1 Mid Kentucky Blue, a traditional Air Jordan 1 sole unit houses Nike Air technology, meaning this sneaker is ready for the court or the streets.

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Velvet Midnight Navy Womens

data.description: Presenting a premium take on the modern basketball shoe, the Air Jordan 11 Velvet Midnight Navy Womens boasts a classic two-toned colourway. Its nubuck leather base is decorated with velvet mudguard panels and Jordan branding. The Air midsole delivers comfort, the translucent rubber outsole provides grip and the speed lacing system allows for a tailored fit. Buy and sell the Air Jordan 11 Velvet Midnight Navy Womens with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Banned

data.description: A Jordan bathed in controversy since its inception in 1985, initially banned by the NBA Michael Jordan was fined $5000 per game for wearing the combination Red and Black Jordan 1's as they didn't include the colour white in conjunction with Chicago Bulls team colours. Not deterred by this, Nike used this as a marketing tactic crafting the 'Banned' Campaign in association with these high tops to promote this particular Air Jordan line. Ever since Michael Jordan defiantly wore them the eye-catching blend of black and red has been a fan favourite. Since then the shoes have been revived in 1994, 2011, 2013 and now with the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG banned coming out in September 2016. With this, a time honoured tradition continues to celebrate the defiance which made Michael Jordan an icon and a trailblazer in so many ways.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Elevate Low Cement Grey Varsity Maize Womens

data.description: Take your collection to the next level with the Air Jordan 1 Elevate Low Cement Grey Varsity Maize Womens, an updated take on an ‘80s basketball classic. Its mid-grey smooth leather base is dressed in contrasting yellow leather overlays and is complete with a matching bright-toned sidewall Swoosh. Minimal branding lets this modern AJ1 model do all the talking, with only an outline of the recognisable Wings logo decorating the heel tab. A trendy platform white midsole grounds the pair with reliable Air cushioning, whilst a chunky yellow-hued outsole features a textured finish for all-important grip. Crafted with a perforated toe box for prime breathability, the modified Air Jordan 1 Elevate Low Cement Grey Varsity Maize Womens is not one to be missed.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Retro Travis Scott British Khaki Ps
Air Jordan 2 Low X Shelflife White

The recognisable brands have joined forces to put a unique spin on the iconic Air Jordan 2 Low x Shelflife White. The white and light bone colourway is brought to life with touches of bright mandarin on the tongue branding, outsole, and insole. The leather and suede upper create a premium aesthetic, and the removable hang tags feature Air Jordan’s synonymous Jumpman. Finishing off the sneaker is a chunky midsole unit that provides its famous Air cushioning for unrivalled everyday comfort on the street or basketball court.

Pebbled white leather crafts the majority of the sporty shoe’s upper, with a grey-hued perforated toe box, as well as heel and collar panels, adding subtle depth to the design. A matching muted grey Swoosh sits on the sidewall, whilst an understated Wings logo is stamped onto the ankle overlay and a Nike-branded label adorns the tongue. The Air-cushioned crisp white midsole is grounded by a tonal grippy grey outsole to finish this minimal AJ1 with classic levels of comfort. Laced with versatility, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Stealth sees this streamlined ‘80s basketball silhouette take on a sleek new colourway.

The shiny varsity red overlays with a crisp white mesh upper will stand apart in even the most complete sneaker rotations. The icy outsole adds further freshness to the clean kicks, allowing the contrasting white and red colourway to shine. Featuring an iconic red Jumpman on the collar and between the thick white rope laces, add the Air Jordan 11 Cherry to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Ice Blue Womens

data.description: Influenced by UNC-inspired colourways, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Ice Blue Womens presents a modern take on the retro basketball model. Its leather upper is detailed with sidewall Swooshes and Jordan branding. Underfoot, the Air midsole delivers on comfort and the textured outsole provides grip. Perforations on the toe box allow for ventilation, while padding in the collar adds extra support. Find your size with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Pink Quartz Gs

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid Pink Quartz is a great addition to any sneaker head's collection. Featuring the iconic Nike swoosh and classic mid top style, this is popular as a woman's trainer. The easily recognisable pink rubber sole, leather material and detailing on the tongue makes the Jordan 1 Pink Quartz one of the most sought after releases to date.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Washed Pink Womens

data.description: Taking on pre-aged aesthetics, the Air Jordan 1 High OG Washed Pink Womens presents a new women's-exclusive colourway. Boasting muted tones, its leather base is decorated with suede overlays and touches of branding. fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low New Emerald Gs

data.description: Released in August 2022, the green and white colourway of the Air Jordan 1 Low New Emerald GS has taken clear inspiration from the original Air Jordan 1 Turbo Green model but offers a greener hue. The smooth white leather upper ensures the emerald-green overlay shines, which contrasts with light grey Nike Swooshes on the lateral and medial sides. Yet, you cannot miss the pops of yellow on the embroidered Jumpman on the white tongue or the recognisable Air Jordan 1 wings logo on the heel counter.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Racer Blue

data.description: A versatile sneaker that bridges the gap between fashion and function, the Air Jordan 5 Racer Blue is the next Jumpman kick to demand a place in your collection. Crafted with a plush suede upper, a caged insert on the sidewalls enhances air flow to ensure you say cool and comfortable whether on the court or off. A toggle on the lace-up fastening lets you customise the fit quickly, while the padded tongue and cushioning underfoot support you where you need it most. Easy to style courtesy of the clean black and blue colourway, add the Air Jordan 5 Racer Blue to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Infrared Retro 2019

data.description: Fans of the Jumpman brand will be well aware of the historical significance of the Nike Air Jordan 6 Infrared, and once again the much-loved high top is making a comeback, and in February 2019 you'll all be able to get a look at the revamped Jordan Infrared 6 2019 at the NBA All-Star Weekend. A living legend that was first worn by Michael Jordan as he took down the Los Angeles Lakers for his first of six Championships in 1991, this shoe has become synonymous with the Air Jordan 6 silhouette as the shapes flagship and most sought after colourway. Designed by Tinker Hatfield sporting a mostly black nubuck construction with bright hits of red (to which the Infrared name originates) on the midsole, tongue, and heel. Since its initial 1991 release in conjunction with the big win for the Chicago Bulls this shoe has been granted a vast array of re-releases, revamps and revivals. This 2019 Jordan Retro 6 Infrared addition is true to the pair's roots, switching from the Jumpman logo at the heel and insole favoured in the 2014 version, back to the original “Nike Air” branding for that even more significant hit of nostalgia.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro Fire Red Silver Tongue

data.description: There’s nothing like a retro pair of white sneakers with vibrant shark-tooth accents for a playful look, on the courts or on the streets. The minimalistic upper of the Air Jordan 5 Retro Fire Red Silver Tongue provides a clean white finish in smooth leather, running across the toe, side panels, and to the heel. The mid of the Air Jordan 5 Retro Fire Red Silver Tongue sneaker has a cut-out section of white mesh for extra layering, while the extra-large eyestay accessories also come in white against the clean white laces. The shoe is then given flashes of bright red around the collar fabric, on the tongue, with the lace’s toggle accessory, and along the black rubber mudguard in shark-tooth design. The black midsole then has a visible Air Unit and a semi-translucent rubber outer sole in light blue to finish.

fields.name: Air Jordan 2 High Chicago Td

data.description: Celebrating the model’s 35th anniversary, the Air Jordan 2 High Chicago TD draws inspiration from OG AJ2 styles. Its layered leather upper is detailed with touches of Jordan branding and features a line of perforations for breathability. Air cushioning underfoot offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and the classic lacing system rounds off the design. Update your toddler’s collection with the Air Jordan 2 High Chicago TD.

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Gratitude

data.description: Paying homage to the Jordan legacy, the Air Jordan 11 Gratitude sports a premium leather and knitted collar, complemented by a glossy mudguard that honours the OG aesthetic. The iconic gold Jumpman elevates the style. With a plush white sole, grounded by a transparent base, the Air Jordan 11 Gratitude effortlessly blends timeless allure with superior comfort.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Canvas Steel Grey

data.description: Crafted with recycled materials, the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Canvas Steel Grey presents an updated take on the retro basketball model. Boasting a muted colourway, its all-canvas upper is detailed with embroidered branding. Air cushioning in the speckled midsole delivers comfort, the textured outsole provides grip and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Shop the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Canvas Steel Grey with Laced now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Black Cat

data.description: Dropping in early 2020, the Air Jordan 4 Black Cat is unapologetically simple in its presentation, but incredibly versatile in its design. Utilising a suede and nubuck upper that engulf the entirety of the Jordan 4 Black Cat design, apart from the welcome addition of hard shell supper caps at the eye stay as well as shimmering cages across the vamp and profile that provide some textural divergence. Akin to the Black Cat moniker all of what has been mentioned appears in smokey black hue with a slight gloss present on the midsole. Don't miss out on a pair of Black Cat Jordan 4 sneakers for your collection!

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Defiant Nyc To Paris

data.description: Signifying the influence that this silhouette had on skating culture, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Defiant NYC to Paris boasts a worn look to celebrate this well-loved shape. Its Light Bone leather base is complete with tonal grey overlays that are finished with a wear-away layer concealing a pink tint which adds to the pair’s retro look. A signature Swoosh takes on a deep black hue to decorate its neutral sidewall, whilst matching black laces, ankle panel and Nike-branded tongue adds further depth to this classic model. The cream-toned Air midsole crafts it with complete comfort, as well as its perforated toe box allowing for key breathability. An appealing all-rounder: the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Defiant NYC to Paris is a muted must-have made to be worn in any situation.

fields.name: Off-White X Air Jordan 5

data.description: Virgil Abloh looks to begin the new decade as he means to go on, dropping heat with his long time collaborative partners Nike. The fabled 'The 10' Collection is nothing but a distant memory in 2020, but the keys to its success are still very much applicable. Meaning that the well established formula of taking a classic silhouette, in this case the Air Jordan 5, and enthusing it with a whole host of Off-White touches is definitely still a winning on. Presented in an all over metallic grey, with delicate hits of yellow offering a welcome contrast on the shoes outsole, the Off-White x Air Jordan 5 looks set to reaffirm Virgil Ablohs position as Nike's most popular asset going forward.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 X A Ma Maniere Violet Ore

data.description: Made in collaboration with James Whitner's fashion brand A Ma Maniére, the Air Jordan x A Ma Maniére Violet Ore is designed with luxury in mind. To finish, a miniature “It’s not about the shoes, it’s about where you’re going” inscription is added to the heel tab. Buy and sell the A Ma Maniére, the Air Jordan x A Ma Maniére Violet Ore with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey Womens

data.description: One of 2021’s most in-demand Air Jordan colourways, the Nike Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey Womens made waves when it first released, and fans of the silhouette are still keen to get their hands on this neutral-hued kick. Much like the OG AJ1, the upper on the understated sneaker is crafted from smooth leather with a Nike Swoosh on the sidewalls, Michael Jordan Jumpman on the tongue and a Jordan Brand Wings motif on the ankle. Underfoot, Air cushioning delivers the bounce and comfort the silhouette is famous for, while breathable perforations are scattered across the toe box for enhanced breathability. Add the Nike Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey Womens to your collection and it'll become your new go-to.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Nrg Homage To Home

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG NRG Homage to Home released in May 2018 is precisely what the name suggests, a homage to the Jumpman's spiritual home, Chicago. This brand new version of the Air Jordan 1 features a classic Chicago Bulls colour scheme, with a leather upper split between black and red. This creates an aesthetic that feels like two sides of the same coin, and a subtle not to not just the timeless Chicago but also the Banned colourways which have become some successful staples in the Jordan universe. Early versions from the initial Chicago-only release are numbered and include ‘FROM’ and ‘FOR’ lettering on the heels.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Limelight Womens

data.description: Jordan Brand shows no signs of slowing down its releases of the legendary Air Jordan 1, with the upcoming low in the Limelight colourway guaranteed to excite fans of the silhouette. The summer-ready sneakers see the usual white leather underlays switched out for a breathable mesh material. The clean white underlays are perfectly contrasted by the lime green hue used across the AJ1 panels. The panels come in premium tumbled leather, giving the sneaker a seriously luxurious feel. The Wings, Jumpman and Nike Swoosh detailing all feature, leaving no question that this is an Air Jordan 1. The sole unit perfectly compliments the uppers down below, thanks to the crisp white midsole and lime green outsole. This sole unit houses the Nike Air technology that made the sneaker famous and all but guarantees unbeatable comfort.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Flyease Aquastone

Finished with an added strap for extra support, buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 Low FlyEase Aquastone with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low White Pinksicle Gs

data.description: Sneakers don’t get much sweeter than the stylish Air Jordan 1 Low White Pinksicle GS. In collaboration with Dunkin’ Donuts, the famous coffee company, Nike has managed to create a candy-like shoe that you'll want to wear every day of the week. The sneaker colourway is, of course, inspired by Dunkin’ Donuts’ synonymous colours, and the Pinksicle hue appears on the mesh collar, outsole, and medial and lateral Nike Swooshes. Also, the Safety Orange shade stands out on the laces and embroidered Jumpman on the tongue tab. The white leather upper, tongue, and midsole pulls back the vibrant hues, improving the sneaker’s versatility and appeal.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low White Gym Red Womens

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Low White Gym Red colourway puts a fresh spin on a classic colourway. Sneaker fans may instantly realise this cool iteration is a play on the famous Black Toe colour blocking, which debuted in 1985 and is one of the most popular AF1s of all time. It's a reversed version of the popular colourway, as the traditional black toe cap, mudguard, eyestays, lateral and medial Nike Swooshes, and laces are replaced with a Gym Red hue. The red collar and heel counter are now adorned in black instead of red. Yet, some features remain unchanged, such as the fresh white leather upper with a perforated toe box and a white midsole. The iconic Jumpman this time appears in Gym Red on a white tongue, and a red outsole finishes off the retro-inspired design.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Triple White 2.0 2020

data.description: There’s nothing more iconic than a classic white sneaker; something that's been captured perfectly by the recent Air Jordan 1 Mid Triple White 2.0 2020 release. With a clean, minimalistic and fresh look you can depend on anytime, the Air Jordan 1 silhouette combined with pure white is an absolute must-have. You can pair it with any outfit and for any occasion, and know that you’ll have an elegant sneaker that looks and feels great. The Air Jordan 1 Mid Triple White 2.0 2020 combines panels of white leather flawlessly, including a fresh white Nike swoosh on the side panelling, and is balanced out with different fabric textures to bring out different shades of white, such as the nylon tongue and collar against crafted leather. The pure white rubber sole means maximum comfort, so you’ll feel like you’re walking on air, complete with clean white laces for a finished fresh look.

fields.name: Air Jordan 12 Field Purple

data.description: Taking on premium aesthetics, the Air Jordan 12 Field Purple will instantly elevate any everyday outfit. Detailed with Jordan branding, its leather upper also features vibrant reptile skin-textured panelling, decorative stitching and gold hardware. Zoom Air cushioning underfoot offers all-day comfort, while its rubber outsole provides effective grip. Complete with collar padding and classic laces, update your collection with the Air Jordan 12 Field Purple.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Infrared 2022 Gs

data.description: Gearing up to steal the throne from the Air Jordan 1, the Air Jordan 4 is making serious waves this season and the Air Jordan 4 Retro Infrared 2022 GS is no exception. Detailed with Nike’s legendary red hue, the grey nubuck upper features durable inserts, a breathable mesh panel and Michael Jordan’s legendary Jumpman branding on the tongue and heel. A secure lace-up fastening allows for a secure fit, while an Air unit underfoot ensures optimised comfort and bounce. Endlessly wearable thanks to the clean grey hue, add the Air Jordan 4 Retro Infrared 2022 GS to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Particle Grey Womens

data.description: This soft, elegant Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Particle Grey Womens sneaker comes with a minimalistic colourway that shows off a delicate grey in various panels and textures. The Air Jordan 1 silhouette, built for classic style, boosted Air comfort and versatility, here shows off a soft nubuck in light grey on the perforated toe box, the smooth side panels, and around the collar. This is overlaid by a darker grey in suede wrapping around the front, around the base heel tab, and up across the ankle strap. A taupe grey is then shown across the side front straps and up along the eyelet strip. The Nike Swoosh is included in taupe suede, while the grey heel strap includes a rubber grey Nike Air Wings logo. The Womens Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Particle Grey sneaker finishes with white laces, a white midsole, and a grey rubber outer sole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Fire Red Gs (2022)

data.description: Get your hands on the 2022 update of the Air Jordan 3 Retro Fire Red GS sneakers. The Tinker Hatfield design features a clean white upper with hits of fire red and cement grey. It's hard to miss the grey and black elephant print on the overlays, which compete with the vibrant red collar, midsole, eyelets, tongue Jumpman, and Nike Air branding on the heel. Also, the silhouette is enhanced by a visible Air unit in the sole’s heel. Find your size with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Elevate Low Black Gym Red Womens

data.description: Taking on an iconic colourway, the Air Jordan 1 Elevate Low Black Gym Red Womens presents an updated iteration of the ‘80s basketball model. Crafted from premium leather, its upper is decorated with sidewall Swooshes and understated Jordan branding. Perforations on the toe box allow for ventilation, while the platform Air midsole offers both height and comfort. The rubber outsole provides grip and the secure lace closure puts you in control of the fit. Find your size with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Black Royal Gs

data.description: A trusted classic that’s always on trend, the Air Jordan 1 Low Black Royal GS features white tones that dominate the quarter panel and midsole, while bold black takes over the tongue, laces, sock liner and leather overlays. Striking blue accents are seen on the vamp, heel counter, mid-foot Swoosh and embroidered Jumpman on the tongue. Completing the look is the Air unit in the heel that guarantees lightweight cushioning for an all day comfort, making the Air Jordan 1 Low Black Royal GS a wardrobe essential that never goes out of style.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Smoke Grey

data.description: Smoke grey and bold red work in harmony showcased in the iconic Air Jordan 1 High OG Smoke Grey with ultimate retro vibes. The classic Jordan wings logo is stamped on the side in black against a bold red ankle detail, the perfect contrast against softer shades of smoky grey. The subtle additions of bold colour are made more prominent by an otherwise neutral sneaker in white leather panels, white leather base, and grey overlays. The suede panelling in grey helps to complete the softer look of the Air Jordan 1 High OG Smoke Grey whilst still maintaining its versatility and stylish design. The Nike swoosh stands out in black against white leather, complete with black lacing helping to bring out pops of dark detailing against a lighter structure. Ultimate comfort meets stylish design in this pair of Air Jordan 1 High OG Smoke Grey's.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Golf Midnight Navy

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 High Golf Midnight Navy colourway is the golfing equivalent of a hole-in-one. Made for the green, you can trust the stylish sneakers will not look out of place when teeing off at any golf course or walking down the street. The blue and white design will match most clothing you own, ensuring you feel confident and comfortable every time you place them on your feet. The cool iteration is a stylish homage to the original Midnight Navy colourway that first dropped in 2001 to much acclaim. Yet, there are some noticeable differences, such as patent leather Midnight Navy overlays and Metallic Silver Nike Swooshes on the lateral and medial sidewalls. The white midsole contains Air cushioning that will help you reach the final putt with ease, and the outsole's pivot circle pattern will improve traction to help you remain on your feet all day long.

fields.name: Air Jordan 2 Retro Chicago Womens 2022

data.description: The elegant Air Jordan 2 Retro Chicago Women's 2022 colourway is back following a long-awaited return. Released in 2022 to celebrate the 35th anniversary of Michael Jordan's sophomore release, the iconic design is now available to new sneaker fan generations. The old-school classic has a Chicago Bulls-friendly aesthetic, celebrating Michael Jordan's career with the basketball team. For instance, the smooth white upper and scaly overlays pair with a Varsity Red heel counter and black midsole and laces. The simple yet stylish 1986 design is created in Italy, combining a minimalistic white aesthetic with sparse branding. The updated version has remained true to the original silhouette, but it offers an improved tongue and collar height and more premium materials across the upper to better reflect the Jordan Brand's history.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Off Noir Womens

data.description: Fashion and function meet in the Air Jordan 3 Retro Off Noir Womens. This sneaker showcases a sleek black nubuck upper with subtle grey elephant print overlays on the front and back. The eyestay and padded collar feature black perforated leather, complemented by moulded eyelets in an off-white finish. The tongue and back heel proudly display the iconic Jumpman logo. Comfort is priority with a two-tone midsole and an exposed Air-sole unit in the heel, providing both durability and breathability. Fashion and function meet in the Air Jordan 3 Retro Off  Noir Womens.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Retro Unc Blue

data.description: A silhouette that Michael Jordan wore on the way to his first championship, the Air Jordan 6 has a rich history, and the Air Jordan 6 Retro UNC Blue is no exception. A sneaker that utilises premium materials, industry-leading cushioning and iconic hues, this Air Jordan 6 ticks every box. The upper is crafted from smooth leather with breathable perforated panels, a toggle on the laces so you can customise the fit and Air cushioning underfoot for comfort and optimised performance. With Nike’s famous UNC blue dressing the sides and toe, this kick is ready for the warmer months ahead.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Take Flight Gs

data.description: Offering a spare-inspired design, the Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Take Flight GS is a certified must-have. Featuring white, crimson, blue, and black colour schemes, the Nike Swoosh is printed with “Take Flight” in contrasting shades of red and blue coloured font. The physics theme continues onto the fabric panels, which include space-like illustrations. The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Take Flight GS design is completed by a white midsole and black rubber outsole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Bred Toe

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid silhouette has re-emerged in the latter stages of 2019 once again as a viable option for the style conscious sneakerhead, and so accompanying this realisation is an ever diversifying pool of colourways for you to choose from. One of which being the Air Jordan 1 Mid Bred Toe, a take on the time honoured classic black, white and red Bred Toe palette that has braced almost every design in the expansive Air Jordan portfolio. This heritage colourway reintegrated just in time for the new decade shows everyone that the Air Jordan 1 Mid is back, and it is here to stay.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro Racer Blue Gs

data.description: Designed for a smaller and narrower sneaker size, this pair of Air Jordan 3s in Retro Racer Blue includes the iconic elephant print on the toe cap and on the heel. You can never go wrong with a simple colour scheme when it comes to sneakers, and this theme of clean white, soft grey, and simple blue bring a refreshing and cool look. The visible air unit on the Air Jordan 3 Retro Racer Blue GS adds that retro feel, as well as a pop of colour in Racer Blue, and the ankle is provided with the all-important cushioning for maximum comfort. The Jumpman logo is also displayed in attractive blue, and this is all contrasted perfectly by tumbled white leather panelling. The outer sole stands out in dark grey colouring, balancing out the white and blue tones.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Pollen Gs

data.description: This pair of Air Jordan 1s offers comfort and flexibility in its low design, providing a versatile shoe in bold block shades of warm yellow and fresh white. The Air Jordan 1 Low Pollen GS model means a smaller and more tailored fit without compromising on the classic appeal of this silhouette, perfect for narrower feet or younger wearers. The vibrant yellow colouring on the Air Jordan 1 Low Pollen GS is a warmer, golden tone, displayed on the Nike Swoosh, the outer sole, the heel, eyelet panel, and front tab. Contrasted with clean white, you have an attractive pair of sneakers fit for any purpose. The cushioned sole on the Air Jordan 1 Low Pollen GS sneaker means maximum comfort every time, and with your warm yellow laces against a backdrop of premium white leather, this is a sneaker you’ll love to wear, time and again.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Unc Gs

data.description: Combining the iconic blue and white colour scheme of the University of North Carolina with a narrower fit, this pair of Air Jordan 1 Low UNC GS sneakers is for those wanting to celebrate Michael Jordan’s own alma mater whilst needing a smaller construction. This is a pair of sneakers in a refreshing colour scheme you won’t want to miss. The bright and bold mix of white and blue mean a classic pair of Air Jordan 1s with a cool look for the courts and a lively look for the streets. Premium leather panels, as always, adorn the Air Jordan 1 Low UNC GS sneaker in layered shades of blue, white, and black. The Nike Swoosh is shown in blue leather, allowing the white and blue to truly pop. A blue nylon tongue and laces complete this iconic look, perfect for any diehard sneaker fan.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Green Toe

data.description: A world-famous silhouette that’s cemented its place in the sneaker hall of fame, the Air Jordan 1 Low Green Toe is a colourway that deserves a place in your collection. Nodding to the OG AJ1 design, the white, black and green upper is crafted from smooth leather with breathable perforations on the toe box that encourage air to flow freely around the foot. The sidewalls are detailed with Nike’s iconic Swoosh, while the Jordan Brand’s ‘Wings’ logo is stitched onto the heel. Of course, no Jordan 1 would be complete without Michael Jordan’s Jumpman on the tongue and reliable Air cushioning underfoot. Add the Air Jordan 1 Low Green Toe to your collection and you’ll want to wear them every single day.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Comfort Multi Colour

data.description: Continuing the legacy, the Air Jordan 1 High Zoom Comfort Multi Colour is one of the more attractive colourways to brace Michael Jordan's iconic AJ1 silhouette. Things start simple with a white base made from synthetic leather that lands on the toe box and mid-foot portions of the shoe's familiar shape, onto which the fun begins as hairy suede wraps around the forefoot and along with the tongue in a slightly-faded black hue maximising contrast. The real star of the show however is located further back, where a mix of materials brace the heel, collar and tongue of the shoe introducing various hits of gold, maroon and blue, a trifecta of colour that evokes the aesthetic of past Nike Dunks, another one Peter Moore-designed models that have drawn inspiration from dozens of college programs since debuting in 1985.

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Retro Cool Grey 2021

data.description: Famous for being one of Michael Jordan’s personal favourite Jordan Brand silhouettes, the Air Jordan 11 remains to this day a highly functional on-court basketball shoe. The next colourway to deserve a place in your collection is the Air Jordan 11 Retro Cool Grey. Staying true to the OG design, the upper of the Jordan 11 Cool Grey is crafted from a mix of patent leather and supple suede, while thick laces are added so you can customise the fit. Of course, no Jordan silhouette would be complete without MJ’s Jumpman logo, which is placed subtly on the heel on this kick. Fitted with expertly crafted cushioning underfoot, this high-top Air Jordan 11 Cool Grey sneaker for 2021 stops your ankle rolling during play, while giving you all the stability and comfort you need.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Unc 2022 Womens

data.description: This refreshingly light Air Jordan 1 Mid UNC 2022 Womens colourway comes in the classic Air Jordan 1 styling with mid collar, with a premium leather upper built for comfort and a cushioned sole supplying maximum traction. The upper comes in panels of matte leather, which begin in clean white across the perforated toe box, main mid panel, and across the ankle strap. This shifts to light blue for around the toe wrap, front side panels, eyestay strip, rear heel panel, and around the collar. Blue is also shown on the side Nike Swoosh, contrasting neatly against the white panel behind, while the white ankle strap shows off a blue Air Jordan Wings emblem. The two fresh shades combine for the sole, with a slim white rubber midsole and a blue rubber outer sole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Banned 2020 Gs

data.description: For sneaker fans of the iconic Air Jordan design with a high cut and breathable leather, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Banned 2020 GS is a pair of sneakers ready to show off your passion for incredible design. Black and red pair confidently in this sleek and impressionable Air Jordan, leaving the minimalistic sneaker in the rear-view and offering an eye-catching design in deep, rich shades. The dark tones of black and red in the Air Jordan 1 Mid Banned 2020 GS are offset brightly by a strip of white on the sole, with the Nike swoosh shown in all its glory in a dark shade of red. When it comes to bold footwear, nothing does it better than the Air Jordan 1 Mid Banned 2020 GS. Coupled with flawless design and cushioned padding, you can't go wrong with this pair of Jordan 1 Mid Banned GS sneakers for your next venture.

fields.name: Air Jordan 2 Low Cherrywood

data.description: Putting a premium twist on the retro basketball classic, the Air Jordan 2 Low Cherrywood is elevated with burgundy-hued accents. Made from leather and suede, its upper features a line of perforations, Jordan branding and a plastic heel panel. Complete with an Air-cushioned midsole, grippy rubber outsole and secure laces, the Air Jordan 2 Low Cherrywood is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Vintage Stealth Grey

data.description: Micheal Jordan’s signature model is updated with a minimal two-toned colourway in the simply stylish Air Jordan 1 Low Vintage Stealth Grey. The smooth white leather base is complete with a perforated toe box and is decorated with cool-toned grey leather overlays. A matching sidewall Swoosh works alongside a tonal Jumpman on the nylon tongue and an embroidered white Wings logo on the heel to subtly brand the understated sneaker. An off-white Air-cushioned midsole grounds the pair with unmatched comfort as well as retro appeal. Complete with a grippy grey outsole, the Air Jordan 1 Low Vintage Stealth Grey sees an ‘80s basketball model take on a versatile makeup that will never get old.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Og Bred 2019

data.description: Celebrating the 30th anniversary of the classic Air Jordan 4 silhouette, Air Jordan chooses its iconic OG Bred colourway Michael Jordan wore when he sank ‘The Shot’ during the first round of the 1989 NBA playoffs. Releasing in May 2019 the Air Jordan 4 OG Bred 2019 is rendered in a build that’s faithful to the original, complete with a black nubuck upper, visible Air-Sole cushioning underfoot and Nike Air branding on the heel. True to its name, this release is a true OG, and sometimes you can do nothing more than to marvel at an icon.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Retro 85 Black White

data.description: Sporting the brand’s iconic ‘Panda’ colourway, the versatile Air Jordan 1 High Retro 85 Black White also boasts retro aesthetics. Its premium leather upper is detailed with sidewall Swooshes and signature Jordan branding. The Air-cushioned midsole offers comfort, the rubber outsole provides grip and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Complete with padding in its collar for extra support, buy and sell the Air Jordan 1 High Retro 85 Black White with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Pinksicle Orange Toddler

data.description: The pretty and playful Air Jordan 1 Mid Pinksicle Orange colourway is a stylish addition to any toddler’s wardrobe. Fun and functional, the youthful design has everything you could want from a stylish sneaker: undeniable style, superb support, and all-day comfort. The smooth white leather upper pairs with vibrant pink overlays that appear young and playful, making it a perfect choice for fast-growing toddlers. The Safety Orange Nike Swooshes on the lateral and medial sidewalls provide a stylish contrast, ensuring everyone spots the cool kicks on your little one’s feet. Your child will be happy to walk, run, or jump in the sneakers all day long, as it includes encapsulated Air-Sole cushioning at the heel, a padded mid-cut collar, and a pink rubber outsole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Pink Red Gs

data.description: With this pair of Air Jordan 1 Low Pink Red GS sneakers in classic Low silhouette comes a red and pink colourway that makes a warm and bright impression. This bold colour scheme combines deep red, hot pink, and soft pink in layered panels, offset nicely by premium white leather and a perforated white toe box. The outer sole of the Air Jordan 1 Low Pink Red GS maintains the hot pink shade, while the midsole repeats clean white. These bright colours are made all the more effective with a sweeping black Nike Swoosh for contrast, as well as deep black laces along a red and pink eyelet panel. The Jumpman logo adorns the white tongue of the Air Jordan 1 Low Pink Red GS in hot pink, and the Nike heel logo works seamlessly with the heel panel in a matching shade of soft pink.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Turbo Green Retro High Og

data.description: Released in February 2019 the Air Jordan 1 Turbo Green Retro High OG combines a classic two-tone colour scheme with clean lines to create a clean and refined take on an iconic silhouette. This spearmint high top of the Turbo Green Jordan 1 marries a textured white leather base with contrasting soft suede overlays in a pastel hue of Turbo Green. With the latter element burnished to give off a vintage aesthetic, a quality that’s further enhanced by a midsole finished in off-white Sail. The Jordan 1 Retro High Turbo Green looks unequivocally retro and the faded white and washed out green combination gives off a very deliberate aged look. This kick is a well executed and classic design that is perfect for a multitude of styles.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 Retro Electric Green

data.description: The Air Jordan 6 is a silhouette many collectors hold in high esteem. The iconic Infrared colourway exploded onto the scene when MJ would rock the sneaker to his first NBA title. The upcoming Electric Green version draws clear inspiration from the OG silhouette but is given a dynamic upgrade. Lightening really has struck twice with this high voltage colourway, rejuvenating a classic. The sneakers upper is crafted entirely from stealthy black nubuck. The luxurious yet sleek look is contrasted by including the Electric Green accents that feature throughout the shoe. The green hue is used for the Jumpman branding on the tongue, whilst the iconic logo remains hidden on the heel thanks to the black-on-black tonal design. Down below, a glow in the dark sole unit features Nike Air technology for optimum comfort. A visible air bubble even stars, giving this silhouette a seriously OG feel.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Christmas

data.description: The iconic Air Jordan 1 silhouette receives a festive makeover with this Christmas design. Featuring a black upper with a geometric pattern and a seasonal red overlay, this shoe will complement all of your festive looks. Also, the warm green laces inject some festive fun into the shoe. The clean white midsole balances the contrasting Christmas colours while helping the kicks to stand out. Nike branding provides the perfect finishing touch, as it features a red Jumpman on the black tongue and insole, and the black Wings logo elevates the red collar. Inject seasonal style into your wardrobe with a pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid Christmas sneakers.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Hand Crafted

data.description: This OG pair of Air Jordan 1 High OG Hand Crafted sneakers comes with a layered premium upper with varying colour hues for a standout look. The Air Jordan 1 High OG Hand Crafted sneaker includes nubuck in warm chocolate brown running around the toe, front side panels, and the main ankle strap. The latter is also adorned with a fabric black and brown Air Jordan Wings patch. In smooth off-white leather, you have the perforated toe box as well as the main side panel. In black nubuck is the side Nike Swoosh, while black returns for the collar panels, this time in smooth leather. The eyestay strip features in green nubuck, while the heel side panels show off a blue-grey and purple, also in nubuck. The laces provide a mix of black and neon orange, while the sole finishes the look in white and black.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Bred Text Gs

data.description: Black and red colour blocking makes up the iconic colourway of this Air Jordan 1 Mid Bred Text GS, with elements of intricate simplicity elevating this classic full-leather silhouette. Gloss-printed “Black” and “Red” text is placed upon each correlating colour panel, whilst the themed phrase “Black + Red = Bred” can be seen on the isolated white midsole. Complete with an embroidered red Jumpman on the nylon tongue and stamped black Wings logo placed upon one of the Gym Red overlays, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Bred Text GS is a real celebration of MJ’s beginnings, making this straight-forward pair a must-have for your rotation.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey Anthracite Gs

data.description: A key pair for every season, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey Anthracite GS takes the crowd-favourite grey colourway and updates it with contrast stitching, clean branding and a mid-top fit. The all-leather upper features breathable perforations on the toe box, while lightweight cushioning is added underfoot to deliver both comfort and performance. Nike’s Swoosh sits on the sidewalls, accented with eye-catching stitching, while Jordan Brand’s logos adorn the collar and tongue. Easy to style thanks to the clean grey, black and white colour scheme, add the Air Jordan 1 Mid Light Smoke Grey Anthracite GS to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Lightning 2021

data.description: Tinker Hatfield's Air Jordan 4 is one of the most iconic silhouettes Jordan Brand has ever produced. The sneaker's popularity has boomed thanks to collaborations with Off-White, with the latest Air Jordan 4 Lightning rendition sure to send shockwaves through the industry. The Jordan 4 Lightning sneaker comes covered in luxurious nubuck suede, with Tour Yellow hue used throughout the design. Black accents are used across the silhouette, with the iconic AJ4 panels and Jumpman branding coming in the stealthy colour. Underfoot the Jordan 4 Retro Lightning, a traditional Air Jordan 4 sole unit comes dressed in black and white with a visible air bubble. You can find Nike Air technology running the length of the Jordan 4 Lightning sneaker, giving unbeatable comfort wear after wear.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Hyper Royal

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid is slowly becoming one of the hottest sneakers within the industry. With releases like the Jordan 1 Mid Hyper Royal it's easy to see why. A colourway reminiscent of the Jordan 1 High 'Royal Blue', we guarantee the Air Jordan 1 Mid Hyper Royal will be one of the years best releases. The black underlays are contrasted expertly by the 'Hyper Royal' blue panelling. Legendary branding such as the Swoosh and Jumpman logo feature throughout, also in the eye-catching blue hue. We also see the Wings logo return to the shoe's ankle in black to ensure the logo pops against the blue. Underfoot the Jordan 1 Hyper Royal Mid, a classic Air Jordan 1 sole features with a black outsole and white midsole. This sole unit houses the iconic Nike Air technology that has made the Air Jordan such a hit. The 'Royal Blue' AJ1 High was one of the greatest Jordan releases, and we expect the 'Hyper Royal' Jordan 1 Mid to reach the same dizzying heights.

fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Starfish Womens

data.description: The Air Jordan 4 is quickly becoming one of the most iconic silhouettes within the sneaker space, and with releases like the upcoming Starfish, it's easy to see why. The women's AJ4 sees the legendary shoe dressed in a technical, hardwearing material instead of the usual leathers. A mix of black, grey, cream and orange make up the colour palette used for this sneaker. The orange accents throughout ensure this sneaker pops when on foot. You can find the Jumpman branding on the tongue and heel of the sneaker. Down under, an OG AJ4 sole unit features a visible air bubble showing off the Nike Air technology used. This sole unit is a mix of the colours of the upper, finishing off this legendary design. This sneaker has drummed up a lot of hype since it was initially teased, be sure to add a pair to your collection before it is too late.

fields.name: Air Jordan 7 Retro Flint 2021

data.description: As always with the timeless Air Jordan 7 silhouette, embracing the retro is a must, and the Air Jordan 7 Retro Flint 2021 sneaker has it all. The understated colourway provides a jagged cut cage-like upper in premium white leather offset against soft grey suede panelling for a clean finish. The grey back fabric panels also include a perforated design, not only for breathability but for a little extra style. The holed pattern continues for the matching grey rubber outer sole, which also includes a jagged glossy black border in patent leather and a cut white midsole for a bold effect. The tall Air Jordan 7 Retro Flint 2021 silhouette is complete with a vibrant purple Jumpman logo on the collar, offset perfectly against its grey suede background. The purple continues for the logo adornment on the black and grey tongue, with white laces to finish.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Zen Master Gs

data.description: Calming tones of iridescent Zen hues combine with timeless black and white for the elegant Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Zen Master GS sneaker. Here in the Air Jordan 1 Mid styling comes this special edition sneaker in Grade School sizing, complete with premium leather upper and cushioned rubber sole. The upper comes with a breathable perforated toe box in white leather and a white main mid-side. Black then adorns the front toe wrap, front side panels, and eyestay strip, as well as around the collar, all in leather. The fabric tongue also comes in deep black, as do the laces. The purple and grey Zen ankle strap comes embossed with a black Air Jordan Wings logo, while the smoky colouring repeats for the main heel strap. The sole finishes the look with a white mid and a black outer.

fields.name: Nike Sb X Air Jordan 4 Pine Green

data.description: Following on from their 2019 collaboration, Nike SB and Air Jordan team up once again to release the Nike SB x Air Jordan 4 Pine Green. Made from a mixture of mesh, leather and suede materials, its upper is detailed with touches of branding. Air technology in its midsole offers comfort, the gum rubber outsole provides grip and padding in its collar adds extra cushioning. Fastened with a classic lacing system, add the Nike SB x Air Jordan 4 Pine Green to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Gs Barcelona Sweater

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE GS Barcelona Sweater takes the favoured Chicago Bulls red and adds a candy apple twist. Coating the hue in patent leather, panels of bright white make it really pop, while breathable perforations on the toe box add a functional element. Nike’s Swoosh branding sits in its usual place on the sidewalls, while Jordan Brand’s Wings logo graces the ankle - and, of course, no AJ1 would be complete without Michael Jordan’s Jumpman on the tongue. Stealing the show, a yellow, blue and red pattern adorns the ankle, nodding to the famous patterned jumper MJ wore in Barcelona way back in 1992.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Dark Mocha Gs

data.description: This pair of Air Jordan 1 Dark Mocha GS trainers comes in a sleek, neutral colourway that's ideal for slimmer and smaller feet. The majority of the premium upper is made from white and black, but it's the accents of brown mocha in soft suede on the heel tab and ankle strap that complete the sophisticated design. The Nike Swoosh is placed in black against the white side leather of the Air Jordan 1 Dark Mocha GS, a hue which is continued for the perforated toe box, tongue, collar, and chunky midsole. Black is then repeated for the rubber outer sole, side front panels, eyelet panels, and laces, as well as black bordering for the fabric collar. The Air Jordan Wings logo is stamped in black on the soft mocha suede, completing the fresh Air Jordan 1 Dark Mocha GS colourway that's perfect for any season.

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 X Travis Scott Medium Olive

data.description: The Travis Scott x Air Jordan 6 Medium Olive which is set to launch on September 2019, was first debuted by Scott himself during his performance at halftime of Super Bowl 53. Marking another addition to an ever-growing collaborative portfolio between the Houston based rapper and Jordan Brand. The pair in question features an olive upper with black, sail and university red detailing. While the model also comes equipped with some unique elements exclusively for this shoe. These include a small pocket with a snap on the collar, a nubuck and suede upper, Scott's 'Cactus Jack' logo on the heel and a glow-in-the-dark translucent outsole.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Volt Visionaire

data.description: With its unmissable neon hits, the Air Jordan 1 High OG Volt Visionaire is definitely one of the brightest colourways yet in the Jordan family. Loud Volt accents sit upon the premium white leather base, with black overlays, Swoosh and Wings logos all working together to break up the textured yellow panelling. This modern spin on a retro silhouette is the perfect combination of staple and striking, with the black laces and outsole bringing this sunny sneaker back down to earth. The trademark full-length Air midsole and a perforated toe box for ventilation complete this stand-out pair, making the Air Jordan 1 High OG Volt Visionaire the ideal eye-catching sneaker for any situation.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Zoom Cmft Patent Purple Womens

data.description: Bold, textured and bang on trend, the Air Jordan 1 Zoom CMFT Patent Purple Women’s updates the classic AJ1 with comfy cushioning, premium fabrics and textured branding. The upper is crafted from a blend of tumbled and patent leather, with Nike’s Swoosh arriving on the sidewalls in smooth satin. Breathable perforations are punched into the toe box for enhanced ventilation, while industry-leading Zoom cushioning is added to the midsole to support your every stride. Designed to make a statement, the purple hue is impossible to miss. A must-have for any and every collector, add the Air Jordan 1 Zoom CMFT Patent Purple Women’s to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 2 Black Cement

data.description: Taking on a classic AJ3 colourway, the Air Jordan 2 Black Cement boasts retro aesthetics and a premium construction. Its leather upper features snakeskin-textured panels, signature Jordan branding and a ribbed rubber heel overlay. Perforations allow for ventilation, the Air-cushioned midsole offers comfort with every wear and its durable rubber outsole provides grip. Fastened with a secure lace closure, elevate your everyday outfits with the Air Jordan 2 Black Cement.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Se Union Black Toe

Bold black then wraps around the toe, moves across the front side straps and up along the eyelet panel in matte leather, while the ankle strap includes a black and white Air Jordan Wings stamp. For the sole, you have clean white for the rubber mid and a return to soft baby pink for the rubber outer sole for a flash of colour with every step.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Unc X Off-White

data.description: Taking inspiration from Michael Jordan's alma mater the May 2017 release of the Air Jordan 1 Retro High UNC x Off-White is dressed in a classic blue and white colourway a tribute to its source material and modelled on Virgil Abloh's deconstructed reimagining of the classic Air Jordan 1 silhouette. The detached wings and floating ‘Swoosh' with a touch of colour with exposed orange stitching is a now staple of Virgil's prototype Esq stylings that have become so successful with his Off-White releases. The handmade feel of the shoe and attention to detail makes the quality of this kickstand alone, and his dedication to delivering fresh takes on iconic silhouettes what makes people both reminiscent and excited about every new release.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Silver Toe Womens

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 High Silver Toe is the perfect example of comfort meeting sleek design. This pair of sneakers is distinctive for the metallic silver colouring set to make an impact no matter where you wear these shoes. Silver, black, and white combine flawlessly on this classic silhouette, and the premium leather creates a pair of shoes that are a pleasure to wear. No matter whether you’re wearing them on the street or the court, this metallic silver design is sure to make an impact and become a firm favourite. Black laces blend seamlessly into the black eyelet leather and nylon tongue. The supportive sole is made for maximum comfort, and the Air Jordan 1 Retro High Silver Toe Womens is completed with the Air Jordan wings logo and classic Nike swoosh.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Tan Suede

data.description: A neutral sneaker with endless styling potential: the Air Jordan 1 Mid Tan Suede nods to the OG 1985-designed sneaker with its streamlined shape and underfoot Air cushioning. The upper is crafted in a premium blend of leather and suede, while the ankle comes in a breathable fabric and is complete with extra padding to support your ankle. Swoosh branding sits in its usual place on the sidewalls, with Air Jordan’s Wings logo stealing the show on the collar. A tan hue is perfectly complemented by hits of burgundy and navy, whilst a pastel grey outsole grounds the pair with all-important grip. Deserving of a spot on your sneaker shelf, add the Air Jordan 1 Mid Tan Suede to your collection now.

fields.name: Jordan 6 Retro Red Oreo

data.description: The silhouette Michael Jordan was wearing when he won his first ring, the Air Jordan 6 holds a special place in the hearts of sneaker fans. Next in line to deserve a spot in your collection is the Jordan 6 Retro Red Oreo — AKA the Air Jordan 6 White and University Red. Made with summer in mind, the leather upper is crafted with breathable perforations, an icy outsole and and an easy toggle fastening for good measure. A handle on the heel makes them easy to get on and off without squashing down the back, while the crisp white hue makes the Jordan 6 Retro Red Oreo effortless to wear with anything and everything.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Tiki Leaf Red Womens

data.description: Crafted with premium materials, the Air Jordan 1 Mid Tiki Leaf Red Womens refreshes the ‘80s basketball model with an exotic update. Its suede and leather upper is detailed with embroidered Swooshes as well as palm-leaf patterned panels. The Air midsole underfoot offers comfort, the textured outsole provides grip and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Complete with padding in its collar, elevate your collection with the Air Jordan 1 Mid Tiki Leaf Red Womens.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Satin Bred Womens

data.description: Borrowing familiar colour blocking from the 2016 release, the Air Jordan 1 High OG Satin Bred Womens takes inspiration from Michael Jordan’s world-famous “Banned” sneaker. Crafted with shiny satin, the upper boasts Wings branding, functional laces and an iconic red and black colour scheme. A supportive collar provides advanced comfort, while Air cushioning underfoot makes the Air Jordan 1 High OG Satin Bred Womens an essential for all-day wear.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og Yellow Toe Ps

data.description: Taking on the brand’s iconic colour-blocking, the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Yellow Toe PS is crafted using premium materials. Featuring a perforated toe box for ventilation, its leather upper is detailed with Nike and Jordan branding. Air cushioning underfoot delivers comfort, the rubber outsole offers grip and the secure lace closure allows for a tailored fit. Add the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG Yellow Toe PS to your kid’s collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro Raging Bull 2021 Gs

data.description: The Raging Bull Air Jordan 5 was initially released way back in 2009 and is one of the silhouette's legendary colourways. This release is the first time this AJ5 has dropped in Grade School sizing. The uppers are crafted from buttery suede throughout, with a Raging Bull red hue used for the sneaker's colourway. Black accents compliment the legendary design, with the Jumpman logo on the heel contrasting the shoe's upper. MJ's jersey number, 23, features on the sneaker's heels finishing the upper's design. Underfoot, a black sole unit houses Nike Air technology which guarantees comfort wear after wear. The shark tooth design across the midsole features a partly translucent outsole showing off another Jumpman logo.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Retro High Og First Class Flight

data.description: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG First Class Flight was first leaked way back in May of this year. Originally called the 'Shipping Department', this model features an ultra-clean leather upper that is painted in white with yellow hues delicately splattered across the design. Aviation inspired detailing can all be found across the entirety of the model with a boarding pass style barcode at the collar and embellishments that pay homage to air travel. One of the most unique colourways in the thirty-four-year history of the Air Jordan 1, this pair definitely deserves a spot in your collection.

fields.name: Air Jordan 3 Mars Stone Gs

data.description: Updating the retro basketball model, the Air Jordan 3 Mars Stone GS boasts a planet-inspired design. Its layered leather upper is accented with Jordan branding, TPU eyelets, a rubber heel panel and elephant-print overlays. The visible Air unit in the off-white midsole offers comfort, the textured outsole provides grip and padding in the collar adds extra support. Complete with a secure lace closure, the Air Jordan 3 Mars Stone GS is available to buy and sell with Laced.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Og Sp X Travis Scott Olive Ps

data.description: Made in collaboration with American rapper Travis Scott, the Air Jordan 1 Low OG SP x Travis Scott Olive PS takes on a mixture of muted tones. Its suede and leather upper features reverse Swooshes as well as contrasting touches of branding. Perforations on the toe box allows for ventilation, Air cushioning underfoot offers comfort and the rubber outsole provides grip. Elevate your kid’s everyday looks with the Air Jordan 1 Low OG SP x Travis Scott Olive PS.

fields.name: Jordan 1 Mid Black Arctic Pink Gs

data.description: Black and pink is a classic colour combination that has always worked well together. The dark-deep contrast of charcoal black versus the powdery subtleness of the light pink on these Air Jordan 1 Mid Black Arctic Pink GS sneakers is a winning combination. Coupling great design with the Air Jordan 1 promise of quality and looks, the Jordan 1 Mid Black Arctic Pink GS sneakers take shoes to the next level. Don’t let the seemingly minimalistic design fool you; these mid-rise sneakers pack a punch with leather uppers and the arctic pink Nike swoosh logo for added contrast and colour combination. There are numerous striking touches on the Jordan 1 Mid Black Arctic Pink GS, but the contrasting Air Jordan wings logo does it for us. Perfection!

fields.name: Air Jordan 11 Cherry Td

data.description: Elevate your kid's collection with the Air Jordan 11 Cherry TD sneakers. The fresh sneaker design features the same two-tone colour blocking from the popular Air Jordan 11 Varsity Red that dropped in 2001, as it offers a patent leather red overlay that contrasts with the clean white upper, laces, and midsole. You can trust your child will look too cool for school thanks to the famous Jumpman in red at the lateral heel. Plus, the sneakers will feel comfortable on your little one's feet due to the full-length Air cushioning.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Unc Blue Womens

data.description: A refreshingly bright colour palette with soft blue and clean white, this pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid UNC Blue Womens sneakers in mid silhouette comes with a premium leather upper constructed of mainly white panels running from the perforated toe box, for extra breathability and comfort, across the mid panels, along the heel and up across the ankle strap. The white ankle strap is then printed with a light blue Air Jordan Wings logo, above the side Nike Swoosh, also in light blue leather. The collar panels are shown in blue, while the tongue switches to a soft grey behind clean white laces. For the sole of the Air Jordan 1 Mid UNC Blue Womens, you have a white mid and a light blue outer, with premium rubber built for boosted comfort and maximum grip, whether on the courts or on the streets.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og University Blue Unc

data.description: Sporting an iconic colourway inspired by the University of North Carolina, the Air Jordan 1 High OG University Blue takes on classic colour-blocking. Perforations on its toe box allow for ventilation, Air cushioning underfoot offers comfort and its rubber outsole provides grip. fields.name: Air Jordan 4 Retro Off-White Sail Womens

data.description: It's been a minute since Virgil Abloh's Off White had dropped a sneaker with Nike, but it was most definitely worth the wait. The silhouette Virgil got his hands on this time around was the Air Jordan 4, a shoe he has not collaborated on before. We have seen this colourway on several occasions over the last year. Firstly, at the "Figures of Speech" exhibit, Chicago, then again in Off-White's Paris FW20 show. We are glad to finally see a release date set with the 25th of July. The sneaker was also placed on eBay recently by Abloh to raise money for various Black Lives Matter organisations. Fetching a final sale price of around $186,859.49 you know the hype for Off-White collaborations shows no signs of slowing down. This Jordan 4 comes dressed in an extremely minimalist colourway, featuring Sail, Cream and White accents throughout. The classic Jordan hangtag also in cream, staying consistent with the rest of the shoe. How do we know this is another Virgil Abloh collaboration? You have the ever-present Off-White zip-tie for instant recognition, as well as the notable "AIR" branding on the heel. The minimalist design of this sneaker all but guarantees it will become a grail for sneakerheads Worldwide and one you do not want to miss.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Premium Elephant Print

data.description: This timeless Air Jordan 1 Low Premium Elephant Print silhouette comes in a sophisticated, minimalistic colourway in soft grey and clean white, providing a great tribute to elephants. Adding something a little extra to the design is the unique elephant print leather panelling adorning the Nike Swoosh and the side-front eyelet panels, adding texture and character to this elegant shoe. The rest of the Air Jordan 1 Low Premium Elephant Print sneaker combines the grey and white leather panels, including a grey heel tab and dark grey outer sole, while the collar embraces a soft fabric for maximum comfort. Clean and bright white laces help the grey and elephant print to really stand out, while a white rubber midsole popular with any pair of Air Jordan is built for support, comfort, and bounce with every step you take in the Air Jordan 1 Low Premium Elephant Print sneakers.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low White Toe

fields.name: Air Jordan 6 University Blue Unc Gs

A toggle finalises the lace-up fastening, so you can quickly adjust the fit, while Air cushioning underfoot supports you in all the right places. A must-have for the season ahead, add the Air Jordan 6 University Blue UNC GS to your collection now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 12 Black Taxi

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Lv8D X Union La X Bephies Beauty Supply High Womens

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Se Light Purple

If you’re a fan of Michael Jordan’s original shoe, then no doubt you’re always on the lookout for interesting new colourways to add to your collection, so this mix of premium purple, white and black leather could be the one for you. With the iconic Nike Swoosh displayed in black, matching the outer sole, laces, and collar edging, the Air Jordan 1 Low SE Light Purple is also a sneaker providing a variety of materials, including dependable leather and perforated suede.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Sanddrift Womens

A must-have for your collection, get your hands on the Air Jordan 1 Mid Sandrift Womens now.

fields.name: Paris Saint-Germain X Air Jordan 7 Retro

The premium upper is dominated by a tumbled white leather casing, which is overlaid on a white mesh background that allows the blue and red colouring to show through. This panel includes a PANAME label in white on grey, while the second mesh panel on the ankle comes adorned with a metallic gold Jumpman logo. The red and blue stripes are revealed in full colour on the ankle of the Paris Saint-Germain x Air Jordan 7 Retro sneaker and also on the tongue. The heel tab comes in white with a strip of red. Air holes are included on the front side panels for extra breathability, while the midsole comes with jagged layered rubber in black and white.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low White Blue Grey

fields.name: Clot X Air Jordan 5 Low Black

Michael Jordan’s Jumpman sits on the left side, while CLOT’s branding can be found on the right. A must-have for any Jordan collector, get your hands on the CLOT x Air Jordan 5 Low Black now.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Low Neutral Grey 2021

data.description: For those who prefer a more minimalistic sneaker, white and grey offer the neutral and sophisticated tones you’re looking for — and that’s what you get with the iconic Air Jordan 1 Low Neutral Grey 2021 sneaker. Combined with the timeless low silhouette any Air Jordan fan will know, this altogether offers a sneaker you can depend on for any occasion, weather, and outfit. Solid white premium leather will stand the test of time, offering a stylish and sleek look throughout the Air Jordan 1 Low Neutral Grey 2021. A subtle grey accent of the Nike Swoosh provides a simple contrast that’s nonetheless effective. This muted grey tone in soft suede-effect panelling continues both on the heel of the shoe and the collar. You can also find it on the outer sole of a Air Jordan 1 Low Neutral Grey 2021 for a seamless look all round.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid Racer Blue 2020 Gs

data.description: While at first glance the Air Jordan 1 Mid Racer Blue 2020 GS may seem like a more minimalistic colourway in simplistic shades of white and black, the additions and pops of colour create a stylish sneaker with an edge. The most prominent colour choice on the Air Jordan 1 Mid Racer Blue 2020 GS is the bright racer blue included on the side Nike Swoosh which catches the eye, set off nicely by the premium white leather background. Another pop of colour is included with the bright orange Nike Air logo on the black tongue. The rest of the upper on this pair of Air Jordan 1 Mid Racer Blue 2020 GS trainers is crafted from premium white leather and soft black suede-effect. The sole is given lift and volume with a combination of black and white while ensuring your feet are always supported with Nike Air comfort.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 High Og Unc To Chicago Womens
